Wbz3_xO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Zeke from Steve’s Plumbing was awesome! He was super friendly and very knowledgeable. He checked my hot water heater and toilet, then around my condo for potential problem sites. He identified a leak in the making in my primary bathroom. Once everything was checked and assessed, he presented the estimate and explained in detail all the charges. I gave the go ahead and Zeke set up and changed out my old hot water heater and toilet. I had him clean the sink line. His work was neat and tidy. There was no debris left behind. I asked questions along the way and he took the time to explain his answers. I’m super happy and impressed with the speed and competency of his work. Thank you.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ML5B_CMDteDMpwczDFUSCiNG-qt6RGz8DY2MZZH-cZdiKOKlttvajn_GMUVr_aGGGg7FNoG76mlo8xu4hLaIKUhgneC9Wl1mqyxYb2D_ZQSzUr4vVtkaxpilx5jyCnga3NQlgWtX9mgGZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Qfqu9xlBZD4gZERAWM_GC_PYg0qEEf8yHijQHI1-tOltNq7z8XwzQuW8A-MVN02p7cjV69sailAV304JBTXglSxD4frOYX2p0Droty4jVdPlJ5GmrhdIzlYzBnEfUz-c_HgY3MbB78tnW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0llMIYu1KtuRtiaee2DsQDmyYu-MLHW40AHfWLZqaqXs6jhPTsDXBz3zibsRYF6M3THu03drf0Fh9Lobdv1f1ocX2qrHnGcUkKM05HslAvOHgRODe66c3lrHsQYw5GsaAOHHh3pj35mv_M=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-11"},{"Name":"Michael Fend","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBrXHg8M_7vsIjbAOqbKdQUcZ1FHb9cMLwjYhLmlCLCWx0FWc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I owned Simply Leak Detection for many years, and whenever one of our customers needed a plumber for water line repair or plumbing work, I would often refer them to Steve’s Plumbing. In all that time, I never received a single complaint about their work—something that’s honestly rare in the service industry.\nCustomers frequently told me that the team at Steve’s Plumbing went above and beyond what was expected. They are knowledgeable, experienced, and clearly take pride in doing the job right the first time.\nSteve Egner has built an excellent reputation for taking care of his customers. Since starting his company, he has created a culture where his technicians carry the same mindset of professionalism, quality workmanship, and customer service. That kind of leadership from the top down shows in the work they deliver.\nBecause of that, I confidently referred many repair jobs to Steve’s Plumbing in the past, and I will continue recommending them to customers through my new business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lacy Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqFbWxjD9xb6oc86_gfb877C67foWwX73W4XDg2I6q6Rkbj4R0sg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Plumber was excellent, had a sewage smell in the bathroom, he gave us an easy fix and didn't try to upsell. Reattatched our tub spout and fixed it so it works properly. Did a thorough inspection of other plumbing around the house to make sure all was in good working order. He was very knowledgeable and explained everything in detail, even things that didn't have to do with plumbing as I had lots of questions. Very reasonable price. Will definitely call them in the future if I need any repairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sue Noh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIarSvmV9V-XBdTz5pDOQ-rwBtklHhxAm_as2I_A4mHXGVYcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I extremely recommend Charlie Tait to be your plumber. If I could give him 6 out of 5 stars I would. Much like how he looks, his work was amazing. He is a professional and has sufficient knowledge in his field of work. If you are worried about the money, don’t be. Charlie looks at his work in the perspective of the customer and gives reasonable honest prices and the work that he did was absolutely worth the money. When doing the plumbing work at my house he worked late and finished the job in just two days. It was extremely impressive as the job that needed to be done required pulling up concrete tiles in my backyard. He not only fixed the necessary parts but also the unnecessary even when not requested. If I have another plumbing job in the future, I will call Charlie Tait. Not only Charlie, but Steve’s Plumbing is an amazing company that has various payment plans. You should absolutely look at their plans and I guarantee there will be one for you! Thank you Charlie!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cynthia Robson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8yXYU4lX-W8b3da9rX_-1V53corym8QWJaze1TjuclbUqVSjp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brandon and Zeke arrived promptly; Brandon had called ahead to confirm, which was appreciated.\nBoth men were very pleasant, professional and at ease with our dog.\n\nBrandon assessed the problem, and provided a detailed explanation and rationale for the repair which he tested several times before informing us it had been completed.\nZeke did the assessment of all of the rest of our plumbing, and left a chart with his findings.\n\nWe were not pressured to do more repairs.\n\nVery happy with the service, and to support a local small business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaitlyn Shorett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIl-leg20apuNJyl3Fmmyo2Heh0V7WlNLwFoCfhVLGwq4zMlw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with Steve’s Plumbing. They upgraded our shut-off valves, fixed a leak in our shower, and installed a new water heater, and everything was done efficiently and with great attention to detail. Dimitri and Terence were both very polite, professional, and easy to work with. They did excellent work and made sure everything was cleaned up before they left, which we really appreciated. We’re happy to have Steve’s Plumbing as our go-to plumbers and would highly recommend them to anyone needing reliable, high-quality plumbing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kekoa keo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9vW1phl8a4h-mOgCmi0FoIvPinXig_ZqhpKnow53nxip25w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dylan came out and did a walk through on all plumbing equipment. He took his time to inspect and answer all questions asked. Was pleased with the feedback and recommendations. Overall great service and quality work will be continuing to use Steve's plumbing for further services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brent Karlen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPknUATurpqepwosY7E0a4bHQLHqvnpjkwgNnURZw_qk896Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service from Steve’s Plumbing, when our family was in a jam. Luke was quick making it out to our house, where we had a pipe burst inside a wall. He found the issue and made the repair quickly, and was incredibly helpful explaining as he went. Will definitely be going back for any future needs - thanks!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
