y had our water back on less than five hours after starting work.  They also relocated our main water shutoff and front hose bib valves so they are much easier to reach now.\n\nThe city inspector came by the next day and told us he was very impressed with the quality of their plumbing work.\n\nPatching and texturing the drywall was also done quickly the following day.  When we told Eric we were not quite satisfied with one of the patched areas, he sent has crew back out to rework it.  We were not sent a bill until we were completely satisfied with the job.\n\nIf you're looking for high-quality work at a very reasonable price, you should definitely consider Express Repiping.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dora Reffett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0wY7NDwk24KuTX4Q4qlW_xeRbGLURadaKZBALt3SSXl0hajGl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This has got to be the best repiping Company in the whole Northwest.\n\nIn the recent months, my husband and I realized that we were going to need to repipe our entire home. It was definitely a pickle that we did not see coming. I felt very frustrated and decided to research online. I called several companies and received four in-home estimates.\n\nEric is incredibly honest and gave us a very fair quote. I could really tell he knew his craft. We knew that we were not going to be disappointed. Eric was the most honest, reliable, professional, prompt, and above all, talented out of everyone else.\n\nI would 100% recommend Express Plumbing and Repiping for your home.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Hill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf2JRAqgi-vHmo0oU5y3N6kWGiVgHuT_uEk3vITCktpUtJAi5O=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eric and crew were efficient and professional. They replaced my CPVC with Pex and installed a new water heater all in one day. The crew was detailed and friendly - they answered all my questions and installed new hose bibs outside in new locations no charge. I highly recommend their services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Omer Cansizoglu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCdzz-EQhm6V14e095klB0kPODpKs0-8viY3Vt9V5G-lF0K-0ryw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eric and his team such a fantastic job to repipe the house entirely. Eric was on time to give an estimate and walked through the repiping work initially. I was able to compare the quotes and companies. I decided to go with Express Repiping because of their positive reviews and Eric's experience. They did a nice job and i suggest this company for your repiping work. They converted all inside, outside pipes and did the patch work. I only need to find a painter now.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tabitha Pomeroy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLf2iNl0xCiavnvjVFMjtc0oMCvkgAD-znX9sdPQjnY5hEVsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eric and his team were wonderful to work with! Eric met me on the weekend and explained everything. He was very knowledgeable and thorough with what would happen during our repiping. His team arrived on time and finished when promised. They also cleaned everything up after. The price was very reasonable. I highly recommend Express Repiping!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vandna Thakkar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPnP5ES0i3xQC2uxXewsMMkvuBO_bimX-jZl6W3PngcuaAfvVJ8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eric/ Erfaan and his team did a wonderful job changing the water pipes in our whole house. The process was super smooth from start to finish. They were on time , finished the job before the time(1.5 days) they promised to finish (2 days). They were very respectful of our home, covered all the furniture /walls. Moved furniture and put it back . Cleaned the space . Super easy to communicate. I would highly recommend this company . The prices were unbeatable. Few of my friends are already working with him for his dates. I have gotten renovations in my home previously and this project was the first one which took the Stress out . It was stress free. Thank you for making us believe projects in the house can be successful without any stress if a team like yours makes this happen.Thank you Eric and his crew. I would give them 20 out of 10.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MK C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_0fONzn0YfnvOKuS_rK_WhaGo6cVTfZqEG6iZJwY1_nE_bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eric’s team provided excellent work for the repiping of my whole house CPVC with new PEX-A pipe. They were fast, professional and efficient. Within five hours, his team finish my house re-piping, re-patch all of the holes (three layers), replace my water heater tank, PRV, expansion tank and my kitchen sink disposal. His estimate is so competitive that makes me wonder how he could possibly be doing that. He has hard working team members with professionalism. He is the best plumber I ever met. I would definitely use Eric’s team for my future home improvement project. Thank you, Eric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rag Guru","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL4Tu8FN5PxeBXu0E2WHTFX_WeFUwrIN4byNdAcITXdEZL1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clean, fast, and professional from quote to finish. Eric explained the process during first walk thru, came on time on project day, 6 hrs and work complete without any mess. I’d recommend whole heartedly.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
