 for the health of the system moving forward.\nI'm thrilled with the new system and was thoroughly impressed with their service. I strongly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Stamper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFN9wn8TnXT3RsVzZzYRLOakiUvynT5OW52szQ4RI0EdE8VQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve used Green House Plumbing a few times now. The first time they were the third plumber I called and the final one because they were the only plumber who identified and fixed the problem. Now I don’t use anyone else. Stay with the best. I’ve also referred them to friends who have had the same experience. Competent. Reliable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jillian Willingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP9Kdl2N78bfNtzj2j4f-glSCZ51YCTjPsBhSzxGA_mt5unTkY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service! Fast and on time. Plumber was quick, cleaned up afterwards and best of all, solved my issue! Second time I’ve used them and would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzhaCugenlyAi44MxcSkLB0B7D6ogm4r-fU2cu9_XTHJj4dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a Costco gas stove delivery went bad—although Costco did reimburse me—Costco delivery was out 3x and still couldn’t hook up the range. I called Green House plumbing and Heating.  From the receptionist to the plumbers, I couldn’t be happier with the service!  They were on-time and hooked up my stove with no problems!  I will be calling them for any future work I need.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeansok Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdS6DGnh390ILPDvJ2V6CbFn9QduQ-9WOVEKIyyDytBOURFWgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My water tank started leaking, and Green House Plumbing and Heating was fantastic from start to finish. Their text support quickly walked me through shutting off the water and gas, answered my questions promptly, and scheduled a next-day appointment at my preferred time. The technician was professional, explained everything clearly, replaced the tank, and cleaned up afterward. Excellent service—highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuQ67q_R2BgnqpfEZkJtt7_I9cvYHF58WGim9gpWH3c7hG8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"GHP installers, Omeed \u0026 Andre, came in a timely manner and were very friendly and professional as they took out my old hot water tank and put in the new one. I’m very happy to have chosen this company for this much needed job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Ringgenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDoojlrqHtUgiDB2AmbpBRnjotdcqQ_xySwBvl-hm1FxEjAkUj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very fast service response same day!\nTechnician was excellent and very pleasant. He explained in detail the problem and how he was going to repair it. Office staff was so helpful and nice!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
