he entire project in one day. We are so impressed by the quality of work and professionalism that we will be recommending them to our friends and family. We are definitely going to use them again in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnZA6brpu5vAis0Ber-0Ba48oCWon5-3rWORJN0YBNSHI85pnS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shane and team at Professional Plumbing were outstanding in fixing my plugged sewer line! They communicated clearly and were very transparent about costs. They came out to scope and jet quickly to clear the line. Showed me the source of the problem was a root clog on camera and explained their process to address it. They located the clog point with distance estimate and dug out the section of clogged/broken pipe. They replaced the clogged section, jetted the remaining roots, then they showed me on camera the cleared line to the street and filled the hole to cleanup. Great communication, great service, amazing team, six stars, highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31acePfg3l_Q23TrRY3Flk9cYPhz8z1r2f1iKZRRL_fE4Rwf6bobCViaKPfS0lgku8bz6Y9vme5lnr2JG4BGZLR9Q27o7AC8X_O21Ea8TD5sM3I0r7eKvYZJDysh6UUFM1L5vw1UdxVsZw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fWmytTeMEJxgxBMD-IQQSFPo1kIyAghMGc42M34yBSbW4zWHPl1tv2iRVw0a2sFHaS6bpZZZbc6PpaWVZD5gsfwehORCykWeohZuddJK7LazzCRHW7XcLsrIWeOFkfOAN6qTYQTfPyO0=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-20"},{"Name":"Saba solomon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoWnU-YSBdY6G8JrY4Ob8c6cUmBGJYBclrhcceSWWBOt5SIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was the most outstanding customer service! I called Professional Plumbing LLC after learning that there was some sort of back up in our pipes causing water to come out of the tub drain when flushing the toilet. Shane answered all of my questions regarding pricing and what type of work he would be doing to fix the issue with m