ation, and real expertise. I would confidently recommend them to anyone who needs reliable plumbing help.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yxVLSUlbLnhKPn7bgHDz1ny-Kr-YZtmVISArg8mMPyBxBzq_Q0KKYJuK7VkrsnVs6zEpUv3ey3Q6hfh2PmEZL5o52ZOK_R2aX9KgDGXeEMHyWLAlRq_HCSNlSvq3GR1-9Kct_x8feZ3U=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3eOaM_PHu51fTT3f38j8dDDLv4l4dPqZPdWHm4Z6hfhoKvRLQl_nQO7rMGtdgnlT9_f-NDNyORXLsnb0Qo4eLZqaxdNMVTH0o3u218mkA9k6igGqybFqcP2BelX5hmYbSd9r0p2xKSRzRI=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Phong Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTlMIa8X7jw2lg1QUvs8H7MtV7n7QWvIgDH0V1AtqyUVnDoCiNLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Late in the day I spotted water leaking from under one of my toilets, not knowing yet that my store’s sewer line had backed up as well. It was the weekend, so I expected higher rates and started calling around. It was about 5 p.m. on Saturday when I tried PriceBusters, and to my surprise someone actually picked up. It was the owner, Zach.\n\nHe gave me a fair quote on what I thought would be a simple job, pulling the toilet, checking the line with a camera, and installing a new wax ring. I told him I’d call around. After hanging up, I reached out to three other plumbing companies. Not one company answered their phone. That alone told me a lot.\n\nZach said he could come out the next morning, so I called him back and asked if he’d meet me before we opened on Sunday to try to get the blockage cleared. He agreed without hesitation.\n\nSunday morning, Zach showed up on time and spent several hours trying everything he could. He didn’t rush. He looked at the issue from different angles even from the rooftop and he really made an effort to find a cheaper fix before landing on what ended up being the big solution, which was digging out the pipe and installing a clean-out so they could jet the blockage from outside the building. I appreciated that he didn’t jump straight to the expensive route.\n\nThe next morning his Calvin and Logan arrived early and had already dug a five-foot hole beside the building by the time I got there. Logan was fantastic. He had a great attitude, stayed polite, and worked hard without a single complaint. They were out there the entire day, digging and working in the rain well into the night. Watching them made me appreciate how tough this job really is. It’s messy, humbling, and honestly the kind of job most people want nothing to do with, but they handled it with pride.\n\nThey did such a solid job that I’ve already asked them to come back every six months to jet my French drains. If you’re looking for a plumbing company that actually answers the phone, shows up, and works as if your problem is their problem, call PriceBusters. Zach and his team earned every one of these five stars.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0CAsZZMqTD6WJqsXEiRGjgGfFuSFXYboLWRIMmVANvBBXgBeX07Tatl4VhVwvb18PpPzOrh0hyO-t2gBbl4sf9-CE2t_njmzjA6edP7ogNV-2TsldbAYJU26y3nEOFPKM7d5c5ZUaNiT4q=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-11"},{"Name":"Joey Reske","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2pF7flNmEfd4A5Yq6pQ2LboxyBx1tfe50y7OE8f1bp1mmLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Price Busters Plumbing. From the moment I called, their team was responsive, professional, and easy to work with. The plumber arrived on time, clearly explained the issue, and provided an upfront price before starting the work.\nThe repair was completed efficiently and everything was left clean and tidy afterward. It’s hard to find reliable and honest plumbing services these days, but Price Busters Plumbing definitely delivered. I would highly recommend them to anyone looking for quality work at a fair price!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kendra Huba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYY6Zs0JnaNkYzaHwhLCOCRMLDOT8x0814WM7JYPVgNvXMFG_y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were extremely happy with the service from Nick, Kento and the whole price busters team. They were extremely professional and went above and beyond. For our plumbing repair, they had to cut some of the drywall, they took great care to cut as little as possible and kept it intact for easy repair. Our house is from the 50’s and had a lot of previous diy. They did a fabulous job with the estimate and completion of the job. Always kept us updated as things progressed and were a pleasure to work with. Thank you Price Busters team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Molly Vernarecci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGZr8bJrg6A56j8xD0BCVGn93V1NcNyXYzXvTmHVjkKqsJ8n70=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish, Price Busters Plumbing made getting a new water heater installed completely seamless. Zack and Nick were fantastic — super friendly, professional, and diligent. They communicated when they were 45 minutes out, which made timing easy, and left the space spotless. After getting several other quotes that were 2-3x higher, it’s clear they offer incredible value without compromising quality. Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tX-aWMVIJXChkc68QJZibu75FUG11eW49pS-PwxMc3KAWQ6hhMz4W4Lyio8NGP_b6J4Nwgh8OBFSf6MvSbnQbk8MwkUBcZLnlfxtzpZjbr8TV9wMdv3bdltvfQ8N5vKLy-PuOaOkpKmg=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-4"},{"Name":"Wright wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM8i8qVnxv-05Ov1BIddCs9H5-qU8uzkKWDRjaE6Qzp6PkFAis=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kevin and Nick from Price Busters Plumbing are absolutely outstanding both in their technical skills and customer service. Our hot water heater went out and we are currently facing freezing temperatures, so that compound the problem. This project was a relatively large one because of the complex system we had prior. The team understood the importance of getting us up and running quickly, and although it was an anticipated that it would go into the following day, Kevin and Nick stayed late to complete the job and they did so with the highest level of courtesy and professionalism. If you are in the Edmonds or greater Snohomish County area, we highly recommend Price Busters Plumbing. They are the best at what they do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ada Goguen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7OW2uqftuQKjoaMNGKv9qUORbNP8oEucj1T_OEiRgnM8egw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another smooth experience with Price Busters. After a different plumbing company skipped their scheduled visit to repair our cracked pipe, I reached out to Price Busters instead. Nick and Vlad showed up right on time, were incredibly courteous, and clearly explained what needed to be done. About 45 minutes later, the pipe was fixed and everything was back to normal. Their communication and customer service throughout the entire process were genuinely appreciated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaimie Reavis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBt4-raegsTOVckV710JwYNZbcQZQHo2My3miufckOhmchg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Price Busters was really helpful helping us with a toilet clog. They clearly explained the potential actions that were needed to fix the clog and what the options would cost. Luckily they were able to fix our toilet quickly and cost-effectively. Everyone we interacted with on the phone and in person was great to work with!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
