Kvu2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tyler, Robert and Andrew helped get us back to being able to use our plumbing. Quick service and knowledgeable in the fine art of sewer jetting. They identified problems and offered option besides just the jetting of how I can fix it for good! Thanks for the awesome work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alicia Land","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTEb2tN4IV2s2MSvbQK0dlL4SZ2yds7S5XnwK_N8IEhg49Too=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today I called Action Jackson for a clogged sewer at my elderly parents house. I had one other company out there before Action and we found we needed a jetter \u0026 camera! I called Action which was referred to me by the other company. I was quoted a price for the job. Tyler and Jake were dispatched to the job! They both knew what they needed for the job to be complete. They brought their Jetter and was in contact with me the whole time from arriving on the job site, to during the job and after. Communication was top notch! Their skill on how to complete the job was fast \u0026 efficient. they both were knowledgeable and knew what they were talking about!  I would definitely call Action Jackson again the in the future! I even talked to the owner at the beginning of the job and he was honest \u0026 straightforward with me and made sure my family was taken care of! If I could give them more than 5* I definitely would! Cheers!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cole Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuvHkVwi-jRPOMc8ZkXFfVVYN3HP1RdDZQa_7xXFVcz1dFyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Action Jackson was extremely timely and very reasonably priced. They were onsite in about in hour from when I called them and got the job done quickly. I highly recommend them and will for sure be using them next time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"_ jkendle@uw.edu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg