e":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAElp4Q6uJJw5iiD4qMIxUyzjekSWFm6vY6IiMEsk_aa3iuGjdss4VVIwngX10fhOaZVcVZqu1p7iyB5YUYyXUMp2D2RAsUE5UJ21mGO-1G6abdf6LGYfpbVEdpemSsewneAgwCDWw=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFR1ObmZCEY0CITGnhGhsTS1dOu6JbzwEyycB80FC7vDM-MskFppTPqDLj2z_L7ssenhRnFnIUJ9Q3KENk9gtqawnVvR01rVSUUdn6jmDj4nZ8hVStdGahzY8BeTrQzTQAyEGc=w529-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"110710796466918685550","name":"Pine Rooter (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110710796466918685550"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Abhijeet Gijare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzunj95Ge-oTUWB_CwBLIBCxFafIVuRMrEKlokS601wcE_wUb_wQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, punctual and honest\nPine Rooter quoted me a price for replacing a toilet.\nThey arrived in time and completed the work with good quality and speed. They also offered to move the toilet to 2nd floor and haul away the old toilet for an additional  surcharge.\nWill definitely recommend 👌","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhG3wdj2-EL6Z_holUHT03UpfZy0NnGKzqoLVaD5zA1iemwAI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pouya was AWESOME!  We needed a few things installed in our new home. I posted a project for the work I needed and Pouya at Pine Rooter was quick to respond. He got the info and provided a quote which was very reasonable. On the day of the work he showed up right on time. While working he found an issue with one of the items. He then went to where I purchased it and got a new one. That is going above and beyond in my opinion.\n\nHe is very professional in his work and attention to details was even better. He did the work as promised and at the cost quoted.\n\nIf your looking for a great company this is your best choice. Highly recommended Pouya and Pine Rooter for any job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pooneh Babaei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIy06enpoPlwEzfwLrbQEsXhCT2dijoePA3eYq05Q24-W6evg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience with pine rooter . Pouya was very professional, fast, and clean. He was right on time for our appointment and the service and quality in the work were top notch. My sink was backing up in my kitchen, and he fixed my kitchen Sind and garbage disposal as well. This guy is the best at what he does, and I totally recommend him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adit Dalvi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIj7T1PPqVXcsgnM1kB3_KeWilxeD1bRmReHra6UXdMGLnzqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pouya did an amazing job unclogging our sinks and fixing our toilet. Some of the other plumbing services we contacted said that we would need to get our entire toilet replaced. But Pouya analyzed the problem, went to Home Depot for parts and fixed the toilet flush without needing major repairs or replacements. Very good work and value for money. We highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Bauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqmzRu5cg15YAgSAphnZZUwj6JPQPZGLAg4gDVFcAxiuM1tmML=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I reached out to Pine Rooter yesterday afternoon and Pouya was here at 9:00AM this morning.\n\nPouya explained what he thought the issue(s) were and when he left 40 minutes later, I had three drains running better than I'd ever seen them before. His work also comes with a 30 day warranty.\n\nHe was the only one of the five businesses that communicated transparent pricing up front and didn't solicit personal information until I was ready to move forward. His open and low pressure approach is what sold me, but his quick response time from start to finish was just the icing on the cake.\n\nThanks very much, Pouya. I wish I'd reached out to you sooner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5HFWAavlFk_essj2HX4MEnnSOT5p7ohVQE5HToARHHWQhs-HA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pouya was excellent. He had been with Roto Rooter for a number of years and now is hanging up his own shingle. I hired him for replacement of a kitchen faucet hose. He replaced the hose, but after it failed to work properly, he went to Home Depot to get a brand new faucet, came back and installed the faucet in a jiffy. Works like a charm and i am back to normal. His rate for the service was very fair considering the time (3 hours) and professionalism of the job. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chinar Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvaQQLfv-mgzg_ILVh7gCopc0CMYT5ejFXTyGLHThSr-t7gwt-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pouya provided a genuine and correct fix for the problem we were having for clogged washroom and flapper issue with another washroom. His price is very genuine. Thanks for resolving the issue for us.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samer Koutoubi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIK22jQItA4V6yjdVMXrbqCnPGkqpGj8pDsqhO9SA7N5LQmjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pouya did a wonderful job installing the new pipes and garbage disposal.  He was clean and went to Home Depot to purchase the needed parts and complete his job well.  I highly recommend him and will use him again for current and future jobs.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
