/ALV-UjWPtMPMi1sjcjuMU5p6TC9hdN5VCZ4Nne9kGY7p9OWXwxyU9HiP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Would give 💯 stars, if possible.  The ABV Team is an exceptional team who genuinely care about their clients. Sherylaine was quick to respond, professional, and very pleasant to work with.  Hristo is incredible and so easy to work with - he is highly knowledgeable, quick to identify plumbing issues, honest to tell us what was broken and not which made it evident that other bidders were scamming my Mom with over-the-top estimates.  Highly recommend Hristo and ABV Team to every homeowner who wants things done correctly, swiftly, and with a plumber's pride and integrity in their craftsmanship.  Thank you ABV Team for fixing my Mom's sink drain and washing machine connection valves - you're amazing and can't thank you enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPkh2NljgNsn3m91Sciud3cHibcJxtSjmKeakZoVDRJgGppQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ABV was quick to respond to my request \u0026 fit me into their schedule the next day as we had an active leak. The technician found \u0026 resolved the issue right away and tested the fix to ensure everything worked properly. I highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bianca Mendoza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK343vvD0ViQUo1KBh16qzMK4WDAhamQXdD6rhPFePLfAlt6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing! Hristo from ABV Plumbing came in, was very professional, let me explain both my issues and proceed to fix them so fast. They came out luckily within 24 hours too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corinne Clarke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCzJb-U-Idz7fndMXLzvvk9sW76tHdPbkxlEsRgF3hisaPrkL4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hristo, Sherylaine and another staff member were delightful to work with. Hristo did an excellent job and I am extremely satisfied with his workmanship. Sherylaine wrote an excellent report for the insurance claims adjuster.He repiped my entire house and replaced a hot water heater. He and his staff took out all of the stress.of this stressful situation. I highly recommend ABV Plumbing, a Very professional company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBMXKYfw-63NO9D-1osoP0XGY7NTlv5dXgQnf5yejcICIn7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I contacted ABV Plumbing about installing an automatic shutoff valve.  The woman I talked to on the phone said that they would need to come out and do an assessment, which would cost $99, and that would count towards the final cost.\nI was concerned that my particular plumbing geometry might make it difficult or even impossible to install --- and thus they would waste a trip and I would waste money --- so she agreed with my suggestion that I just text photos and data to the same phone number I had called on --- not looking for a guarantee, but at least some sense that “yes we can do this” before having them come out to assess.\nI did not get a reply.  So I followed up with another text asking when they might be able to reply?\nNo reply to that either.\nThey might do great work if actually engaged, but I would not work with a company that just blew me off like that.   It would be fine to simply say that they can’t or don’t want to take on my job, but leaving me hanging like that after agreeing to that approach?\nNo way, very inconsiderate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6gtQ3GhXMU4tGN45jGGeyVTsYc7JTPqRBuKLzvOyZpUylsYVV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edited:\n\nAs described below, there was an issue where the calls were not getting through/went to voicemail. It was frustrating until they resolved the issue. Then there was great communication. They were very apologetic and scheduled my service quickly. Nathan did an excellent job on our valves. Glad to see my experience better aligning with others here and that the issue was just a technical one!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKxY8SqX37vZpTN7gcz_uHNgdvGN-rtQOTJHqq6SUMv0TKt8We=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nathan was absolutely wonderful, communicative, and just a very efficient and smart worker! He came right on time, told me everything he needed, said what his plan was to fix our shower water temperature valve, and got the job so so effortlessly fast! I really enjoyed how great the experience was and how I felt safe leaving his expertise to keeping our house in great shape. Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mohan Manuru","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpBrVTekAVRApL5zP-INKHb0SAfnp_bd_lrymhU3NI2Rc6NSXB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hristo was prompt and very through on diagnosis the issue and able to fix it quickly. He went above and beyond and got the access panel to cover the dry wall hole. Highly recommend!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1dHb198W8sEM5CtPMoUt7dejOX5yVhnuYYAjyl1fZM_8o-p3qqz3kvgg1rjjKVpTf9VOSY_FAtIQMR75qOF5MJw5HsL_xKRa2EXV1qwmLEUTzKdhxZRxoZBlaPL_hBsVZad8XauA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qezHb1d7XIqs7VgWsy8CEm6uJtYe-xh1Y_tPPCBeq9hki6JWsQXk1e8sQyigO-qJufy1RcroR1bViNnFRRZqqbox3NRP6CyNiX_PbbHY9gr4FpUu3AOq3ikYlsSh2AjUaJYSD=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-3"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
