i","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIN4XAoy4WtQw6Nh_mt4Y5JUirLclckUYmteUqofdCj8L_i4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Goldstar Plumbing (Russel and Adam) did an excellent job installing our new 80‑gallon Rheem hybrid electric water heater. They handled everything smoothly, from the permit application to installation itself and coordinating the city inspection for code compliance. The price was fair, the work was professional, and they even hauled away and recycled our old water heater, which was a huge help.\nHighly recommend Goldstar Plumbing for anyone looking for quality service and peace of mind!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37Ziw31Qv-XN8_q70TpDFLP3LiFLB1V1wNFlpYK8LTA61a-r-0w3ScV900dcN1sh482jBNoeRjSJFAjEfLl6vmEFhcVWYXvQql5Ljgn1sIenSnDwexs76YSdmsY3iuNfS2dxIwL5syKf0j=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-30"},{"Name":"Kahren Tevosyan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLh9WBGbpOmJ6J0eq5J8ZBN9bnBhE7u3UtjUhVPvdelrgthw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam Mirson did an outstanding job on the plumbing rough-in for a new full bathroom addition in the basement at my home. From the start, he was thoughtful and thorough—he recommended the right equipment for the project (including a toilet with a macerating pump) and clearly explained the design choices and installation details. He answered every question patiently, was always available when I needed clarification, and accommodated all of my requests along the way.\n\nAdam also went above and beyond by helping me find a great general contractor for the non-plumbing work. He coordinated closely with the contractor throughout the project and helped ensure smooth communication across everyone involved, which made the process easy and efficient. His advice was consistently valuable and practical.\n\nThis wasn’t my first time working with Adam either—he previously installed a dual sump pump system in an exterior well to pump rainwater into the mainline, and it’s been working flawlessly.\n\nAdam is professional, knowledgeable, and clearly an expert at his craft. I highly recommend him and would happily hire him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sachin Umashankar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc9GNvyNYKhUbeSth46GS9egrC5angERXIgbsGpgH5hGMmtgtsmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam was great to work with. We had a LG heat pump that needed to replace an older tankless system- they were able to handle the installation with relative ease, and also incorporated any requests I had. He also helped educate me on a lot of the things he was using and working with so I got a better understanding of how everything fits together. Will definitely be hiring them for any further plumbing projects that come up","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKML9Yx6ARHydifWCSjwOEQRc65BLnSar6ffRrui6D3PgDO2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For any people looking for verification, here's their Washington credentials you can look up through LNI:\nWA UBI No.: 604 580 198\nLicense number: GOLDSPL757N2\n\nI called Adam (owner) for a water heater flush and to get an estimate on repair vs. replacement to tankless. Before he even scheduled a visit, he walked me through my situation over text and a call to help both of us decide if the trip was worth it. Didn't charge anything for this, which I appreciated.\n\nHe was professional in every way. If you're just looking to get a job done quickly, you might think the labor is expensive. For our purposes of properly taking care of our plumbing with thorough solutions and longevity of our home, I felt like I got a good deal. He walked me through his entire process and shared all the tips I'd need to handle maintenance after his visit. He was willing to meet me at every point, made sure we did things by the book, and gave us all the information we needed to make decisions as responsible homeowners.\n\nAs someone who has had to navigate the online process of researching businesses through a lot of bot-generated 5-star reviews, I'll admit I was nervous seeing this place at all 5.0. What helped me get comfortable was noticing how most reviews aren't templatized and are from profiles with multiple reviews. For me, Goldstar passed through all of my screening.\nIf you care about staying away from private equity undercutting local business and want to support local, I was happy to work with Adam and would consider him again for future work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andras Heczey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgsudFjRAwFyUnqT17BHHk17a5QAb75SgrqtvDSbX6dtjkSnk2pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional service.\nWe worked with the company on installing a new energy efficient hot water heater and pump. Adam was very helpful in explaining the process, was responsive to ad hoc questions during the installation and did an outstanding job.\nHighly recommend Goldstar Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS1qrK6uPWaZP8mzKJxb8eGVA_gUXcXB_lDD_tGTmNYty4iIaZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam expertly fixed both our leaking stop valve and the toilet that was also leaking. He was not only incredibly friendly but also very efficient in getting the job done quickly. I have complete trust in Adam to handle all our plumbing needs, and I would happily recommend him to my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"YY L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu1OSWleycycmSw4_NuxDbxCr0m4PtQzD9_eTJ2qHZLJJ4Vi4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam is so professional and coordinated,  my water tank was leaking on Christmas  Eve, I called him in the morning and he made some adjustments with his own schedule and replaced a new tank for me just in a couple of hours, he is detailed oriented and so patient and professional throughout the process. You won’t regret to use Goldstar Plumbing, they are the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Duval","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_u5gfZpt1-oIEiL2b7Zbi_wwVoBgjCvuPyl3n90HBfNj-WYE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service experience with Adam! Installed a new water heater that needed replacing -- on the weekend -- with no unexpected upcharges. Pricing was on par with the other independent shops, and less than the \"big guys\".","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
