he problem was almost certainly the Valve control board, so I bought one. Jake came and installed it in around 2 hours and the system now works as intended. The preparation and understanding made the interaction very pleasant and successful - and it was a new experience for me.  I strongly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tim Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzDelkkcmbjq7wnefM48RY1XDzqqK0FuWluvWNMGBTJEeMJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had Prima out to our house on 2 occasion's for some plumbing fixes and they have been great.  Timely, fair pricing, considerate employees, and quality work.  I would recommend them for any home plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andra Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ-b2RfAyKccDFZkhPWtUNGGeHc-QpiczsdImIWdpcnaJZYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Bell-McDonald Family had a great experience with Prima Plumbing. All the way from front office response to final touches of installation of a tankless water heater. It was a bit out of the ordinary as we needed modification for propane on a small houseboat, but Jake \u0026 Wayne did a fabulous job. Efficient, personable, flexible, and professional! Finished everything well before time estimate and so clean we hardly knew they had been there. Would recommend this company in a heartbeat for any plumbing needs! Cannot express how wonderful a hot shower was after months of cold water and overpriced and unresponsive plumbers who said they were available…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Perfect Circle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7cNMI6JTVvBDFTgiOJqYRTEchdbpSY5CzI7F8EHcI5ojpW98=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are now repeat customers of Prima Plumbing; they will be our go-to for future needs, and we recommend them to our friends. Their pricing is fair; the time-and-materials model allows for several little fiddly items being covered in the same service call. Pete is friendly and informative and a pleasure to work with, and Alexander in the office makes you feel like an old friend. Very glad we found this outfit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zeke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkXfxoUz7_SMXRhAXWKVZUhq331PybwZEe0_NPthRrLkbdBKE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic experience. Initially got evaluations from two other plumbing companies about low water pressure in our house, both of whom misdiagnosed the issue. One of them was Beacon, who tried to upsell us, suggesting we re-pipe our entire house. Prima was super helpful and experienced, clearly knew what they were doing, correctly diagnosed the issue, and completed the job for 1/10th the price that Beacon had suggested. STRONGLY RECOMMEND!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leanne Goulding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrqfABqgY0mQTiLXeg_hOo-ZzKpPVEA-0FEw51gD-OHkDDnCk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a landscape designer and project manager of 30 years, I have a select team of trades people that install my client’s landscapes.  I rely on them to be professional, knowledgeable, reliable, tidy, resourceful, work well with other contractors and clients and be fairly priced.  Prima Plumbing is my go to plumbing company.  They have installed gas lines for BBQs and fire tables/pits on several of my projects.  Jake and Wayne are efficient and a pleasure to work with, as in Greta, the owner and Alex, their in-house coordinator.  Over the past many years, I have worked with several plumbing companies and having finally found Prima, I will work with them again and again.  Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"stacey bennetts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjW0ygIFAmrX8LlIV4PtOVnb91IRPfBGAUGB-RQpSx3bT1VBU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Prima Plumbing does fantastic work. They are honest and on time and professional and always get the job done. They also advise us on a better way to fix things for the long term, how to save money with a better set up. Everyone that works there is fantastic!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Erikson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAOz39Yx59GeBCH5cCJWKAI0VMvh7PKGCRVCajXnAEjL10P62d=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We so highly recommend  Prima Plumbing. They have helped us out so many times. One by one, things are going in our old condo. Prima is always just a phone call away. They are professional, timely, and informative.They do not \"take you to the cleaners\" as the saying goes. Quality work. The tell you what to expect for service call rates in advance. LOVE PRIMA!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
