sible seating","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"taylan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5f9YaX3DBsq-7zhYkuIzoYsui4ONNh5rDYBr00pMca54zmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe did a fantastic job! We had a main sewer line clog, and he performed a camera inspection that revealed a broken section of pipe. He returned the next day with his team, replaced the damaged spot, and got everything back in service quickly. We highly recommend Moe and Knight Rooter!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0OM_e8jaW_J4kvwIRbwsi0zB8cCPVLEjL3qMvDFu_oXoYih8DYSGTUtXxE14T03pHWhoWvAJZjmPEAUtMfuNwUmTY4EXEhw5zsGGLJDzYeCuhhRsbmAgN-33FLgfxctuJDZ2wrGNlCYjrL=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-24"},{"Name":"Beatrice Silkie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJitULMzsZLh8SDC16FSDxWy2Xtif8yvDuGBnbvzXeR6rfKTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe assisted me with hydrojetting at my property in Seattle, and I would absolutely work with him again. He was prompt, highly responsive, and exceptionally courteous throughout the entire process.\n\nWhat stood out most was his knowledge and transparency. He took the time to thoroughly review the situation, clearly explain the available options, and thoughtfully discuss both immediate solutions and longer-term preventative strategies to minimize future plumbing issues.\n\nHe is clearly focused on customer service — communicative, professional, and solution-oriented. It’s rare to find someone who combines technical expertise with that level of care and transparency. Highly recommend. Will definitely do business with him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mahmoud Ghofrani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKANI_SYZ2gwf8AUCCf56gxcbE-ii1GTngG3ni0upwWndXWtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe is knowledgeable, honest, and professional. He took the time to show me the camera footage while diagnosing the issue and clearly walked me through the entire process so I could understand what was going on. I really appreciated his transparency and willingness to explain everything in detail.\n\nI highly recommend him. His services are not cheap, but you truly get high-quality work and peace of mind for what you pay.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"An Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9xLgoFUfWCWw-qdZJ3XtmqOAJc7nJFU2O7JY6ahkylCobsGsP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe was professional. He walked me through the problem, the solution, and what he would do. After the hydro jet, he showed me the videos of the amazing job. My sewer cleanout was inside the house, so he covered my carpet with blankets to keep my carpets clean when he brought the tools to the house. Very thoughtful.\nI called him at noon for the estimation, and he came that afternoon. He gave me a discount for doing the work on the same day. The price was very reasonable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZWmFNQfREtHW0W1kCIG3aXSDMgrphodPTOj-VEX9nHxJo_nU4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sewer backup problems are always the most stressful because they occur unexpectedly and need to be resolved quickly.\nThe company I used in the past went out of business.  So I frantically searched for someone local with great reviews and fortunately I called Knight Rooter. Moe answered my call quickly\nand after I explained the situation he immediately understood what was going on and was able to come out later that day.\nHe fixed the immediate problem with the kitchen sewer line. then he thankfully put a camera in my main sewer and found massive root problems.\nThe next morning he came back to the house with his son to hydrojet the roots.\nHe did not rush and explained everything in great detail.\nSome companies are flashy and just want your money. Moe is kind, respectful, skilled and trustworthy.\nHighly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allyn Family","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4G0G0BZCDQ6swplsyxRB2mhlCWqWBCghYwZCODZm-M8LVHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have a long (+250’) old 1910 sewer line in north Seattle going through 2 neighbors’ properties and it backed up on us. We had another company come out and they hydrojetted the line but did not get through to the end or solve the problem. After talking to some other companies about digging out to clear the line Moe came out and was able to take care of the issue with his hydrojet and expertise. Great experience and wish we had used him first!  Prompt, easy to deal with. Great experience. Highly recommend Moe and Knight Rooter.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jolin Fang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZ-r1JAE2TzvRXR2SsruXO6RkfKpEPK-sSwdQZM2XyBP-o8HY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe was super responsive and flexible with time. He helped with our sink drainage problem in no time and explained very thoroughly what was the issue, what we need to do next and what to watch out for. Super transparent, helpful and knowledgeable. I highly recommend his services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabriel Mititelu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXunDWxyL_maUWrAw2QbeiYMZsrO2T7Y6-DURft7nkDMyoRYhe2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moe was quick to respond to our request and was able to unclog the shower drain. On top of that he also offered advice on how to maintain it better. Very throughly handled the issue. He did such a good job that we immediately booked him for cleaning out our outside drains and jetting them. As well here he went above and beyond. Would totally recommend and I’ll definitely reach out in the future when needed.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
