aning.\n\nBased on these changes, my assessment of Southwest is that they are not ethical and can't be trusted on their assessment of required services and repairs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YZZG-VhbE6yrfTgxQmzoLL7y03JMoGB5AljU9szoCH5AUPC-Ijn4MaLvq5v3zfwg-r779Okdu55vrzmAQ618x_yx-xhbF1IA7NuPCqab91lAqw2UrG4iWt6f-kUu3mabuTQYhE1cZBGFC=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-28"},{"Name":"Ellen Eades","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJI-D1twtvcSAT3t9VbpdlWPi46_fBJFOiQ7MbLVTJgDGXW-0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dillon and Drew came out yesterday to install a heat pump because my furnace had a broken heat exchanger (shout out to Donnelle who diagnosed it). As with previous appointments with Southwest, they went above and beyond, working from 8:30 AM to 9:30 PM to get it all done. Drew explained all the new stuff and left things meticulously tidy. So glad to be working with you guys.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33bZSgEpeP9eJWO1OFiUeEHJL0x1QGVngdx8cTzopwdqPWAW7nhKK7Ga2Mb7_EZ3LfZJsgwPviPHaYSiXu1Xjw1FX_vI0QaM45uVE70skQylu_VZRM_qkD4lYSH7r863s0-HTU1QtGK3o=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Ra5VywNnLhUfe6Wuq8KwFxvzF5aFm46-8257vCydHUEJ4yG2nDli5xIfM3fteBG3xvm-vS361lFhDCZke_gkF45REi3i13ounU-49ve97JdEAGzb9kWzKJl0YjtUkCkjXCHLfoQTVDYg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1LQ6fD04bcw9dDNBE8zScJqDX5iZK-BKCbpWP96McHxtLIkEVDDD_8Hy5AXL74GWO4OpRAaRxb79X8jcTX4LHf_mm61V2ynH3P0nge-hsuYyQBmeSbFStaVrV1jkmsSP3y9vv-JPOrqlkj=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-27"},{"Name":"Jeff Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXD5VUn5k2e2UCJX87Atw3ME-KQ-9XOKKRAgmwuUXTwxtSvtKw5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a new furnace and heat pump installed. Everyone I interacted with at South West was super professional, knowledgeable and courteous. This includes the technician who diagnosed the problem with my old system(Mike) to Bert with sche