to immediately confirm a technician arrival time.\nPeyman was fantastic - he arrived promptly at 8 a.m., quickly diagnosed the issue, and walked us through repair options based on parts availability. He also inspected the other pipes in our home and provided helpful recommendations for future replacements. He did an excellent job and ensured everything was fully working before he left.\nThank you so much, Peyman! You were a lifesaver!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn Bird","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ_sgTgpgH15iz_aPJicRMeGUS0-mXRWunNyglqx2CRTD3-_SO9g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'd never called Roto-Rooter before, but when I had a stubborn clog in my main line and nobody else could fix it, I decided to give them a try. I'm very glad I did! Jesse came out and got my entire situation sorted in one visit, at a very reasonable price. He explained every step of the process, told me what to expect, and helped me understand how the whole system works and what was going wrong. He was competent and cool the whole way through, making sure the job got done right. I have a lot of respect for skilled workers like that. It wasn't an easy job, but he kept my mood up, and in the end everything was fixed. I am so happy to have running water again! You don't realize how much you need it until you have to go without.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"steven lowery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLJ-s5Z-nZ8FCoPGcIRR-2ONRoN2w1MQL-eNin0J7K-1rHDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lead tech Drew and his assistant Christian were a rock solid crew . Came in quick and performed effectively and efficiently. Great workmanship","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AhpgQQGvgV4uHK0rUOWAOEbwf0d6SAJQ6X1R4KN0h9jlmtIisAhrsQ_C_d1cfqAG5hrEw_KW4GWoSOjAaBSmUFlYNrVTKNXWweZdocD8nvY-1h8I6z3n-SDIYzb_y5-9oQ-g_J989ODPW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vYvx74