e basement yesterday , we called Roto Rooter at 7 am today and our tech Jesse tech #2101 showed up today at 10 am right on schedule. Jesse cleared our clog and showed us on camera the plumbing all the way to the street. You can really tell Jesse has been in the business for years! His experience and knowledge allowed him to explain everything so well. He also was able to provide tips and tricks to help us out in the future! He was respectful, funny, and very knowledgeable! Would totally call and request him by name! Thank you Jesse! Your a life saver!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Lindgren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQbB0kGH8Rpg8vu4YQdIqCICRoavHVpJZ_eEnfAbhOaS7jnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Jesse!! He was amazing! He went above and beyond expectations trouble shooting and solving the problem. He was professional, friendly and very thorough. He patiently explained everything  as he worked tirelessly until he resolved the issue.\nWe trust him completely with all plumbing needs and moving forward, he will always be our plumber! Call and ask for Jesse, you won’t be disappointed!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
