e loop on some key decisions along the way.\n\nI can’t recommend them enough for high quality work with extremely fair pricing, and I’m grateful to have found them when we really needed someone. They even provided some advice on another project we are working on as well which was quite appreciated. While I never want to have to call anyone for service, if we ever need to again they’ll be first on the list.\n(Note: the shoddy drywall repair was my work, not theirs)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn161ihxxG1rFsqMUtqRTYQLUGBJ8heL32kdyP-9iXnVh0D4aKjsWEvUiUyao1wmaJOkpz465RrtFKKLdzXHZWO8iO56fsT_pPz5dSKnAMJimtEKbgEYz60GEBrFcWfxpMBxpYDs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn298M6FX_-bf7CW9QV_DKK2TBn-ZvIoImhSU2M-uem5908FlFu-C3Yt8RGVh2_6zti0fq6I8an9laM407Rq4WSBJUUXhhSKQ8PHMMxaA7dvMSh3R3HVTqWJs_aibL4bjz8z_7fGAA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RMF_on7QMIUWQZb9Ggkw6iNtjxUWi3xg0SGjRwTQTbOyPNgwcwqlasJMqZ88ZdX3YwFYwTWycejc3-9GHc20fdrG5wa5OTr4noDQ6UaH8ILevAHd0voQR6izncTtO09rUb8E=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-7"},{"Name":"geneen courtney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0Mu5FADcPAletc21TcDRWibDeGN6bWV7o-l5QaG2qvXNB5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Platinum Choice Plumbing has made stressful situations a breeze. We got a very reasonable estimate and they were able to get to work shortly after. The work was clean and done in no time. The team was respectful of our home and left the area in better shape than when they came in. We will definitely call Platinum Choice again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1i23bsAgl0OaL2xViwwiYuSn0ektV4SXRrE4C-6uxz_IwuZcyaAzws6-jy7Qb46dQx2WtqZRx3Hl_jdQVTZ9HHrEQApKzmelVd82tVmuRKh6ZkdSqz-RolijLCzJbn-t7zgQotDg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1UcU-rcpGWyE_QPz-KTeLgKI5Zdb0ildtTJE2SyIiWwPrtjWOov6EdWBDCnbrG3hB6YRSZEDDSnVm5_AdfQsiz69LGobGlJNKF0RP-mtAoGmXrUVbC90wP6A6Pv0mRHy9sN-XT=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-15"}