d their suggestion of rerouting through a wall to remove the pipe previously sticking out the back of the garage is going to both look stunning, but also give us space back.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fYf2oS3lmHle5yYd29-0hhh4g-2MPdNS16CK0VDgJqzioppdL-yd-4_uhgLVdsusitfLEkuFESsCn4F7y6CHeHu_NwZW_NfgPWHXfRAyy6KzM8MDXuGTxpE78sb7I_y9JPYxj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2jlXIu57Ah2tBsE6jzdM79eqxA590efmgQ5iRPdJVWfduN7l6fITaLxm0Nyq5Ejhlqw1UllvrhrgPTH5_kwwz2JwgQa3YFIAYQXSGtq7LbGZcf9utldQYDvG5hDKct8ieMbeQgJg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1IZ6-4_r6wcBZeABir5wXoHkaETDXt1vik2YAUjLE_BMfIg1hr5Zm48kGrpvygxVBoxVHq16r1ATx_4pWDf3nsfpGGllpZoOuEY8ca6LqyVZTvyQbVcV1JFNEKkXEM8xsbCfBl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3lYdVXqx_pEb5i02uwBCkvdk5ct9KKe-3iAk2U5ReTIQeWU9oekKn321sOdxMwjrShxZ7LhOPSSuhIvw6MoK4AEffd4PtVGHGKbD16178CC3xXJhbfAxsdJ8poJODhnJdf1LiEFA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0URRq_AbPRw_IwFFrs9FCB0DsrKybrSH69xMObRlHCNLQKyS1hJgX6oncc58SSIvXHrRUz6fe4-lgWrL9vBqCg7982o2PNiVIVJyQLNCw2lRZDEuUmqR5WhlEdS4JjduvqvO4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2mDUxvr1UBhzcpeKJg7qA_nabJeSKVJhMZUR3Z41W7NT6SdUFVttvYc3h6WKeJ9k-ArHHrwYUrzFiOf9NGJ414RvUfrSMERTAoV9ylrAUrhvtqbIqloRN8pV3SKDeh8Ll849apWQ=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Julianne Aultman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxsoMrN50Lr8-U5yEj_3OW-QPmtU-mgmmo0vG2kLLBSEydUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We purchased a sink and faucet and needed someone to install this for us. Looking at reviews, we decided to call  Platinum Choice Plumbing. They came to the house, and were  very polite and friendly. They gave us a reasonable estimate, so we decided to go with them. The day of installation, they came to the house with blanket and tools in hand. They laid the blanket down, and got to work. They noticed that the drain pipe needed to be lowered, so they informed us of what was needed. They took their time and made sure that everything was working and most importantly leak free. I’d highly recommend Platinum Choice Plumbing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20Hs-yEFuuoEjyvLzzsKi0i0mkHX7jAmuMC_xm7nd85c8arI0JvlkKA9SHaZ2CDgp3tsc1GlWQdr-bUUHCFdIW3M4GWBIl8GKRgs9tHFTOfak-8lGWqtggvqP6vZDuDvx2yvOu=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Tri H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnAipPYdjAhiwNQ1DgQvjcKOxHnXqT6uye5tXg_UGDhjdsBApS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing quality! Great Pricing! Johnny and Baruche were great and helpful when I explained my insane water bill. They came up with a better solution than the other plumbing companies I contacted and got the job done very quick! They also helped me with a water leak adjustment with my city! Couldn’t have asked for better service, I would recommend them for all plumbing needs!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zaXqyyTrs2NdMFX3Lw3wbQ_qwrO-Z0LoRUakGoFb9E2a1bh37GTum-eLfDCCqI3MGbLPvU5UVrz9EqepDz6S5LEB-1_TJXHWvP9wBpcMRtsdd6sC1vk9Yog75jqCypHegdHY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3hl8sYTRcnDDy5QjraoP0MfN9sKQKp-JeMf-j5SCBlULbf3nCc0SfGfMPtPXnNglaB3sfzZ7fdGy0CH4hHnwwU8HdRB0Hxpq1QBV_q5B0HJxVOlsjZs6VJkgfGbcRmjkPllxb7Yw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QUx5piULOLHXPl3qm0S28my5jTB1mjItpDIp39M_v6dDK-qIK2yJ6WE4pjbZ4aMcb4nXffVoOMSYDjdRnVu5OqDMV3uQPXqjWpKNcseZrSjga_NCjFOoz5q3L8U9q4qFMWxVc=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Aron White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrCIorSlC0_otgI1Yzbo-YSUu88XZMv6Rj9fK_mkdu05W4whf4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jonathan and Platinum Choice did a great job!  I've hired them several times previously and this time I needed them to install a new waterline between the street meter and house. Jonathan came out and provided an estimate and completed the work in a timely manner, including installation of a water shutoff valve, pressure regulator, and servicing the existing water heater tank. Jonathan and his team do excellent work. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natalie Debray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhkJimiindFYDFfknl1jtkGOcp60RcYoXwd2G5Gmb4N5BZog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had to replace a water heater and were referred to Platinum Choice Plumbing. We will use them for every plumbing need going forward. From their prompt response and professional service we could not be happier. We opted to upgrade to a tankless system and Jonathan walked us through the process explaining the pros and the cons. I trusted him completely and felt that he truly had our best interests in mind. It was more involved than a standard replacement and Jonathan and his team worked all day to get it done. The results are top notch. They are also just incredibly nice people too. We are fans!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
