ervice, the best technician, and zero hassle. Highly recommend Danika Plumbing to anyone looking for fast, reliable, and exceptional service!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15Y5t8LWvzym9xKEg72eIi7O_Qc7dVTWnq5WFCZG1lWS_bgaFM_zqcdLdWJi6TkGori8QU_H3s19EeGIGr3YluwwYgJgX93NyEVx2a4B-O_JP-IJbiaOe2XZFUuNvzqJRnldg5C-EJFfzj=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-29"},{"Name":"Eliu Lopez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJm3qdIvMAG59Xcnljx4yYMBkxzATUsngtkJNBHOIFiUNxzAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had Travis and Nick from Danika Plumbing come out to my home, and the experience was honestly like being at Disneyland — smooth, enjoyable, and exceeded expectations! They capped the gas line behind my stove and handled the angle stops in the bathrooms and kitchen with absolute precision.\n\nBoth of them were prompt, professional, and extremely knowledgeable. They explained everything clearly, worked efficiently, and left me with total peace of mind. It’s rare to have tradespeople who make the process feel stress-free, but Travis and Nick did exactly that.\n\nIf you want top-notch plumbing service that makes your day a whole lot brighter, I highly recommend Danika Plumbing — especially Travis and Nick.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Rtj6ueF8QkPrK5wqECDh4yLt17WE4lA3iow2GomvISZ_xyWBs_la4p3mKQRflKt4xrkTM6bh1KqTfDl_NvjHyTcDnOmOdnnaVd5hriLEGXapFd7ZlX9ygDywHG-mV9k_0P4baTLoURaju=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1IbW4BySAfRQ7C4Hfre5sBttKNCkR0bdssR9HwAo9yTDEB-EYpAt8YloCEh--8M09YlQGcDaUybiBVPGAIFclrQOSahZeOkfmDcUlW4OwWEfvBhJE0wAsIlCNJf_in6qJri-4FWHZOTl8e=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3PnWeQWO30c8dmht5r_m82Q6B5exQLV1IE1KD0Sl4avts78_iICvFaEHAr-6ivPHR7xAzVZ-go6y93rl3cwTQDvLObIuehrCsXHDATW0HmWbyV4k2ducG-fDwjV7jI3sxUrQGbjXL5c4Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13h_ojUaYcgCqt-yUl4cOR8we6cUijjtAZLSCzbAvnJhts3Pg74Jnc8aUMTCXykBp4Y3UabtKcwS-N43