I had already hired two other drain companies to investigate the issue. Both told me it was a pipe blockage, and one of them even proposed a very expensive repair plan that completely missed the real problem.\n\nTravis took the time to carefully investigate and correctly identified the real cause — a stuck ejector pump. On the first day, when there wasn’t enough cleared space for him to access the pump, he was very understanding and willing to wait and reschedule for the next day so the tenant could move things and allow proper access. That flexibility and patience meant a lot.\n\nWhen he returned, he efficiently completed the work and resolved the issue. Travis is very knowledgeable, professional, and easy to work with. He was also willing to coordinate with tenants, which helped make a stressful situation much smoother. On top of that, he is friendly, helpful, and genuinely cares about solving the problem the right way — not pushing unnecessary or expensive fixes.\n\nI highly recommend Travis to anyone looking for an honest, skilled plumber who truly knows what he’s doing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0kWBzPv6ZeoU0lvvzHIMgakgOHUljSBk-1fPlpNija1kRHRYi25qAvAQUywUdJkX9XF2mH6HmCm3pDe_3ThqgT8o3lr5PU2MbGgTjffGEk4qbiFiK6FZf1r8XVfbsO3x_PjOHmkzZ-jixl=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-31"},{"Name":"Jeff Carl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiIucUXG2NMVWxCgTjIioRyqlw4RuUg5DICK8KzutHxqOs2Ek78w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Travis is the man!  He has helped me with 2 homes and 1 business now and has always taken great care of us. Highly recommend Danika Plumbing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1b5p5YSD_jM2SGqgBx-VZhWpCibk3A3YvPC4PsQp-QrpzAfTOG6UIZwVoGH9GnfrMR4kNGGR3GcPU0BaruqdqawTy2CeTT2e-fiJpZVbDDEj_lHvQE6wZZhjk7dlZ2e39VDrL--7bqCI-T=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-10"},{"Name":"Robert Chamberlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgSEfoRkvzrse-XH8VfUQar4ZtSvWS-Fl0Y9q03Os_-mAvH--o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needed two gas water heaters replaced due to age.  I compared Plumbing Co’s.  Read a huge number of positive Danika reviews so we called them.  Bass came next day and showed us how both tanks were leaking (rust was visible).  He also used a pressure gage and showed us that city water pressure is a bit high in our area and we need a Pressure Control Valve PCV on the input water line.  The high pressure likely contributed to the tank failure.  (I have verified that building codes now require a PCV.)  Bass recommended new high quality tanks from a Supply Shop.  I have verified that most product manufacturers (for many various products) make an inferior product with the same name for Big Box Stores at a lower price.  That’s OK if you can tolerate lower quality, shorter product life and a shorter warranty period.  Bass and Nick installed two new high quality Water Heaters with 10 yr warranty the next day.  Bass and Nick are amazing people.  They are smart, very knowledgable, highly capable, hard working and efficient.  And they have a clear understanding of the value of a good customer relationship.  We are absolutely delighted with our Danika experience and would request these people by name if we have any future plumbing issues.  Many thanks to Danika.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
