out":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Alex Harms","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGLH5cuUZ8TjSxMH3sxQbcu-F5-lSW0bQaIZhW2mM0SYl_FGyL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Five-Star Review for Gene Johnson Plumbing\n\nI cannot say enough good things about Mike K. Mike K spent hours here working extremely hard and never once gave up. He was literally sweating and did everything in his power to resolve a very difficult toilet clog. I have honestly never met a more honest, hardworking plumber than Mike K.\n\nWhat stood out most was that he was determined to get the job taken care of today for Mike K — it was about doing the right thing. He thoroughly explained all the options, called his supervisors when he had questions, and approached everything with professionalism, integrity, and care. Mike K truly went above and beyond.\n\nBecause of Mike K’s incredible service, I will be using Gene Johnson Plumbing for the rest of my life. I will also be referring Gene Johnson to all of my friends, family, and colleagues without hesitation. This level of service is rare.\n\nMike K is not only an outstanding plumber, but a genuinely great person and an absolute asset to whatever team he is working on. He is the kind of professional you call and immediately know you are in good hands.\n\nThank you so much, Mike K, and thank you Gene Johnson Plumbing for employing such an exceptional individual. I cannot recommend you highly enough.\n\n⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0U_c3HSNcS0F9EEChEpHmT2U76SpD9MY1nrJ58_g1c9aX-YvrMDy-OVx3AOsaYe-HLPyEcsUQT