usercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLF-7gz_is-eQMp_OrxXWRJr2yN5zZmMPJ3-a1i2FgFIoD1kw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an outdoor water leak from a pipe that needed replacing, and several companies made proposals. The best prices were Jafco and another company and decided on Jafco because of the A+ BBB rating and positive reviews.  We experienced them as an on-time and highly professional operation. When the installation completed, they arranged for an inspection from Seattle Public Utilities which passed.  When I called Seattle Public Utilities to ask for water credits, the customer service person was pleasantly surprised at how easily she was able to pull up the inspection result, exclaiming that this company did it correctly for a change (compared to other companies).  All in all, our experience with them was first-class and they lived up to their stellar reputation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa O.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz6NxX-qU36ZI0LwHtfZu3aF-_v2IgncyypKaBmPyXhKRAi7mk9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Garret and Abe were awesome to work with. They installed a new sump pump in a tricky location and repaired the waste lines from our kitchen sink. We have used and Jafco on several occasions in the past, and would absolutely do so again. Great communication. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ravi Shankar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUi3dpJd3-UbkkSg2sA9jaCdK1viFJzbzmyYN-rCZcFsNTkwAhr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with Garrett and Abrahim! We called about a leaky outdoor faucet, and they were able to come out within 24 hours. They were friendly, efficient, and got everything fixed quickly. Really appreciate their professionalism and fast service. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAOxWAPRvv-mdg9HYL1G42empXSZjT-IJC_Ju0gU5eDCJa_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Garrett and James did a great job replacing my faucet. Not only were they quick with the install, but they were also very professional and friendly.  I really appreciated how they were mindful of always putting on their shoe covers when coming into the house. I’m really big on customer service and notice when the service is great. They were attentive, responsive, and very communicative. This is my third time using Jafco services in a 5 year period— from a sewer line repair to faucet replacement. Each experience was great—and why I keep going back when I need plumbing work done. Thanks, everyone! I’m really happy with my new faucet!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LCemAa6ZqkdmoszBuaaoJRfLPm29GtWx9odODfP8EmqxkI-ift1kEj3rLUHKDJ-8ORkKcbIYlVWueG0Ed-DJtDaawuEDmyqrNJAvWGc26_jlQyo4UFor9oY8RkeYf_2uJUUoOAg=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Joe Sherman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP4d4PtbITeS34kq3nmVmYou3zq53xNP8zY7izsqqrBSIZf-Oqjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Jafco with a clogged bathtub drain after getting frustrated with my regular plumber's lack of response. They arranged a visit the same day and told me the time of arrival within 2 hours. Miguel came and answered all my questions calmly and patiently. He not only unclogged the drain, but helped repair some of the hardware on the fixtures. The price was very reasonable. I would recommend Miguel and Jafco to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Devon Little","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo-berwRC5EAPf-yoj89pImX_-uLdwuxOyxJ0EZ_DvyG-ZEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Josh and his team at Jafco were extremely responsive, knowledgeable, and collaborative. We had a complex situation involving a downspout, broken sewer line, and massive sinkhole. They gave us astute assessments that made sense, provided different options that would get to the root of the issue while minding our budget, and never pressured us into any decision. They also put things back together so that our yard is in better shape than it was before the issue began. We recommend Jafco!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Balls Fattness","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5aaljPnGJKX7cC1CdOM2rinuOhoTBiajQmESFoSWHnMzhDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Garret is an absolute unit! I had a major issue with flooding in my garage so Garret and his little buddy  showed up right away when I needed him most to handle my pipes. Great company, reasonably priced and punctual! Cant recommend them enough. He saved my marriage!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amish Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRD1yQoij45ISnefYORHH4srADEafZHVsgGx3QBjFuYtKGHON1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Starting from giving the quote to executing the project went really smooth.  Josh kept me abreast of all the updates whether it was getting the permits approved or talking to the engineering team at Alderwood water.  The work was perfect. They cleaned up and restored the area so nicely that I was impressed.  Ian / Miguel and Luis did a great job at digging to restoring thing back to like they were without cutting any corners.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-NTwmHETbca7MhyFh4t9vbLjs7_4Y8t9Lcdht1a4MuUZkYcEdqOs4Bd3hJXExXp4fqePJ9swjq36U7UfT40gZ9ftj2RuzYfZzbaMVHrXoCf87FeGFg9GaysybZEty2HO-w9Y=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0EDX1C_GQ_M7Y0awgY7SkYNfaX0pUOCXGOxRtrpcgv5AurGgvNbpT-ShZYjo1cyqTMGBnNGEpGENfPAPaGf5W64lk83ZF2hfitD0dha1y2Dbl1luOz0muHRR1PqShnxkND2odHxg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3mfhj3hfvtwjivApW213ppKehxx7_JwHSBLm8lT4bOHWIr59W9LGGnO1h_FT7RgzvZZPsm9XjHc7J8jlR3cU2nr8ruUa-SoXKw43DXEOuagj4Nn08rmWKc8gl65PGaVFAQriei=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qgY6dfH6X3jUwFsh3FgD4gl