d the issue and repaired it. I’m planning on hiring him for other plumbing jobs in the future. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shraddhaa parkar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlGwGi2ud3BdC1JqPT5uvGg_n3-XbSHJUWmbPrwhEmwEcn1Z-R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fred was quick with diagnosing the issue and fixing it. He completed the work within a few hours and was available to help. Our pipe needed replacing and junk removal, we were unable to use our dishwasher and guest bathroom. Fred came the next day and everything worked perfectly fine after he completed the job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daisy Dukerson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhHGLipSYTGqnGuU-_z3onzDoguOjPZTQRKReGD48cJhrASQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fred did a great job replacing a noisy pressure valve and cleaning out a shower drain.  He is an awesome plumber, very honest and gets the job done quickly.  Highly recommend him!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKX08yJ2KQNvzIflTpg08VWJrb_ua9FZ0U734sLebLlIJTBHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fred does a great job at reasonable prices. We had a new water heater installed, unfortunately it was bad. He replaced it the next day! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nisar Ahmad Nishat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUODlZvrrdL0kf8DrlnyczgNoHdkOU7IYqzYKm0HvcveF5wpPuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a plumbing issue that needed quick attention, and I’m really glad I called them. They arrived on time, diagnosed the problem fast, and did clean, high-quality work. Pricing was fair and transparent, and they left the area spotless. I’ll definitely use them again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reza Safari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6Vy1NMoIXy2GDhqEhyuzAdnQKVvnPMCRotJglFHwn88fE0zJk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fred from FT Plumbing is truly exceptional! From the very beginning, he impressed me with his professionalism and honesty. He took the time to give me a thoughtful and helpful suggestion over the phone, which already showed how much he cares about his customers and not just the job. He clearly explained my options, and handled everything efficiently and with great attention to detail. Fred is knowledgeable, reliable, and truly goes above and beyond. Thank you, Fred, for the outstanding service and support!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
