Paris Plumbing were amazing. Their pricing is the fairest and customer oriented in the local area hands down, and the professional and fast service with great communication is hard to find these days. When the Hot water manufacturer played hard ball, they fought for us and got the solution figured out.  Highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stevie Thrasher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsAN2JNUGO_Bd8D4TJhiqUoadseOnm4mZCHC_nwTi__huwn2yo7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Farris was AMAZING!!! Give that man a raise. Very kind, polite and knowledgeable. Completed the fix so quickly, efficiently and went over everything with us and taught us so much about plumbing! We will definitely be using Paris plumbing again and requesting Farris.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaleb Matthies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRGd4A3bMGdgRPi42BmBBMbVabh_cO9WGAtkA-OoeUedyaiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Farris was very kind and professional took care of a corroded P trap for us and made sure to address all of our plumbing needs. We will definitely be using Paris plumbing if needed in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl Keyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzRa8XG_dfmaIgWmCONYF8a5hYO0tMgRX3MX6OpFt7hmNyEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are trying to get your plumbing project a permit from the county and finished very professionally and in fast order, I highly recommend Paris Plumbing!! Tyler Rennell is the owner and a wonderful person to work with. He's very knowledgeable on plumbing and works frequently with many different counties.  We will certainly be calling on Tyler and Paris Plumbing for all our future plumbing needs.  The Wheeler Family","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Eikel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjWeLkFiwKCnXOeKSbi6AaT3uGgLx8lHJ_pfNNU6Axanhifg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just completed a very complex whole home repipe with the Paris team, and I can’t say enough great things.  (Older copper piping that wasn’t installed correctly leading to micro leaks.)\n\nThis was likely one of their most challenging repipes, a four story home with a very complicated recirculating hot water system and boiler heat.  The team took excellent care of my home, were upfront and easy to work with, provided a fair price (and stuck to it despite a few surprises along the way), and did a fantastic job.  The project included extensive demolition and restoration of drywall (with level five finishes).\n\nTyler (the owner/manager) personally checked in on the job every few days and kept me informed.   These are true professionals that provide terrific service, stick to their word, and can be trusted in your home.   The Paris team worked in my home for several weeks unattended, and treated my home as if it were theirs.\n\nThe Paris team took on the role of a turnkey repipe,\ncoordinating with a general contractor to restore my home in better condition than when we started!  This included packing and preserving my furniture and belongings, and ensuring no damage to anything inside the home.   This project scope included three kitchens, four bathrooms, a laundry suite, and a commercial boiler.  Definitely not something to be entrusted to anyone less than a very experienced professional.\n\nThe majority of plumbers I found were unable to provide this level of customized service given the circumstances of my home.\n\n100% Customer for Life!   If you need an honest quality plumber in Seattle, this IS the number to call.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3qK5OyL07SRkXQFybFCvvw2Gt8QfP6IBl5c2SR2GLVbXYVPAcjiLFeTw6csakJQWl3006_mkjQwRTvkW584PbxJqsb56jiZZoAL6rtfuqvBpkO0G0in_X6vOZmq8FTymigcsgJ=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-27"},{"Name":"Dayne Remlinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFGxDmG8YrFs6UKhjaWOpG9qxp5WMVbFFcXvaEJ-ofjBics3Vu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needed some plumbing work at my home and a new water heater and came across Paris Plumbing and gave Tyler a call and they came out and got it taken care of right away. Great company and very easy to work with.\n\nI highly recommend them for any of your plumbing needs, Great price and very professional team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stewart Moore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3SmfwSooKvzq604CWClUeEj35ruGpPSjTsC1ZKdQIrhPFUOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently used Paris Plumbing at the referral of a trusted friend. We had noticed that our basement ceiling was filling with water and soon saw that something was leaking in the walls. We contacted Paris Plumbing and put me on a waitlist for cancellations as they were full at the moment. The next day, I was pleased to hear them call and say they could have somebody out that day since somebody had canceled. They were able to come out and quickly diagnose the problem and referred us to a drying company since the water damage was pretty extensive by that point. The next day the dryers came in and within a few days everything was dry and the leak was fixed. They were also able to talk through some insurance issues with us and gave us clear options to choose from. Would definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
