6pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://book.servicetitan.com/od5rihw9bdhye6u274eblocn?rwg_token=AFd1xnE1ezcSsSGnxo1OAZrgunygM6-ppOwNk6GsB0Zrm6oBg-2O4cCMJoQUd6SOH34sgEXzXE1_oAG2lmaW8V89sa3SpS1KKirkilqwRlFxVgfMpS8yiKk%3D","source":"servicetitan.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"113329799077967970361","name":"Plumbing Experts NW (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113329799077967970361"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Silver Lake","street":"3508 105th Pl SE","city":"Everett","postal_code":"98208","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Lisa Murano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITRx2eYbYLNe8rkRCd2F6ws9XJwxQGyU5aZbJNHpc5EpiqfUs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"An employee of Plumbing Expert NW, TJ Johnson, made a racist remarks on social media. This was very concerning and reflects poorly on the company’s image. I hope management takes this seriously.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brianna Bettenhausen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHlcg06BayBNbZGg_ogGcuNvsz73zbI45YceM8XRoDwlExiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Overall fantastic experience! I had Darius come out and fix my leaking outdoor faucet. Very professional and kind and got the job done quick! I was given a time estimate of 2:00- 6:00 and they came at 3:30 so very speedy.\n\nI will definitely call them for future plumbing issues in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rose Maras","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXV0jzfr7AqnqbR8rctXn9OoJoL6rbOOGT2dgFyyh09KFuKFCTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company is the best. I needed a plumber to scope a sewer line in the house we were buying and they came and were not able to scope the full pipe because the way the clean out was set up. They didn’t charge me even though they took time out of their day to do it. I will for sure be using them for any future plumbing work we may need. 👍🏻 [ we also have used them now to install a bathtub and they did a great job and price was reasonable!]","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shameless Rob","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvUomfYdma0w4InFkQ8Dbw_jRJWkfT8fSO8v5oja2u2LFnqHou=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's so difficult finding a plumber that is fair in pricing, personable and who does quality work. Robert at Plumbing Masters NW exhibited all these qualities. He also appreciated my Veteran status Military Service, and Law Enforcement service, and personally thanked me for the sacrifices involved in public service. His pricing was incredibly reasonable, considering I obtained multiple written estimates from other plumbers. He was on time, easy to contact, returned all my calls promptly, and the quality of work was excellent. The work done was a large job. We put in a new kitchen in an above ground basement. We had to cut concrete to tie into the sewer for the clothes washer drain. We had to put in new plumbing for the sink, drains, dishwasher as well. All the work was inspected by the City, and passed with no issues. He also replaced the regulator shut off valve to return proper water pressure to entire house. Robert was a pleasure to work with, and I will use his services for all future work! I highly recommend their plumbing services. Thanks again Robert and Plumbing Masters NW!\nRespectfully,\nRob (Mukilteo)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roy Jensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKewWQCHXJD2I31yeTsx-Bl37wydXqA7JVC6Zosay7Ytfj_lA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently retired and decided to remodel our master bath.  Having over thirty years of construction management experience I decided to manage the work and hire the specialty subcontractors to some of the work, and that included plumbing.  Plumbing Masters NW gave me a fair market price for the work. They arrived on the scheduled date, and worked hard until the work was completed.  It took two plumbers several hours to complete the work.  They were very professional and polite.  Upon completion they reviewed the work several times to ensure there would be no call-backs.  I was totally satisfied and would highly recommend them.\n\nRoy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Glenda0220","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6UQkw7m6AY8O5jY5Eoljzcb0HSCwnqtPvgovZ583Rr-h2SA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Plumbing Experts Plumbing was so quick to respond to my plumbing problem from making the appointment (just the calm, respectful tone from the receptionist put me at ease) to their professional yet nice demeanor to fix my toilets was a most pleasant interaction I’ve had with any service company! Their pricing was the most reasonable quotes I had investigated. Adam and his helper were great! I will definitely use their service again if I should ever need them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJe8FKAVC-X_auPgO7GTcYa9uyOMtyPdbLitp6JHLjDSFszzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very impressed!  Nordstrom like customer service.  Robert from Plumbing Experts NW was amazing.  The company was great with communication, prompt on time, and did an overall great job.  I had an extremely clogged bathroom tub drain, and Robert took care of it, he even repaired another problem that I didn't even know I had with the faucet.  Thank you so much for your excellent customer service, and I highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"minimoto san","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7SHaQaC8TMWZ_FDECwPBR-hakQDfXntJnII4NzUx9KsQgwN9xfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely so helpful. I had some water leaking which led to hallway and it was going to get much worse, and here I did some extensive research which to trust and who to use for plumbing. As I was reading reviews, plumbing NW has some great reviews and I wasn’t wrong. They found me same day appointment since mine was urgent, Saturday. Came and inspected and right Away started drying and installed dehumidifier. Following the next day we got connected to different water damage guys and all of these went so smooth. I’m still in the middle of fixing it but So far the experience is amazing and they are very straight forward. Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
