298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"112394235091869526716","name":"H2FLOW PLUMBING (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112394235091869526716"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKflicdVoI_rzcNvlhXu6qFTmun43f-Ej9qPg3OPeuKoh-y_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Initially, we had hired a different plumber who unfortunately kept canceling and rescheduling us over a span of four weeks. When they finally showed up, they told us what we needed was impossible and literally walked off the job.\n\nIn a bit of desperation, we called Hassan. He answered right away and was at our house the very next morning. From the start, Hassan had a can-do attitude, reassuring us that the job was absolutely doable. He explained everything in advance, provided a clear estimate, and completed the entire project within just a few hours.\n\nHassan's workmanship was truly exceptional. At every step, he made sure we understood what he was doing and even went above and beyond to ensure the result was something we'd be proud of. Besides his top notch skills, Hassan is personable, friendly, and extremely knowledgeable.\n\nI can't recommend Hassan highly enough. If you need a plumber who delivers quality and peace of mind, he's your guy. A+ service all the way. Thanks Hassan!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eduardo Piedra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3WiST0AuMs4brRvmSF9h35gBHecs3qjs-RH2KoXdxdWpFWDmC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a nightmare with a burst pipe in my front yard and other little things. I called H2flow Saturday morning and bam… he handle it before I got out. Hassan is an absolute pro! He left and no mess to be found. What blew me away was the price… he saved me a headache, a high water bill and my wallet was not hurt. No hidden fees, no upselling just straightforward honest guy. I highly recommend for all your plumbing needs. Thank you Hassan!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee Hankins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImTVGURAI8JCqQB15uz_epMJsT-1h26aRHAprG9y9GyOE1Ww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Couldn't be more pleased with the work Hassan did at my home.  Promptly responded to my text, quickly and expertly assessed the problem, and remedied a long-standing issue.  Hassan is a pleasure to work with, professional, timely, reliable and a genuinely nice guy.  My highest recommendation!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Herman Chou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWRGE_P78tdpKoGYBH3tNta838VpekiEzoSlLEvU4DuQ0lkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hassan re-piped our entire house and replaced all bathroom faucets.  The price is reasonable.  He is very professional, knowledgeable and responsive.  It's amazing that he worked so hard.  While he was on the job, we asked him to look at the slow drainage in the kitchen.  The problem was bigger a simple clean up but he took care of it very professionally.  Highly recommend H2Flow plumbing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0essA8y8eT3EO6tNTtaEM2UsigF-JCcwvbUoKfaJuQou3bICMdC6btWqA32CiSY1oLbch6GCNm3PFhpdPGxodFykWex8uib9z5YNG8hekvXeVLu2SzGsu6J-GOyrXoIEqMJNAEjQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3i9XVQoCE1gBuizdKF9s9exWpVB1L4OcYLd5G4SlkNidC9t6qkv62byKyDYeuLiZt6vEgYuycK5FOT7h0WLQrhwca5e4VemsLL53K_9Kz-MscPzukL1pSsJrkAHRUN9-uIlbRI=k-no"],"When":"2020-10-15"},{"Name":"Christopher Pynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWv-BSlet5a5aYC_QtSWEKLIBtV_dwhAADon1U3--bH-QFZ2k8F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hassan came by for an estimate and quickly debugged what other plumbers *claimed* were major issues. Easily saved me over 1k in service visits. Kind, transparent, and genuine!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sigrid J Strong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXgOyAuGqkgdfXtmuexFHs54F3YrdQ90C8xRPCv3dqzTglMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hassan is absolutely terrific to work with on plumbing needs. He was prompt to come and assess my broken hot water pipe. Made a plan and was prompt to fix it along with some other plumbing needs. I couldn’t have asked for a nicer person to work with. He is very very good and trustworthy. Will recommend him to all. And will continue to work with him on additional plumbing projects. Hire him with pure confidence!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Molly Hollinshed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbn7SmLQR9KV_Pf-1yzFohYiQDzCObpH-ClNM7-oxcdwH9zmyY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hassan was awesome to work with! We went through 8 plumbers flaking on us for a commercial job and finally found H2Flow who not only matched the price of our previous lowest bid, but completed the work right away with no issues/complications. The city of Mountlake Terrace is not simple to complete work in with the strict guidelines from the city, but Hassan met their strict requirements with ease. Very professional, responsive and pleasant to interact with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Schuyler Tjeckpes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVVsNZHPvSHn_xywPRM-Wr0ByQi-hrUOe3xa28egU-f6KXBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a general contractor. I found Hassan from another customer who had hired a plumber. I pay for a licensed plumber because I want to minimize my liability. I have had zero jobs where Hassan caused a leak or needed to come and fix an issue outside of hardware failure which wasn’t his fault at all. He understands the small tricks needed to prevent leaks that occur from following manufacturer directions. He also has a big smile on his face","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
