vC2YNMiGX-VALNqhzgMc3mOPPbnmTp6byE-gX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In the service industry its hard to find somebody who will give you a fair price and hard work. Jeff replaced my main sewer line at a reasonable price in a very reasonable time. He even made sure to make my lawn look nice after the job was done. I am thoroughly impressed with his honesty and craftsmanship and would use his services again any time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rick Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9vh_eHAVCa70i3UwwB_XyRh3nemEsBi-IHEGbbM9VVwJHwCk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeff did a great job on replacing the main water line to our house.  He was there when he said he'd be there, gave an accurate estimate, and finished in a timely manner.  There was minimal disruption in our daily water usage which made my wife and kids very happy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P T M BN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8gbtWCkUv-KI0vdYzJJlSj5t0l9pEN-C1bu6X69QP4esytQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent workmanship at a very fair price in a timely manner, 5 out of 5 stars in my book. My thanks to the Resolute team for help when it was really needed.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
