.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3guiTdvAbUOdidhUEEdzZ2SLyz6fWK3ibSC1b2SChMXF1YaAAodwgxveYKRlW3dnOUrBoUHRsBth2X6fs6XfwhWUGQoRwkYGTBqdMDRmUr1Sfi9xHNQnwlH2NdsI0_hYxsnnb3_x1X6FA=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-16"},{"Name":"Carol Maynard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuQjJpJ6GCLDhYKuNkFstMQ1vwVUHAOMmEL2UzrsGQyIzNpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Out of all the professionals that I use on my remodel… Falcon Plumbing was amazing!\n\nThey responded very quickly when I called. They were incredibly professional and knowledgeable. They even helped other projects in my home, such as with an electrician and tilers to troubleshoot their own issues!\nThey had no obligation to do this, but we’re very helpful on other projects!\nFalcon has incredibly fair prices and work hard/swiftly!\n\nPS-This is a real recommendation from a real home owner with four bathrooms , five toilets ,seven sinks and a pool system, etc.\n\nI am grateful to have them in my contacts; for sure!\n\nWhen you need a plumber; and everyone does at one time or another …you want a good one and these guys are better than great!!!!\n\nThank you, Falcon Plumbing","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_6QxfrAXpiF7jQr838Xo03xDgdetFU8PtximRZBt_J6pgy8Ec8DMRCyuOJdKuE36wUXWU9OG20_lVCvbO2AQKFbTqw-ou68gZ6rIIGKLfmUwXtqweP8HDNqgjallWm8d9dmaacA=k-no"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Spencer Richey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAXVKV84EJA89KXMWOxBraIoiMM0SwjtCgsY6Y_rMbRsUlYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve had a great experience working with Falcon Plumbing LLC! They’re responsive, professional, and get the job done efficiently. Communication was smooth from start to finish, and their team was respectful and reliable. Highly recommend them for any plumbing needs, thank you for the excellent service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julian Zamora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfk79ZB--VrSKBDw6yfPj4xKOD-4RD-iUbdLueJVnhsQ5-_ETI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a Maintenance \u0026 Validation Technician at a work leader company in the bio industry, it is imperative to find the right business to get the job done right and be efficient in all aspects. We needed two wash stations to be installed asap. Falcon Plumbing was extremely helpful, responsive and efficient. They got the job done professionally, efficiently and effectively. They guaranteed all their work and are very easy to work with. We have used them twice now, and we look forward to continuing doing business with them. Thanks Falcon Plumbing. Jamlech Z.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Long","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMka0w_otJILCVZR_qLxwX7SsxJiGzkCyBdLSukfD4BNmRSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very honest and timely service at a reasonable price. Fixed my leaky pipes and talked me out of more work that I didn’t need. They even replaced the drywall they cut (in contrast to most plumbing companies). I highly recommend Falcón.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Duncan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzfsC69pA_KWpbSMu__c0VmiZxdiEY54oVz42QmIJAa2aM5LY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have known Nahu for many years now, Everytime I get plumbing issues he is the first I call. Very communicative very quick and done right. I highly recommend Falcon Plumbing for everyone. He drove about 70 miles plus to help me out on water well once, that says a lot about his character. Thank you and many blessings.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marisol Johansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEoc6cQP9WMd4F8F8ma1dgSClU0ZtrqSHIrIHDDwZfED6tYVc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a faint gas smell in my laundry room and the guys at Falcon Plumbing came right away, identified the issue, and solved the problem within the hour. They were quick and effective in addressing a potentially dangerous situation. Highly recommend their services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avi Dabush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYs0Ky-0kMQSjzAWHy9ykWubfLoAZJ39KuuFxV-Ffis-Ufbtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired and worked with Nahu at Falcon Plumbing on multiple projects. They have great service and always provide exceptional results. I would recommend them to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
