0026 light fixture (very nice upgrade!); 3) installed positive shutoff valves to the clothes washer (no more drips). Gabe \u0026 Dante kept us apprised of the progress on each project \u0026 upon completion explained operations of changes. Work areas were all tidied up before their departure. Very pleased with the results! Thanks guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jingting Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJl_cR0rM9lcDaRZ9Khcit8feT2OXwsi9YVULQynP5wWoP18g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you Brandon for fixing our broken water heater so promptly! I called around a few companies and most expected more than a week to get the necessary parts to repair my Rheem natural gas heater. Brandon and team were able to source the parts locally and fixed the heater in less than 24 hours! I cannot express how thankful we are for being able to take a hot shower in the winter. On top of their great work, they were punctual, courteous and patient when answering my questions. Their rate was competitive and communication smooth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chell Black","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8z6_Uoz0Opp0kC4QfNAGZp-pi621Tfje8n8WknMnYVvntzTHX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We knew we were getting close to the end of life of our water heater, so during this year's annual inspection it was no surprise when a leak was found. Dimitri was able to do the replacement same day and updated a bunch of mystery to me, but \"things plumbers know about\" stuff, like fittings and tubing/pipes. Always happy with the service we get from this company and they come back and take care of us year after year. We have gotten amazing mileage from the Diamond Club.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taylor Frazier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM8NS-hgs_kLUSiYJEbL1PnSrubbStmKTcfHEcmNW0TOMqJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a Diamond Club member, I couldn't be happier with my recent service. Riley and Cole worked well together and with me. Riley is not only a great plumber, but is a great communicator. His people skills are top notch!  I felt no pressure to do anything and felt supported by the decisions I did make. If you are looking for a reliable and friendly plumber, look no further than Steve's Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chelsey Fairris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRcq87ia7k-t9UlGRQi8URUWAwB97A1fJ9rM8IzKqUJkiwNxGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an emergency leak on a Saturday at 5:15 p.m. and called Steve’s Plumbing. Their plumber, Thomas, arrived within 30 minutes. He was extremely professional and a pleasure to have in our home. He quickly identified the problem and explained the issues clearly so we could understand our options.\nWe will be working with you guys again.\nThank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marni Apio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlwJyeaxD5o2dzJoiEHcBlSL_vzMrCXM7KFxOghSBbcmERWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabe was prompt, courteous, and incredibly helpful.  He used state of the art technology to scan our sewer system and provided a maintenance plan. Everything was cleaned up from a toilet repair and tankless water heater flushing with no trace left.  Thank you Gabe and Steve’s Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heather Moran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD1yWYDksoSQDW4RmayHC3h7bwEakUmImkh0qL-Jy3QcBLXaVv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional service! This is how I would describe Gabe and Levi’s work.\n\nThis was the first time I have used Steve’s plumbing. I previously used another plumbing service for an extreme sewer line obstruction under my home that took over 8 hours and had to come back for incomplete work. Gabe, at Steve’s Plumming, was actually able to come out to my home the day I called to survey the issue. He determined additional help would be needed and was able to come back first thing in the morning the next day with Levi. They were both extremely professional and explained in detail exactly what they would be doing. They were able to clear the entire sewer line within the hour and made sure every drain in the house was working prior to them leaving. A huge thank you to you both!!\n\nI will definitely be using Steve’s Plumbing in the future!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
