e}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Dereck Grieve","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWw2ZXIAhEaQU6DqpMoT87slyzCMmLomxrC-0ZwL7-qgmV8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They replaced my water heater, added a filtration system for the whole house, and re-piped the whole plumbing of the house. Incredible job! It so nice having filtered water throughout the house. Thank you so much!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1wnsnaFo1j2qBm3rFQgMc1gxWKAJusnD735eWdn23mx7e6f9mA4mmf2gNE5O1vpQErWUwFeDt6sfhb6B8uyd8orHtvpeuJKKWxIIiKtJOry7KXycfKc8qdDU_O1ZOhV6GaOPpJ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2s_bff-D9OB2tuENkaGi1t8W6t1UBNZ6rzVwutM4S96AS9-smUTaeQUNWky9rBzg7lT4zNCvVjrYuJjpsk9xR40EJWL0WRFpU5jPjkaHkYyZr9ofw1cNrn_vKsfHSYvqgqGaMXhw=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-14"},{"Name":"Becca Jones - B. Jones Photography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtpnhOhVYcRP4h_gO0SQ7YQvAN8CxdQK5FyCds-hXlw7SHtHmJXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Review Title: Excellent Service from Gibson Plumbing!\n\nRating: ★★★★★ (5/5)\n\nI recently had the pleasure of working with Gibson Plumbing, and I must say, they were nothing short of fantastic! I faced issues regarding a cracked hose bib and needed a pressure reducing valve installed, and they handled it with the utmost professionalism.\n\nAustin, the plumber assigned to my case, was absolutely stellar. His communication was clear, concise, and he was always on hand to answer any questions and concerns I may have had. From the moment he arrived, he was dedicated, focused, and determined to get the job done right.\n\nHe provided a swift and detailed estimate that was fair and reasonable. The work Austin carried out was thorough and meticulous; it was clear he took pride in his work, and it showed in the high-quality results.\n\nGibson Plumbing, and particularly Austin, provided me with a seamless, stress-free experience. They are reliable, efficient, and highly skilled in their craft. It's not always easy to find a service you can trust, but I can confidently say that Gibson Plumbing is one of those rare finds.\n\nI highly recommend Gibson Plumbing for anyone in need of plumbing services. Their professionalism, dedication, and high-quality work are worth every penny. Thank you, Austin and the Gibson Plumbing team, for your exemplary service. I look forward to utilizing your services again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nessy Pittau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwrlejQeu7n7Kprrsk2Se9-g3XXkDZpRGoHDsfaOiXFYOOnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan and Austyn did a great job on my new ADU plumbing project. They had to create plumbing access from the street to my home. It’s been a couple months the job was done and everything is still in working order. I highly recommend hiring them for your plumbing needs. Thank you guys.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Meyers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTC7cODFRWYV0mgtSOg5pcWZ2sBE45_V9Gk05MxB5afNF8pGsr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't stress enough how accommodating, helpful, and responsive Gibson Plumbing has been. I was having issues with an outdoor hydrant that had water pooling around it from underground, and I had a pipe in the shed that only leaked when I turned on the hose faucet. I also had some general maintenance and operations questions about my water filtration and pump system.\n\nAfter exchanging a few texts, Dan and Austyn came out to diagnose the problems and take note of what parts were needed to fix everything. When it came to the questions I had, they were very patient and took their time explaining how everything worked.\n\nThey got back to me with a quote in a couple of days and came out to repair everything the following week. I highly recommend reaching out to Gibson Plumbing for all your plumbing needs. I already have them in mind for a future project!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roberto Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLffAEtR7JD6iN6vCIx_GGKVQCfeYHHhH6sFT31Jzi-sZzTRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Austin was professional and friendly. He identified the issue quickly and repaired it.\n\nI am very satisfied and will definitely call Gibson Plumbing again when needed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgE2NPJvWHQpH0J3VZauFYMtC2YPvUAfTwFU3CszVbnTY1KA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Gibson this morning with a leak that I needed taken care of, and they graciously worked me in this afternoon. Austyn was professional, knowledgeable, and a delight to work with. Gibson helped us out quickly a few years back and it is good to know that they still have the same great service levels and people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"thomas harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwzjJeWsyJykqqKIyGZViWB6UmhPT0itzAqcqyPh94Hg6Pfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We remodeled our primary bathroom which needed completely new plumbing for a brand new shower and free standing tub, and these guys did an absolutely amazing job. The quality or work was excellent and I would definitely recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mohamed E.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsMNp-yAo1WlBj_GcXbl0TV7ZSVck9VYez60ifNG-qfUVjPhlu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Gibson plumbing to check a water that was coming from the ceiling - was scary to experience. Austyn came in time and the first thing you notice is that there is no rush to cut your dry wall. Austyn started by making small holes to find the source of the leak and he tried hard to avoid cutting the ceiling open unless it’s the only option, even though cutting was more convenient. Luckily it turns out that it was very simple leak upstairs. Austyn was careful to make sure debris are contained and not scattering all over the place. In addition the charges was only for investigation and was super reasonable. I can’t recommend these folks enough! Hard to find that level of integrity these days!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
