m/maps/contrib/116743901188398674903"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Gilbert Saraspi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKomIqlkrxXECDIlT6j7nn4ukDeiYs-REjBnbzoZ3e1MsXmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Kirkland Water Heater Company for a quote and was impressed with their knowledge and expertise. I needed a replacement water heater right away and they were able to schedule me the next day. The technician was friendly and fast, he was out of there in 40 minutes. Their price is competitive with other companies I called but the overall experience I got was even better. After the job was finished, I got a courtesy call to see how everything went. I can't say enough and would highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natalie Crandall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKv6_9W_YMhAaXPcmVxAY1a8GeLp9O1ZiU6Nj-unULM0MwXrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike and the Kirkland Water Heater team are top notch. They got me a quote and replaced my tank within a few hours and somehow managed to take all the stress out of the situation. 11/10 would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary McGrew (McGrew Who?)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKC7fVP6NXS7i_UQtJ9PPTuCzO5wFlMC9IDO7AYq-1UNQ-UTCE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kirkland Water Heater Company saved the holiday! When our hot water heater stopped working two days before Thanksgiving, I thought we were going to be stuck with overnight company who couldn't even shower! Most places I called couldn't come out until after the holiday, but these guys were on it the next day. Mike was very helpful and he gave us the best possible price! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Coli D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIrmNDQzB-WXoo_lRj80KFANhmN15nLjwKnR5kZQIsFEu8_TB0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was so thankful for the help I received after my water heater was on the fritz. I couldn’t figure out what was wrong with it and contacted Kirkland Water Heater Company for advice.\n\nMike was extremely helpful as he tried troubleshooting a little on the phone with me, and then he came out to fix it for me.\n\nThe speed in which he arrived, the quality of service, and friendliness was enough to make me not want to go anywhere else ever again!\n\nMike was able to tell me exactly what the issue was, give me options on how to fix it, and quotes on pricing before he did anything to fix it.\n\nI was extremely happy to have the help of Kirkland Water Heater Company and would recommend them 1000 times to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fred Dodson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVp-MCeterEfY-GKmPrQxCAAwq0Mlr8DBfcxlacD-9xzTO5quO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my water heater go out I called Kirkland water heater co. They were quick to give me a quote and they were even quicker getting one of there plumbers out to    to cap the water heater same day so constant leak would stop and by next day they were back and had my hot water back in order. Mike the plumber by far went out of his way to make sure I was good and had everything I needed him and his helper was very clean and professional I definitely recommend this company thank you guys 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Loesby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzPJiFq-FxU1qJR2y7WTI1sQvQV9YN7ZrCjLvRYQJM5DmmIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tenant called late last night....water heater leaking all over.  She turned off the breaker and drained the tank  last night.  I called Mike at Kirkland Water Heater Co this morning and he responded within  two hours.  New tank in place and a very happy tenant.  Happy landlord too.  I will use them  again.  Mike was 6 stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Gallagher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVR37WOAiI7Sr-NENA8J_aX002SCmJlAd4ygbEBBlDm47OUYK4OUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quality is the word I would use to summarize my overall experience with Kirkland Water Heater Company.  For any business such as this, you sort of expect a certain amount of punctuality and professionalism but for all sorts of reasons, you don't always get that.  I try to have reasonable expectations whenever I deal with repairs for my tenants...yes, timing is key but if a vendor rushes out to complete the work, there is a greater chance that additional repair might be needed which delays normal living conditions even further.  The pacing, professionalism and quality of work are exactly what I hope to experience with such important repairs.  I'm grateful for their time, energy and talents in getting things back up and running again.  We're all so grateful!.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"veronica macias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaVkdzW1dpCyuRdbhYvYRK0Wo8IJvtDhUUrNL-PL5aJdrCZo8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Called them and asked for an estimate to replace my water heater and told them they would need to come out to look at it because it's a unique situation. They told me to take a pic of it. I told them I was not able to do that but wanted to make an appointment for next week and to have it done right away. I called them because they are a small company in Kirkland and I wanted to support that. The guy was rude to me on the phone because I couldn't take pics and Wouldnt make an appointment for me without pics. He then told me to find another company to work with.\nNot a good start and really bad customer service. Glad I didn't use them because they really don't care.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
