":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Chris Holm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWq_Ft9E4Rz-wZeN51tCeqP_liVKizva5mFN6q8_BvhPH6Yu3IE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lighthouse Plumbing is the best plumber I’ve worked with in Seattle and the Eastside. Ryan and Bradyn are as good as it gets.\n\nI bought an old house a couple of years ago, and one of our bathroom sinks stopped working. I called Ryan at 4:00pm and he was here the next morning with his team to diagnose the issue. He was direct about the issue, and recommended fixing the issue thoroughly to reduce future costs.\n\nWe scheduled a time which worked for us, and Bradyn and team came each day on time. Bradyn texted me specific updates each day, and walked through the steps of horizontal boring through our steep driveway, and repiping our house and replacing galvanized pipes. Their communication was so good.\n\nI would highly recommend Lighthouse Plumbing for fast responsiveness, honesty, and amazing work. I will be using them for my future needs without question, and I’d recommend them to family and friends.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3dzhuGOnVP0kMqV8Q1oqpnRf2CkWZngcqlQq6ZvtVogoADT0oKFe5anVmQCvfb90iOIcJjpxHNHKxoXefIgqxrvTlARa4otJQNEsj5BKzmDOjH91AWy2NC_cv4EJtVLWenTCt_cSrohxnK=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3yhGvrtzw2bMqJeHJ59PNFgQ1TrYKqsvfs3FtVz9_xNIUQQKWG3ISlKkTEoYiaEWpmStpwqsVXMYTx2qnOeLK18uzOqXzxFD5tXVPjF7rcF9tmsL7Fq_hnucxMhe4I_OHzhZe65ZuwFK2P=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-24"},{"Name":"Keith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOlAyvuNxTcyi4i2VfCSrOTI5LP0H6TpYf7kiwVlopjp7uvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lighthouse Plumbing is a local, for me family run plumbing contractor. Layne arrived on time and replaced our water heater, capped a couple of old W/D valves, and fixed our second tub/shower drain issue.  100% professional, Friendly and easy to work with.  Great company and people, very reasonable price for the service and accommodating for scheduling.  Great Company!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2pem7QyIcv3eUcoQa94LmUQz5G9Td1y7E6OG1FsklEXRVPkw-IECefm6mYEu0edeuSSInG1_bdx0P1wRAtxZOCnZ7bpip6Fi-VkcJUdHmfYEkar6eh2Y7G4J0qdOMySkZ256xwdtPB06qu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2TVFL_yZc91hH4XVQTBNQbnxihrPlvRrC3hzu96wUpetiVVei7aAIdbjBRixqhvMFouu_8ckiCHrcq12DEOeh2R0nSJ6oEmCjv5y4AvLIMZWa-ed1zNjY54_DhJyy31tM9pGzZAiRM3rPb=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qsHmC4HmDApYxRNAQ7cxlmw9-ogQVbqdqMj5KwCf5qeyuKzIijHJ17OSIeldx5hstaPkqabg5FNvm-lOZDaeW2Dcgn28B4YMnTvIq6652Qv9GNVTUXiY9KktoYq6Aw-UsddJqDLw9nXnR=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-26"},{"Name":"Brandy Zwiefelhofer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKivtHG_xpq2dPyiNHgPoWYernD9AlOSZeIWTE2gieVnFjVNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an exceptional experience with Lighthouse during a really stressful situation involving a leak in my main water line. From the first call to the final repair, the entire team was professional, responsive, and incredibly reassuring.\n\nThey took the time to clearly explain what was happening, what my options were, and what the process would look like. I never felt rushed or pressured, just well-informed and confident that I was in good hands. In the middle of what was a chaotic and overwhelming issue, they brought calm, clarity, and real expertise.\n\nThe whole team was fantastic, but I especially want to recognize Layne and Beau. They were awesome! Efficient, knowledgeable, and super respectful of my property. They executed the repairs seamlessly and made sure everything was done right. It’s clear they take pride in their work.\n\nI’m genuinely grateful for the care and professionalism Lighthouse showed throughout the entire process. I would absolutely recommend them to anyone dealing with plumbing issues, especially something as major as a main line leak!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Xu5XRBOk6a4RcO62YCwwKnY2qGT8ha6iElwsJpYWKlUJD9amvqKm6St3voAYlo823mXu-vtwffHNjej2oTNVkAyZXoHetebcWecZJi3PcXkpu_wcO_nO2x0KEKZX-sR-uJeE-zZBwLWJl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14VELtxMIkajYAfCafcYUSG_795pZ7skG3nTaAmINAYI0Mw6b1jTiEe0zSYRVk6A61Ne6mk_Ohdn3biTKHmaR_BCWAgdSVu5_IDW7l7kmzo47PzBAGxoEaHq4FJVuOjRluXPDDjXcNV7af=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2xCABkiPHIb8f0InhHtWiWj3qkmGvAiLYHKaG5oSOUiWZckabVzPIX0mR5RY8envGRIy51Xa-m2z4H_UYIaDrEDC6f_1F6pdgrP5PYZwqs5eF6vDyWWznXd7pGD3JcU90i6xmz93F0jIsk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17x8z0TDgKCAGE7dafIY97cHIeEH65-J_dHsEUmP5NPwpwAy3dRqD-VH6cPqsQYiRjLy4AJeHR_BLxgDDrk-6kKD2VAYp_d1hIQNmYIIo9ns0jZay9UaPIz5iC1CcEYSpUcF0LuoHNHd8=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-26"},{"Name":"Michael Grantham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9JK2ABIT8247w__QpZeo8FM6ODXr75YXZC13o7F7WxoUv9OE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Braydn and Beau were super easy to work with and did a great job. Brandon very easily identified the quirks of our setup and knew exactly how to manage them. They made a point of leaving the water heater piping better than when they found it. Jackie at the office was also super easy to work with. Everybody was prompt, communicative and curious. Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Akshay S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX19krFsnmXbAX4aTp59mrvZzbwH_eEL5poVDbJo8Tt4xlu4WGR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently hired them to install a Bradford White hot water tank in our home, and the experience was outstanding from start to finish. The team was prompt and professional - they showed up right on time and kept us informed at every step of the process. Their quote was competitive, and they delivered a high-precision install with zero mess left behind.\n\nSpecial shout-out to Blaine, who did a terrific job! His attention to detail and commitment to doing things right really stood out.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0OuafDfrKPq4WsIy5uc8CQf4v7hINCMFubTwl0b3SKsEfp2XvChxdQvDQqEv2svBehi7jXY1DbXFQDpB_mHF6FQ3pIseHtf6aakKw8Q3pCXqioxx39eVxOku6B_btCiIqYPXo0_Qc3UKI=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-23"},{"Name":"Alina Moreland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWN5_bCH3W_2vgZAUdT_btjtErr_sZaL7jroamihfdsmgFgW-G_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an excellent experience with Lighthouse Plumbing. This was actually our second time using them, and great experience both times. They came out the same day, were quick, professional, and immediately found the issue. What stood out most was how blatantly honest and genuinely nice they are — no upselling, no scare tactics, just clear explanations and fair pricing.\n\nOur first experience was with Ryan, and this time Daniel and Beau helped us — all wonderful. You can tell they have a high level of experience, and I feel confident the repair was done correctly. 10/10 recommend Lighthouse Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Downs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7oO5zPp66EgsQuyRXGsKT3IS_w2vNNSIdaby2Igb_t9cs724=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ryan (the owner) took my call late on a Tuesday as I was looking for a knowledgable and trustworthy expert on a plumbing issue I was experiencing. He took the time to listen to the horrible experience I had with a larger 'Big Box' plumbing company and helped guide me through the appropriate next steps. He showed up promptly, reviewed the situation in depth, and helped guide me on the right path forward without pressuring me into a situation that I wasn't comfortable with or didn't understand.\n\nPSA: If you're new to working with a plumbing service, make sure to work with a company like Lighthouse. They care about their customers and their reputation and they operate with that in mind.\n\nThank you, Ryan!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe Cole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8aVFbaAL7RyMcXMN7_jUF8hnkeAsomYejkdJayZ2IJLEwig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really impressed with Lighthouse Plumbing. I called on Friday morning with a clog that left us without use of our kitchen sinks/dishwasher/etc. They had Bradyn out that afternoon, he identified the problem immediately (turns out drain pipes going UPhill is a problem), and he had completed a reroute/repair that included the addition of about 20 feet of new plumbing by noon on Monday. So much of being a homeowner is knowing who to call when a problem comes up. I will absolutely call Lighthouse Plumbing back when the need arises. They answered the initial call, they had someone out same-day, they were up-front about the cost, they fixed it the next working day. . .Thanks guys! Great job.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
