e under the cabinet where I had to crawl on my back to shut it off. He made it easiest, fastest, pain free for me. They even used 80 bags of pebbles and sand to backfill the hole. I am very happy to work with kind, hardworking, competent professional who put homeowners at ease. I will definitely use him again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3yA-8AsoE0P6Bafc-BAJ98Zce1COBzdPN0GVreTrcSAUW_2eU30IW8UxOd8OJC4cB3V2b9tzobtYmbIqUTFfW0lFPW3L7xczPi0exRikkbwj-hxSXa9ucQm7cZFL9JPsEqQne8ngtpnIEU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zl3RseOSdEWzTQ6YhYMcBViXKlhCMsKPSmayiajv5h_A1EuPs913ZX6DG_I64c8XjDLf-Y895jcCm3Yr6b9zn3YJ27FteSx8NIlhF8sMgjZjIHEEqKLDhuJslqMywgwZWBoJyh0YiqPU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0aiYtDZPnxCzOuFOu9hIvdVj2GtmTnVEBMTj-1kFU0C3iYkht91jit4vy5l2hej5ULcUdkZr0BDxgIGbOYOA4MIj4kzycjz_u8ot7L9doPAbBH7iwS3i_Exi1ukdAf9Qc71Hm57ThpVJA=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-14"},{"Name":"Iris Yuen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbIBvXERa1gNVfeEigxYFSnAKSBarryXoeqtP6pcy8grJHoaWF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jason is super responsive and get everything done perfectly in a short time! He professionally figured out all the pipes leakage areas and fixed them in no time. Very knowledgeable and highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4uTX1SnmKU4TX3_c9nSFVmkxaAIOqPMHHJ_jzU-Q0yZCSzfZI_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing! Jason and his team are incredible! Excellent communication, detailed explanations of not only what he’s going to be doing but a review after it’s been completed as well. He answered all of my questions in a way I could understand and ensured that I knew all details necessary for the future before leaving. They were clean and made sure to lay down tarps so that the carpets remained untouched. It was an excellent service, efficient, and was completed with care