en-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Justin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYn56HUCGzSBTP76qc0F-CKQZjeqR4Zw8Ri5UZp2xQQdQNKx-76A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Anthony's Plumbing did a great job installing a handheld shower and slide bar in my bathroom. CJ was prompt, efficient, and very friendly. He took the time to make sure the placement was exactly how I wanted and completed the installation quickly and professionally. The finished result looks fantastic (see the attached before-and-after photos). I would definitely recommend Anthony's Plumbing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn18U0QXl9pqF4yRv32bCsHPb8tKZgxJowzIGgCw2x72rWnZMmuW8LIHPHNoFFnxbreTP1D3q59dSDjqcJD8XJ0D-k3J2xgoGAvRL9Jq3cSF0C3WA7M9vLv5m9NxOIrPBPOl3Ukr2cyOcRA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25gGLwhzA_VZeq-i9QvOoFSUfksmUVrc8UU17gCQYslZ9AAnwjc1JRJvDUQgPeqLq_hktEl2-uocnjCJxHbn57IIzY8Y2PRHs7kURFTckm8dyJ8kVvbJaPlGnYz2NnniS2_unsIWdG3js=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-10"},{"Name":"An Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKERNfm7NRgoS_HPmn-rN-4tGcePUkaZWmsPe1xWPcBMRKZ34o0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob and CJ are professional, communicative, and easy to work with on a tankless water heater install.\n\nJacob initially stopped by and we discussed my home's constraints, future plans, and various water heater options. I received a quote promptly after the visit, and after getting a few additional questions I had answered, was easily able to schedule the install.\n\nCJ was very thoughtful throughout the install. He reviewed the plan, provided context during the install process, and ensured he had my input whenever a decision needed to be made.\n\nHappy to support a local team and will keep them in mind for future plumbing projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Javier Marin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIupjjuysMXOgta13j11vDPmBYgjGojudzrz7I68H9RX8Zqzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience. We had a kitchen faucet that needed replacing and we ended up going with Anthony's. Easy scheduling and quick responses. CJ came by and was able to take care of the replacement quickly and gave us tips on how to deal with are particular situation if anything new comes up. Great and friendly guy. Overall great experience, would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Douglas Wick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLm1RRstiH_AK-JT_lAwQLwV-KNXY7CFLMKtvrFk2-nRSxPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very responsive to the needs of homeowner and scope of project.  Jacob allowed me to send pictures of the job and receive a free estimate.\n\nDetailed and accurate estimate given for time and materials.\n\nCJ did the work well, and consulted me when issues came up (ultimately easily resolved), and he had excellent respect for and attention to keeping all used spaces clean.\n\nI received estimates from 7 plumbers, and Jacob's was competitive and without the standard trip fee estimate where you  take the job or not but still pay.\n\nIt is great to support a truly local establishment. I would highly recommend Anthony's Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cutter Werdel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9SMGlKrRVEmFzf0K2aduFTKjcjmsBsbMVg_rSA59KrRtzGBs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you to everyone at Anthony's Plumbing. Especially Jacob for his outstanding assistance. He went above and beyond to make sure all my questions were answered and that I got the help I truly needed. I really appreciate his professionalism and dedication! I’m incredibly grateful for the help and guidance I received from Anthony’s Plumbing. From the very beginning, they stepped in with genuine care and made sure I felt supported every step of the way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John T Monahan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIjaokXes9GWjcf39_HRHd9Th-Nk8uIKpRfudAvD_uxEPyqnb-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not recommend these guys more highly.\nIt’s very reassuring to have such smart, capable and thoughtful professionals replace my leaky water main. They did excellent work, for a very reasonable price and far faster than I expected. Their timely work resolved an expensive leak and upgraded my interior connection for a reliable fresh start.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Clonts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIp5qsJxbMOdjHkSQNGoreQLIqjYMAHVkxksATtMb_9faabnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"CJ from Anthony's installed a water pressure limiter valve at my house. Super professional, quick and informative. Also, Anthony's was up front and gave an estimate before the project, which I've found the larger plumbing companies around here won't do. The pricing was also reasonable compared to other companies. Definitely recommend these folks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Fridley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFLxEIUqdscvUnO9JvE9HxC--Lmf_Ih1EOCNleU9x-dl80mg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob and CJ snaked our sewer line for us and made the process as easy as possible. They squeezed us into their schedule and finished quickly, all while explaining everything thoroughly so we felt equipped making decisions. Pricing was fair, and we found a plumber we trust to use in the future. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
