{"Name":"Vince Sure","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPx2Qopa7s0MX1BWNsGvWWuwE2tfpQ2ESCm6w5Th1ejqo6py5Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Logan and Kevin came to my place to check out an issue I have with my sink. They explained what was going on and what needed to be done to resolve it. I was informed that there were several options regarding the repair. I am very pleased with their service and commitment to resolving the issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ahmed Aslam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzRQ7XOm3dnpSSUWCtGrToS1kVuA8dCW96Yt9-G7Zt2uvFrcSh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A long overdue review that i have been meaning to write...\nThis company is great!! Last July on a Thursday night.. my water heater broke down all of a sudden. Friday morning I made a few calls, almost every company quoted me an egregious amount for the urgent replacement request or charged a service fee to come up and inspect my unit.. Dappers technician Alex York showed up. inspected the unit and gave me a lowest quote of all .. he even waived the service fee and gave me a hug (honestly i needed that) .. this guy is awesome!!! he spent 3-4 hours replacing the unit and even changed my plumbing so that maintenance is easy to do in the future.\nNot to mention Heidi who handles front desk is awesome and was able to get me scheduled quickly (Thank you Heidi!!)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Isyron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJos7uIoYFdYKOZP7NL5hF86-PaiprQxg6LQVLeBZECnTPHtA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They fixed my heater after a different company botched the job.\n\nWhen they fixed it, they caused a wire to short that didn't show itself until after their test runs.\n\nThey turned back around and had it fixed immediately. Problem free since then.\n\nThey even hooked up my dog with a dapper little bow tie","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SeattleOrganMan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS6lj1uGmHLrj1_N5FSiVGXZd54b3wNjpOZxydP15MDfFkhAI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the first time we've had to call a plumber in the 13 years we've been here. But Dapper installed the Natural Gas service to our house for the gas range. They also installed the exhaust fan over the stove. And their great work is why we called them for plumbing work. Alex was wonderful to work with. He communicated well about what was going-on. Our sewer pipe under the house was backed-up above the clean-out 'Y' so it was going to be an ugly and unpleasant job. But he stayed directed and busy and got the line cleared with snake, and all is now right and good. We shared a cup of our home roasted coffee with him before he cleaned-up the work site and departed. And if we have need again with electric, gas, or plumbing. . .I know we'll call Dapper.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Denice Nelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoLitEZ6xneiCSSVVAO7TeH6o5PzTG01DAiP43E8cVoBu0vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kevin did great. He was here on time,  very helpful in explaining what needed to be done and the reason why. I will definitely call Dapper for any of our plumbing needs. He replaced two outside faucets and had to re route a bathroom drain.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katrinia S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWECVV9aAZzMFq9q7CjG_VR22AZPGShtIibH--6nZc8NgGg9rzLkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Greg come out this time and I feel like he really knew what has been causing the issue since this was installed in June 2022. I wish he had been here sooner. I was pretty frustrated because I didn't think this should be even happening if installed with a trap cleaning vent to start with and a bit of customer information. But either way he was able to explain and clean what was there and give us information going forward. He's been the most informative tech I've had out yet I feel like. Also, I signed up for their maintenance plan that seems like a good value for $20 a month. Overall, I'd recommend them. But I can say I had my frustrations with our install with them in 2022 and not going this way from the start. But Greg at least figured it out.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angella Deaton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcvvRjCuG1pH6jcQ3XEYy5_FsYZRzu5IJusciUIPqFt2g1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"George W. was very professional and funny which I appreciate! He and his partner talked with us about the process for replacing our hot water tank that had just gone out 2 days ago. Gave us a quote we signed and they got right to work. All said and done it was installed start to finish within just a couple of hours. Afterwards, he went over everything with us and was very thorough. We are repeat customers with Dapper and have always been happy with their work!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3itBcJMOyMdVs4AZJ_Rs_CnGURMx7wb-KTstgcI9iAGIQKrjLxEGDZt_-Swl-eQULtM2W-tc2FTjXBZU1e-UMf5bqK9zC53UOrafozpwiC0w7MCrvPgT9-iqD4jllXam5R6DKh=k-no"],"When":"2024-2-2"},{"Name":"JME ELECTRIC GROUP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWn09ww1JsPORCzGbsygQEnI6wNyOYK6Pz36gP7fHoco-m-NfM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️\nDapper Plumbing \u0026 Electric did an outstanding job! Their team was professional, friendly, and provided top-notch service from start to finish. The quality of work and customer care truly set them apart. Highly recommend for any plumbing or electrical needs!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
