eet View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=E2UcTugMDX0gNb7116x_Dg\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=265.44574\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"","name":"D Young's Plumbing Inc (Owner)","link":""},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Industrial","street":"10417 NE 109th St","city":"Kirkland","postal_code":"98033","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mark daves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsCdiOcwqykcN-QodbAmfSgqIX9RUW-V1eSPhTj-pyecTVHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"wood floor bethesda, team are very professional. They did a wonderful job to install the hardwood floor  for me in my house. They're hardworking and they care the details. The project went very smooth. I highly recommend their service","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0l0DmuNITA5Fc1CSje73wDTH8IQ5DxQjE8JGnWNK0uXDIJKFq150oRGSREcdnWOW2XNd-20wqlXLGFfYBjE6t7ky7Sr78QCC8kgCmiIICERdAcUiVqucKm92eoUpJ6WKqVm5d5=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0XNMWJpKUNCue0Oef46YSE9xC61BE71PCc4GnkH7BLQDYBXIpDQS0TIpWjGRBlPH8HBF4kPj1sCgui_w9gUATPZDWoee6SKja24fgV_HWWGEWMS9I6S5CQf0ocXV3sadKd3Xji=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn38aK2-KUoljv7PvdN_JN6oZpuWDJi73MiSd2LjjBfTJ0T-UoqjfYdJJrdIh6Ds64SwUOJh8kCTQEZKikF8thDTZhxWVTdy_Pkq_gk0EIr9UCKqbo6hKgQ9LF8If_UKmg7DopN0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Frfk64W-tZofTQmKhruQiBPg7axDEvDUsxclUJIS8YEZlHXepXxMf-XLUvSVZpOfKyLPKQRDWmZjA_Oh_06FhyColcarIup7Y9VUkY3SZADDmImY4Ifd7bCAn_aXWfkkduLCt=k-no"],"When":"2018-2-9"},{"Name":"Gracie Bach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9accawEE3ddduTQX1tTB1ACg7bPXqjpnkwHhGli3PVO0Pxyo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are getting new kitchen countertops, sink, and faucet. We needed a plumber to disconnect our old stuff and reconnect the new stuff after the installation. We received four quotes from different plumbers, and were shocked at the cost. I kept looking and eventually found D Young’s Plumbing and the cost for the quote was fair for the services needed. The owner was very kind, and their scheduler accommodated our tight schedule.\n\nMatt, showed up on time, and got the job done right on schedule. He was professional, very friendly, and did a wonderful job. Matt has excellent communication skills too, making sure to let us know when he would arrive, and walked us through the process.\n\nIf you are looking for a local plumbing company who charges fair rates AND does quality work, look no further. Thank you Matt, and support staff a D Young’s Plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe Venters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtvZar6Ns0OOR8Rd-EdfQKo1bLKs3iIexuZaEnUUPejqVb0B1cRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys are some of the best local plumbers that we've used. I highly recommend giving Guy and his team a call. Dave was a lifesaver after our bathroom remodel went south.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3q4_15mvIUWFGNvIoUJn6CSMhLy5vhGdBhbeHV_KhJzmuNXA-wbE38vg8sC0_5NYWQyyKts_DrJNVzSuQvfZm9i4qDtuXdH4b5-DSfHoLKVQDrUZWsx3FKzqa0k7fQnHTaXj-8=k-no"],"When":"2020-4-14"},{"Name":"Alex L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZ7OQBQY81a-Va8Lp9f3JUUKKezscKID7iRMcWMX1Xbt8XmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a surprisingly positive experience with this company. I needed a plumber to resolve our emergency by fixing the leaking pipe inside the wall. After contacting the receptionist, I received a call back from Guy within a few minutes. He could schedule the urgent appointment, and his plumber was able to resolve the whole issue within the next couple of hours for a reasonable price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diana Jorgensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9tV5fyo1Ramd8_NVQkHevrsVK7VHX7EBg8mWgzJJBWtjUpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Can I give ZERO STARS?? Cause that is what I would like to do. I called and scheduled an appt in the morning of December 14th for a time frame of 12 - 4pm. I was told it would be about 2pm-ish. I called the office at 3pm, 3:45pm, 4:15pm to ask if they were still planning to come (Cause I hadn't received a courtesy call they were on their way) and talked with the office lady who said they were still coming and she would reach out and have them call me (each time). I NEVER received a call from the plumbers. Around 4:45pm I called and she told me she couldn't even get ahold of them.\nShe setup a meeting for the next morning to meet them. Mind you, I don't live at this location so I had to drive 45 mins from my home to hang out in my tenant's place. I met Matt the following morning and he was great, they didn't find the water leak and hope he finds a reputable plumbing company to work for in the very near future.\nI received another call from my tenant who said there was still a water leak. I left a message for D Young, to have them back. Scheduled it for 12/20 10-11am. Guy said he would meet me. I called the office at 10:45am to ask if he was still coming, because again I had not received a courtesy call saying they were on their way. Guy called me just after 11:35am. He asked what he was doing for me because he couldn't remember. I told him nothing, I told him he was horrible for leaving me hanging 2 appointments. He responded that I was a HORRIBLE person for not letting him work on my place!! When I had been waiting for him in the window time frame they had given me and been completely DISREGARDED for my time with no communitcation. They left me hanging twice!!\nI would never recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharla M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICxlbzfVgD_TbnVzgHQsX8gH349wTcnuEqFIJCjD4n4uoq6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sooo impressed with this business.  I had a broken pipe just off the water meter.  After my phone call, the owner, Guy, was out to take a look inside of 15 minutes and had me scheduled immediately the next morning.  Guy has been in the business for decades and has the kind of customer service I wish was not such an outlier - friendly, professional and down home.  His people were out the next morning and were equally impressive.  Price was more than fair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fortune Cookie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgW0BKdnYjnkuOHAeJ1cBWcfgjpeXBwhm3gElAS9WSrlY_l5I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"D Young has showed consistency in their professionalism, friendly attitudes, from the owner to the receptionist and to the plumbers. The work they have done with my kitchen faucet is really good.\n\nNow I'm having issues with two other dripping faucets and the main condo unit shut off that didn't work and became a potential emergency, they always are there for me. Thanks D Young, I would not choose another plumbing company :) Appreciate your services and your attitudes. Take care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Kott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCvM4Mk3NQ4KefXzdaiudAr1Mz42hlUVnUnSWvGHolT6PW5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A friend from work recommended Sean from wood floor  Bethesda  to me and told me she had him totally redo her stairs. after the first call i knew he was going to be amazing. he came and gave us a free estimate and was able to articulate perfectly what needed to be done and it was right in our budget. he was able to bring with him color samples as well as picket samples for us to choose from which made things alot easier. he was very kind and friendly and you could tell he knew what he was talking about. he fully sanded and restrained our whole staircase and also painted the risers and stringers white and it turned out phenomenal. he finished exactly when he said he would and the project was beyond our expectations. his whole crew was amazing and even though he didn't have to, he would always bring coffee in the morning. I would recommend Sean from wood floor  Bethesda  for any stairs job and also look forward to having him remove the carpet upstairs and install hardwood soon.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
