ame":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Faisal Jamil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFH_A5LG-6_Nslgb-_wFc1uP9rD-EklJ-_c5m2Sl9CTow1wJMAWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a water leak that flooded the garage.  The first  quote was for the next day.  We decided to ask around for something  sooner.  Hugo came in took care of the water heater in a few hours.  He was very professional, very clean and caring around his work.  Great customer service.  I would recommend to all my friends.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Mrr9BmnHBsyiMxLl-fLkpnYR1vmurc-QQYRFiC05tVtij2FhtCNf_RzeWFR99S-d4fafLEe0QavZk2G-0qoY3O99aamYumiqB_27qxHSrj8ObuhOD1ylnVtqy7kTy_E1BcyPX1SP8JFc=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-2"},{"Name":"Will Fant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpVh4uvbxq9wCKh8shWX9pve2Ums-IxvPxUbzKTSgpdloGg7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jaren Larson, A plumbing technician from Gene Johnson came to do work for us a couple of weeks ago. We had a nonworking toilet because of a leak out of the bottom. I called and He came the very next day. He Completed the job and cleaned up thoroughly. He also spent extra time going over some non-related questions we had about piping and heating elements Housed in the garage, which Runs throughout our place. Later he sent over an estimate for a possible future project. We would love for him to be our go to guy if Available, If any future issues pop up. I’ve waited\nto do this review wanting to see how the work held up and so far everything is working well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Hozjan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnEhxwbsy_iq4ckfKOby35HiYqC9MJTlpAWS6PPGcp74tVhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Called Gene johnson plumbing with issues with my water heater tanks leaking at a fitting they sent technician Derek solberg out \u0026 he discovered that the previous installers had did it incorrectly . So gave me an estimate on repair cost which was way lower than another company quoted me \u0026 completely different than what they were going to do . So with out hesitation I agreed with his estimate \u0026 did it all today done and a very excellent job done by Derek  ! Highly recommend this company !! The other company name ended in town - they had nothing but excuses for not showing up to do the job but I’m now happy with them not coming there loss my big gain ! Thank you Gene Johnson plumbing !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tina Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTn7tksTThFJzAQ-JDlW8X8eBp8vzjJt0ttQGwk1Vip06GytE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hugo Lira Hernandez was our technician for water heater maintenance. He arrived on time, was incredibly professional and courteous. He clearly explained the maintenance process and fixed some small issues. The work is completed efficiently and thoroughly. He provided great advice on things I could do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW05p201_9JgGwl8L5qox60j5KK_hck6vh34V6PrhaSZCAN5dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike Pierce came to my home today and inspected a plumbing problem that I have. He clearly knew what he was doing, and did a good job of working with me to diagnose the problem.\n\nHe educated me on the nature of the problem, and described for me a number of solutions at different price points.\n\nI appreciated his professionalism and clear communication style. If and when I need a plumber in the future, I'll be calling Gene Johnson Plumbing again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Wade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJEyWyRxVXxIzc3nvF977oAZltQwuU1XjklxvOH5mkmbv2vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hugo did an amazing job. I called because of toilet issues and he was able to diagnose the issue. He also was able to notice issues with the water heater and get that fixed as well. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elaine S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXKk7Kqq0NxnN1M8j4VOqehEyp_qAEmKdCKPmZv52lZXjPBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David Sanchez, Plumbing Technician, not only is highly skilled, but also superb at analyzing plumbing issues and taking the steps to resolve them. He cares greatly about ensuring the customer’s concerns are addressed and welcomes questions. David cares about his customers. Additionally, he cares about maintaining high standards of practice and is a real asset to the Gene Johnson Company.\nIn order to properly address my plumbing issue, which included a leak, he assessed the problem and installed new piping. Because I am interested in my house’s plumbing, I enjoyed learning about each step of the repair process. He was very thorough, and got my permission for the additional work. When he was done with the job, he carefully cleaned everything up. I will definitely call the  Gene Johnson Company for any future work that may arise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiju5wcPcBRdxhBIeeVR-FWmiiG-wW7Y6ZBrzgxGsHpF-KzR-O=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Installing an air admittance valve under the sink was straight forward due to Jose’s skill and experience. But nothing is easy and he had to cut thorough two layers of hard plywood, which will have to be replaced to finish the job. But Jose left the work easy to follow with removable clips for water pipe. A separate vent pipe will have to be covered due to a vent pipe hole being cut and left open (by someone else).  What I also love about Gene Johnson and especially Jose, is the education I got about plumbing. From the number of vents on top of the roof and their origination, to the tangle of pipes in the basement and their defunct washing machine hookups. I appreciate the clear communication about the scope of work and his careful, courteous and clean manner by which he went about the job.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1URwBPCx8QlGyA8KJgSRpAlBdZ9EWQa18AjTOCHXIr9ljZ4ypA7kSxThFZy9UPJMqPf42bHmoCrNS_ezGnUDkprZuie5QkkN9DqiHiTr4RxXtKktNpKfHF6hz5SW6Of8ua40M-=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2XzwijkY40COR8bLm3kVfBzWGQkWDQFqNwNBrDZPt6Fy2XvCcyUM7nujYnIN_CcTVH6PbmGKIQHWoGfQf6XKMxerRHqWW43zDqRbdg2OC4fqiQRxkM_un5SApCzwaVS5B4q2RD=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-7"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
