owledgeable. He answered a ton of questions for us and we will definitely continue to call him in the future. Thank you David!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1YAIF87nWstSAOAcwo8c5fQiZjsTDDRxFVJlXTCZXtAnC_l95cWBXS9F6hmjfC8wUhxCCOwxuxKWN0QtD5k8RmSmFb2elbYNCJE0FERbr5pmNzCuHo_ii3RywG_cIKPCiaXRzns1yhQu_8=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-5"},{"Name":"Kathy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK79oVgyAqKchplfhc_-UsI5kZQJPMoT-lA04Hk4d6C2jN7cg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David is top notch!!  By far, the best plumber I’ve ever used.  He will be the only plumber I will use from here on out.   He is excellent and efficient, and very skilled!   He fixed the plumbing issue with our toilets I originally contacted him about (replaced the components inside the tanks), but when he was here, I had him look at something questionable with our plumbing under our sink, and he saw a problem, pointed it out to me, explained it well, and he was able to fix it when he was here still!  I was so grateful and our plumbing under our sink looks and works significantly better now!   And he was extremely thorough and did excellent work!\n\nAlso, while he was here, he noticed the water shut off valve on one of our toilets was starting to fail.  I would have never known this was failing if he hadn’t been thorough!  So he replaced that as well.\n\nI loved that David didn’t just come to “do the job”, but he went above and beyond expectations!\n\nDavid is a super nice guy, very professional, explained everything so clearly, he left the spaces he worked clean, and just very friendly and personable.\n\nContact David for any of your plumbing needs!! You will be very happy with the results!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1WGBh1mEdpDIxXOB0Kij4eNEGsC0j37Hr8k6i38u0n9Zol5ZvTNS9XWqs7CyTDF8fm1Mt0labNZofrdAw_S5XzwLQZgqs2NeIYNhXFwoOoeUmCXDw1d4-aLGUs92fTibRAgtCw-n_v9LSO=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0QBdlyubW0lmwzGSyMzSTWZwEZFoCNBIXIaIqMhGoy_-7g17vgt5WhmF4gf8ciCi0FEJKgflp5W-kjOQgSlQnkMxaXnbcyyAnKdspBkfCsbgv42tLDQCWkDPtX4b7E2V0irIN361iX03X0=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-4"},{"Name":"Hope Sanford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKTriqFKkFGKxQ4k2TRI-ggyCybnkiOQjQXsiptg6aWkudYFVAzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have to say, every step, from the initial phone call with David to getting the work done was a pleasure. I got texts so I knew when the plumbers, John and Dylan, were coming. They were very professional and easy to talk with, and explained exactly what they needed to do and where they'd have to cut into the wall. I put their card on my fridge- I have an old house and will need a plumber again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerry Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX47U8rxBVVRwcjhm_Agl6deaLJDWqL7fxGcl-_LS-aW7UXniUu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and excellent work!  Highly recommend Seattle's Plumbing.  They fixed an underground water leak and aslo replaced an unfunctioning earthquake valve on my gas line. Both quickly and expertly done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Rowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ93o6rBWOqk2giQxkBCyab380VFxlCDOkfNGI07dDkpAXo5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David is very professional, friendly and knowledgeable. Communication was easy and he was right on time. We had a great experience working with him and Seattles Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Craig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_WGQ2Ks2eyTsoBA-BPiL2udhPsHAoEE32ixL5u8oG4INx7eN9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David at Seattle’s Plumbing easily earned a 5 star review from us. He was able to respond quickly, was on time, friendly, professional and communicative. He took the time to answer all my questions and explained things in a detailed way that made sense to me as new homeowner. Priced very fairly as well. We will keep their number for any and all future plumbing needs. Thank you David!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID2p-zB5AkNk3E1K27AEPlKLBWNcuny1gWI8NKUxsnlLEQ1p4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the third time we’ve had the pleasure of working with David- the owner, and once again, the owner went above and beyond even after hours—to ensure everything was fixed properly. From sink plumbing repairs to bidet installations, and now repairing a leaking expansion tank, he has consistently delivered high-quality, reliable work.\n\nWhat truly sets him apart is his genuine commitment to customer satisfaction, his quick response time—even with a busy schedule, and the peace of mind that comes with a one-year warranty on his work.\nHighly recommended for anyone in need of trustworthy, professional plumbing services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Larson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMB8g_XX5VEwOorKvuxDpGCUvxbOjI2-a1gkP7CJlMx-SG_tTj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have had David, owner of Seattle’s Plumbing out twice to our home on different jobs and have been so impressed with the work he has done. David gave us different options for what needed to be done and explained the options thoroughly. The job got done when promised and how it was promised. We highly recommend Seattle’s Plumbing for any of your plumbing needs. You won’t be sorry!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
