erings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"JL C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAH-lPkxPfduBVbHAK0eKOXsgiN7UR6NQWPQ3G0ecF5bGoqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Fischer to do a plumbing inspection purely for peace of mind.  Travis was very thorough, going through a detailed checklist and talking through his observations and findings. Very informative. Answered all my questions clearly and pointed out options to tackling some current and future jobs. Both Travis and Calvin were professional and pleasant, and they assessed my plumbing from a homeowner's perspective which I greatly appreciated. Highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin Rees","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtYzUx5Vux225YiKIek55zSQWdsxGBs2EOtTot7-2WE67q8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fischer Plumbing is always the best!  Great service, fair pricing and quality work. Aaron Posey and Salvadore are top notch and we had the best experience with them replacing our water heater. They were extremely knowledgeable, friendly and got the job done quickly at the highest of standards. I can’t recommend Fischer, or them, highly enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CHRISTINA CEDERSTRAND","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAhmlRF9h0oLbpqXHni_ZUTb1-c3CNEqRaBP7Xp4ak_irAOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you so much! I highly recommend this company. Travis was fast and efficient and fixed my problem in a timely manner. He was full of good information, Which made me feel at ease and you could definitely tell he knew what he was doing.\nI will definitely be calling them for any future plumbing issues!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Warner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJq-prfX_b7oq6Gi-MFFkCv86w1mTNDW9MjiCc1J5i3tOSU2ZM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first experience with Fischer was fantastic. We recently purchased a dishwasher and the previous homeowner left us with a rather shoddy pipe setup in our kitchen. Salvador was incredibly professional, optimistic, and efficient. It went about as smoothly as one could hope for. We’ll certainly be calling Fischer again if we have any issues in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ana Cappelletti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf994xRFoLVP-TSelbAuZ9On1aT028kwT_bNB-8AYnj7ibxMFG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the best service from beginning to end. From Michelle in the office helping us secure a hot water tank and getting it to the warehouse for an early delivery and install. To Aaron and Fernando, all I can say is WOW! What great service. They explained everything and helped us in so many ways to make this an easy transition. We will never go anywhere else. Fischer Plumbing and Heating are the real deal. The owner knew what he was doing when he hired his employees. Thank you! We felt truly blessed by their great service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Audra Favini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW79LeMQLPcaM2O-SqedSFZao23ANHiQyw5TpaRAuUd59GdnJB5Sg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our 2nd experience with Fischer Plumbing. We had sewage back up into our shower and flood the bathroom floor. It was not great. Fischer had someone out within an hour. He was super nice, efficient and knowledgeable. At the end of a crappy, stressful situation we were just very appreciative of the level of care and service by all the folks at Fischer Plumbing. Noah, you were out here today!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bill Krippaehne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRr56PFGDw46SUaron5uoiuuyh7PvWtcVjvFK7EHw-j_GDxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Fischer Plumbing. Lost our plumber of 30 years due to retirement. Cedar at Fischer meets the requirements and couldn’t be better; he was prompt, highly knowledgeable and skilled. We recommend him without reservations.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth 9812","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3RlQINaJD5e42nD23FNBuy-K4onZiLfmEOYsLILMHwXVjEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Oct 28: Travis and Tyler did an amazing job installing a new kitchen faucet after I had to have my kitchen pulled out from a flood in February of this year. A very stressful experience for me, but they made it very seamless. I was anxious to move back in my condominium and they were extremely resourceful. There was an issue with the faucet I chose. Instead of having to have the entire condominium building water shut off , they used  their smarts and expertise to do a flawless installation!!\n\nThey also reinstalled my dishwasher and garbage disposal with no issues. Another local large plumbing service  told me that I would most likely have to replace  the brand new sink or have the plumbing valve lowered, which would’ve been a major expense for me.\n\nTravis and Tyler worked their magic and everything fit perfectly! They also rechecked my washer and dryer to make sure they were reinstalled properly and fully functioning.\n\nAfter experiencing a major flood and being without my home for So long, it was reassuring to have professionals in my home, reinstalling all of the plumbing to give me a peace of mind!\n\nLastly, both Travis and Tyler worked efficiently, were extremely friendly, engaging and all with the most professional standards.\n\nI would highly recommend them for any homeowner  or business!\n\nElizabeth","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
