ble seating","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Nandita Agarwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4CfXDfEObZ_xRY1aTLOX2wHuaDpYDO0-APPhuvLiXtE5MYB8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience working with Frank from Rooter Pal Plumbing to replace my water heater. I got quotes from multiple contractors but decided to go with Frank since he explained everything with a lot of detail and patience to make sure I understood what was needed. He was thorough, yet didn't overwhelm me with false information or try to oversell his services.\nIf you're looking to get your water heater replaced, look no further! You might get cheaper quotes from other companies but most of them are not licensed plumbers and use a cheaper brand of water heater. Rooter Pal installed a Bradford White water heater with brass fittings, which are way more durable than what the cheaper competitors use.\nHe was able to accommodate me in his schedule pretty quickly and made the whole process seamless. He even came back to replace an out-of-stock part free of charge. Rooter Pal will be my go-to for all my plumbing needs in the future.\nThank you doing a great job, Frank and Luca!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0uJeBcXfV9xC5I-WhmMtxy8T03bq1u8HCHIlAyO2Gtx3YMkh9g6pedMhFKJkT7J-YpeEwqpZc4sJg2CJapg9cDewAxYBu5fVIZX6I9txP01rkH6zdNFHSs2YQPRLcTIS6-Sz9Pptq6KLU=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-23"},{"Name":"Catherine Colio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz4jCN-8z7RD1gvMJ2UwNxmnc9qGtEi7jN-pb6JaQ59Y_Ghw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing from phone call to completion of work. Saturday afternoon we found water coming out of a landscaping wall. After utilities came and turned off the water, I found Frank on Google and gave him a call. He was nice and actively listened on the phone, then was even able to come early Sunday. Once seeing the issue, he was ready to get to work to try and get water back on for us as soon as possible. Due to some interferences they had to dig to try and locate the pipe, but not only did they work diligently, but they were very careful with the landscaping. To the point that they dug some plants and temporarily potted them to make sure they would still be healthy.\nEven after hours of digging, once they located the pipe leak, then quickly (and properly) fixed the pipe and started refilling the holes. They not only filled the hole, but nicely replanted the plants and left the area cleaner than they found it to the point of raking the dirt.\nHands down amazing people and work. And loved how they would explain things, in a way you know they know what they are doing.\nFrank and team, thank you again for your tireless work. You are all much appreciated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edhi Sarwono","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoMWxlyL8eBJjwsk_vUIVWOKISxq6Y8tssIIIJSXngjihQ1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rooter-Pal Plumbing is hands down the best plumbing company I’ve ever worked with. Frank and his team, especially Luca, are reliable, professional, and incredibly knowledgeable. Simply put — they are the only plumbing company for me.\n\nI first met Frank during an emergency back in December 2022 when a pipe burst in our garage on Christmas Eve during the snowstorm. In a panic, I searched Google for a plumber with great reviews, and Rooter-Pal came up. I called, and Frank immediately picked up. He asked me to FaceTime so he could see my water main and valves. Within seconds, he identified that it was the outdoor bib pipe that burst and guided me to shut it off. In literally five seconds, he solved what felt like a major disaster. I booked him right away to replace the pipe, and he did a fantastic job.\n\nFast forward almost three years later—I needed to replace my water main shut-off valve because the original builder had placed it right next to the HVAC vent, making it impossible to turn. I sent Frank a picture, and right away he noticed that my 22-year-old water heater was already leaking and way overdue for replacement. He and Luca came in, replaced the water heater tank, installed a new shut-off valve that I can easily turn from the garage, and even replaced a Delta shower cartridge for me.\nFrank is a true problem-solver, and both he and Luca take pride in their work. Every work they’ve done for me has been outstanding - efficient, thorough, and high quality. I will always call Rooter-Pal for any plumbing needs. Highly recommended! Thank you Frank and Luca!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-RPNlb9s4s1CJHSH0PF2wy1YhRmvDZHoZjrC2lPfJIUu3ishCcwdQMBWtmne2DLH9BVFTOFxazDTEWHy-8ouf9KWa3izH_wtRA7Z9sFLDSsnErTDfBLsmlBqitjGDeeB78gQDCz_lY-lG=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-11"},{"Name":"Ali Fozooni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIEOkoF-OWx8hmQMpr2cNVCUIgMkFPq2RIVdbZl8XrV5oA9cB4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an outstanding experience working with Frank and his team. From the first call, Frank was professional, responsive, and genuinely cared about solving the issue rather than just getting the job done quickly. He explained everything clearly, gave me an honest estimate upfront, and showed up right on time.\nThe work itself was top-notch. They diagnosed the problem fast, fixed it efficiently, and left the area cleaner than when they arrived. What stood out most was how respectful and friendly they were throughout the process, it’s rare to find that level of professionalism and courtesy these days.\nFrank clearly takes pride in his work and treats every job as if it were his own home. I’ve already recommended his company to a few neighbors and will absolutely call him again for any future plumbing needs.\nIf you’re looking for reliable, skilled, and trustworthy plumbers, I highly recommend Frank and his team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yama Rahmani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLp6xUsoXnai2sgKcbI7f9-v4OhW7Pk58BN_q7I7UjceJ-mIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"RooterPal Plumbing did an outstanding job replacing our recirculating pump in Kirkland. From start to finish, they were professional, punctual, and knowledgeable. The technician explained everything clearly, completed the installation quickly, and left the work area spotless. Our hot water is running perfectly again, and the whole process was stress-free. I highly recommend RooterPal Plumbing for anyone in Kirkland needing reliable plumbing service!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0EE5RnaO4QKxdD9LTwYJhyR8ZLM_kBZoBzjCmA82TcbBprXFyfS_v3HK7PCNqWAm8UmIyhiGsTMdjrlrP1Hmuf5IkSX_F8YiCKv8gAlKHBBqOnoZMksZ_8VSihcV8WyAkcmbPmfacv3Dc=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-3"},{"Name":"Laura Morgan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmjEJ6qSLi0fwUTgGeN9BCqofNMlIGsuiM8tf2XXUFTFmPkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frank and Luca provided excellent customer service for our septic plumbing issue. They were able to schedule us with same-day service which was a huge relief. They were super efficient, professional, and pleasant. They did a fabulous job and we highly recommend their services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"seattledrumguy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5uqfnjcu2mn75cPa5lKdo6N6M3wleBG6BPOWeI1QA06jERd8N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"1/25/2025 Update! My 2 year old Rheem water heater gas valve decided to croak on a Friday morning. It was going to take 2 weeks to ship me a new one and no local companies had one. Frank and Luca were awesome at advising me on the warranty process and ran down to pick up the replacement WH and got it installed before dinner! Once again excellent customer service, professionalism, honesty and follow through. Thank you RooterPal! My wife/life is happy again!\n\n——————-\n\nLuca and Frank were prompt and showed up on time. They aren’t the cheapest but weren’t the most expensive either. I had them install a utility sink in the garage and had them add a spigot to the outside of the garage. They did great work, great clean up and accommodated my schedule. Plus they offer a 1 year warranty on their work. Thanks guys!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jH4TfKygd4RMRBjDR0Zywg_hU5PWv3HJyhNtPS8juHkQRJPlkDTLAon68y3GWiuIJHHtKjXRGpYHcCQciSitB9jeTvWx_7cd6cmkEj5bv6eBk6t6ciYTIymbFNTTGxTjdHJiw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_NHbPiC68U04MvQnY8BTxyitYQfgGkqtmnvSP861nE5U8bU7yCsyOSlUtkDgkZQJr3GfqeKPCm0OpO1UiO_nqm-ffA6JCE5Bgi0sAbIvMRh38N-tJKoOa628S4reJM5VygUGBDg=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Eric Teece","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCJ_dGN6C7e5DUUZNPcH1UP4-RHY0QbIJLw8EYLgl3F1_TpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rooter-pal came, same day, to clear our kitchen drain. Communication, setting our expectations, work and cleanup all exceeded what we have come to expect from most contractors . We will not hesitate to recommend Rooter-pal to anyone we know, who needs a plumber!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
