ssional and friendly and explained what caused the problem and what they needed to do to fix it.  On top of that they were both very gracious as my kids asked them 1000 questions and kept wanting to show them their toys.  Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"stephanye smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLC9BK1ooZKCzHarrCtVB-UG6lOLgqMrehzVXW9811u81Kwuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Santino was amazing! He showed up right on time, was very professional, and I could tell when he was inspecting he knew exactly what he was doing. He walked me through everything that needed to be done and he gave me an excellent rate! My kitchen sink had backed up when my washing machine was going. He snaked the drain and cleaned up after he was done. He went above and beyond his duties by putting air in a flat tire I had on my truck this morning!! If you need a drain cleaning I would call these guys and ask for Santino!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brenden Narloch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrbIUW_1gpMG8JPf99XQDytbthMdLdu2_m0dRJEaPbi-nexHYl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an excellent experience. Steven was very easy to work with and had great knowledge. He fixed the problem quickly and was a great communicator as well. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Daniels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmHWzci8RDVv4RCKhoog0pOqV-ShhiOK8qdWNAia2xszrUyIHAgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a clogged kitchen drain that I couldn't clear. Called Roto-Rooter and had a capable technician named Toan (tech #6849) arrive at my house within a couple hours. He fixed the issue promptly and was pleasant to work with. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
