s://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdV8pSE09AuZxDp69Q4BwyVMwlj4T8qsouOhGlmgGpCA_-nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My driveway had a pool of water due to a clogged drain. I called on 2 plumbing company and both companies quoted more than $1200.00 to clean up the drain which I thought was too much. While I was checking the NEXTDOOR site, I came across numerous positive reviews on Farid and Washington Rooter. I called to inquire and he quoted $500 and was available same day. I was skeptical at first but when he got to my property, he presented himself professionally and confirmed the price after inspecting the drain. The inside of his van was immaculate and looked fully equipped. He worked on my drain and within 15 minutes, the water was draining. He also told me how to maintain the drain and where I could buy a replacement grill/cover. I am so impressed with Farid and called 3 of my friends to share my experience and his information. He is now listed as my go to plumber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"joeycscott71","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE6tkLEFQHLen-Pg25m_HZ6-OCuKrPjz2uRgtcar1N5zICZtV1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Farid went out first thing the next morning, after I contacted him. He unclogged the kitchen sink and provided recommendations for a repair in the line for a separate leak. Charged a reasonable price and no pressure for a larger scale job that is potentially needed. He knew what he was talking about,  I would definitely hire him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anne-Louise Lorentz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe_15_12DG-D45wFBSKpuI7dZ_EQC19_Ntnu_mX06SmrMGJDcp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Farid is great! Seems like an honest, hard-working man. Answered on the first call, got  immediate service. Cleared out a sewer drain very quickly. Saved us thousands by not having to replace the whole sewer line. I am relieved and very grateful. He will be my first call for any plumbing issues in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shalena Sequeira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlNUYQT13JNYfRmb8itWrO5HzpjmyfS1efuvcqV_sqBp4Cnd_OQw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very happy with their prompt and professional service getting one downspout unclogged using hydro jet. With all the rain we have been receiving, the water drains perfectly from the roof gutters. Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Calvin Lwin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjyuur-HkTVfbuKq3JhCtMOiDc-qPX9rnEN7PAwZYmV9x-cg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent, professional, and fast service.  Farid came out quickly to clear out a backed up downspout drain pipe that had been a problem for us last winter.  Used a cool hydrojet tool that blasted away debris, roots, and the blockage so we are now set for the Fall rains.  Will be calling him back next month for a water heater replacement.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
