C2winjUqOU3Is6reGslJw=w224-h367-k-no"},{"title":"Pipe","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAH7Edhhrc5LaTrz_Nef4hC8zrHKf-jJfCnyfIHGoByKbyNz7LXh3tssz7SHr0Ga3HJbLwTU5lfJcJD9uSLCGDGze-CH-A3Fr2GWR-41tl93seP0u2fU8JZKs4YRTckeTTaKH5kb=w232-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHaq2oiIBpLkDj5HUkbPNCxOeoEUcLhUEIzHlFP_qA5fJeOOvUOM6VEPGNa9O6nTPxJqYUeIHM3e7nkg3V6QBjAEkf_IQYPJj4mtyT1fhTgNg3QDDr0DFFhj5gmNV0JKFKuvrFg=w529-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"105010936096532263288","name":"Wolff Water Heaters LLC (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105010936096532263288"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"22521 Echo Lake Rd","city":"Snohomish","postal_code":"98296","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kevin Luk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEP1BnRwTqfZerj6b5AD5mdB90QB_KEcyDF5MqKC5fdrtjbTGs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam, Ben, Aaron, Holly and the rest of Wolff's team has been great to work with. They do great work and are transparent with their estimates for the job. They communicate well and are willing to teach you little things about your own home. They've earned our trust and we'll continue to go back to them for our heating and plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Benjamin Gay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGZtc7gZvCq_oY3r4sBHLG1kA0xXsE68CRRTGMPFJ6hRFrpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Wolff Water Heaters for a complex project involving the replacement of two water heaters, a sump pump, and the installation of a whole-home smart water shutoff system.\n\nThe Wolff  team demonstrated a high level of professionalism and expertise throughout the project. Adam, Aaron, and Ben were meticulous in their work, showing great attention to detail in every aspect of the job. They were communicative, clean, and respectful of our home, ensuring the project ran smoothly from start to finish.\n\nThe quality of the installation was excellent, and it was clear they take pride in their workmanship. The project passed its final inspection with flying colors, and the inspector made a point to comment on the quality of the work. He noted that the installation went above and beyond the requirements and was exceptionally well done. Receiving that kind of validation from a professional inspector provides incredible peace of mind.\n\nWe are very pleased with the outcome and would recommend Wolff Water Heaters without hesitation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Knm Anonymous","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRVxhygKPy3skXmANvwinxSEaud04c7vqHquHPzuqxHtnAT2gcjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ben is an absolute pleasure to work with! The company is super efficient at scheduling, providing estimates and getting the work done! They have earned my loyalty across two projects, a new water heater and a new hose bib. Already thinking of what other projects I can request their help with!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Huddleston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeMBf7-iWT22eZ_Z8WW7IigYmttw17JY4nMGIs92itaY9p1oSz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I could not be happier with Adam and Ben. They are quick to action and more than reasonably priced. Although they specialize in water heaters (hence the name), they are FULL SERVICE residential plumbers. Look no further.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl Kendrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdu9XY3kk5tOLRsl8PbuxVSyZ13J5P3tSXDBxfmE0PlKcgPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kitchen sink leaking turned into big problems, Wolff Water Heaters came out and helped me, having to make a few trips to repair and replace while the problems were getting resolved. So kind and helpful, I am so grateful\nThank you 🙏","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2wzx3xJen_ya9V0xUgf6sfmA27Vrhz4oxrSj2HiuL-ctZTlNsPT2viPDB676pEuDE0pz9LvjCDH9oZow4E7A_JK9I2jWSH-DLdjZq_tc6i1yLNZqC25W_gbGLHrrfYnIhu_pSW=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-26"},{"Name":"Daniel Jankovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXI6wwt_V51VUxnhDj7CgyyEq_Ljdid5AhTVDNeZ4J5eHuEhzppA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent and trusted! We have cats and they did some serious work for us (Expansion Tank, Pressure Release Valve, Replace lots of old valves and piping etc.) and they did it professionally while making sure our cats don’t escape. Super friendly, hard working and affordable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Graeme Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVGOxDaNx8WhgtZdrOw4uh2dQITgQ2vA26r1m1Qemn7EVpQK5I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A little back-story: The previous owner of our home had been leasing a water heater, and we had to take over the lease when we purchased our home a few years ago. We've had nothing but problems with the water heater and had to call the leasing company 2-3 times per year to come out and fix issues. Some repairs were \"beyond the scope of the lease\" so we repeatedly had to pay a lot out-of-pocket. Well, last week, the water heater went out again (pilot light wouldn't stay on). Called the leasing company, and they sent out a repair technician. The technician ultimately decided that the entire system hadn't been set up correctly in the first place and said we'd have to rip the whole thing out and go with a \"power vent\" heater and quoted us an astronomical price. We decided to dump the lease and just go with an entirely new system with a different company.\n\nI did some research and found Wolff Water Heaters came highly recommended through our neighborhood Facebook group. I called them, and they were so quick to jump into action. They were so friendly and helpful, and had a technician out to our house that day. I peppered him with all sorts of questions about tankless, power vent, etc. The tech was such a knowledgeable and friendly fellow and even called manufacturers to ensure that the system would work for us.\n\nThey provided us two different quotes on the spot, which were \"all inclusive\" and was less than the leasing company's plumbing tech's quote. We signed the contract, and they were out the next working day (happened on a Friday, they were there Monday). They were on-time exactly when they said they'd be, called beforehand to confirm their arrival, and explained everything they were doing.\n\nThey were done in six hours, and we have a brand new tankless water heater setup that is phenomenal! They cleaned up after themselves, and the work is incredibly professional.\n\nI highly recommend Wolff Water Heaters!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IxRe0RF218LrOkaQFWRRk3WUYPzbe2LJtOiHP5MoC6bLeYkLpEUqIB6P-vxYRHgxHZsKnF8Vm1i-gtns5uQ-6trBGUQXJsA73ni6dLPr8E--RQbYevN1Pc0JkSuA_n1UPJ4bhFQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Tana Ingersoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtVaHJ0VMTvHHshciVKg0mss1SJwAfL1kvDJBrdoS-1TMGhCt6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam Wolff installed our tankless Navian Water Heater in 2017 and his team continues to provide the best service, taking great care of our unit.  They are prompt, thorough and professional in all ways.  Highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
