ccessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":false},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":false},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rany ElHousieny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1yvSA4kJhyWjVDOM_XfYlx3IA5FPJ7drDLokgKz_sCou9bh5W=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Outstanding Plumbing Work, Honest, Professional, and Truly Above \u0026 Beyond\n\nI had JD Plumbing \u0026 Fire Protection come out for a very difficult plumbing issue at my home, and I honestly cannot say enough good things about the experience. This was not a simple “quick fix” job, it was one of those frustrating problems that requires real expertise and patience.\n\nFrom the moment the plumber arrived, he was professional, knowledgeable, and extremely thorough. He took the time to explain what was going on, walked me through the options, and then executed the repair with care and precision. He didn’t rush, didn’t cut corners, and made sure everything was working perfectly before leaving.\n\nWhat impressed me most is that he treated the situation like it was his own home. Clean work, great communication, and very high integrity. His pricing was far lower than other estimates I received, and he even took care of additional work at no extra charge just to make sure everything was fully resolved and I was satisfied. That level of integrity and customer focus is rare.\n\nIf you’re looking for a plumbing company you can actually trust, that shows up, does the job right the first time, and handles hard problems with professionalism, I strongly recommend JD Plumbing \u0026 Fire Protection. I will definitely be using them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robbie S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQFmihXZH39zOLE0uq9ehoyKLCualgZ75ylcZIp-Im0HxdBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Osvaldo and his team were great. Quick communication, arrived on time and were honest in billing. The work was easier then they expected and they charged me significantly less then the estimate. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyAoT279CC0lUYIYIIkpMjBiMEIz9mFNv1W6RqOZTxpASZ2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After several plumbers were unsure how to handle our root issue, we found Osbaldo and his crew. They arrived on time and quickly assessed the situation. Unlike others, they confidently tackled our challenging problem with a straightforward, cost-effective solution.\n\nThe team was knowledgeable and professional throughout the process. They explained everything clearly, provided a fair price, and completed the work efficiently. The quality of their work was excellent, and they kept the work area clean.\n\nOsbaldo and his crew were friendly, respectful, and clearly know their trade well. We're completely satisfied with the results and wouldn't hesitate to use their services again.\n\nHighly recommend for any plumbing needs - especially the tough jobs that others shy away from.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Flohrs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhm9q_PvCLOHAWfCE2-oSRxuVtcxFHq1XIq9zdTYd6GFp2Lf8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my second go around with JD Plumbing and Osbaldo Del Real is just as his name sounds. He’s a real guy that understands the customers needs and sometimes urgent requirements. I had an expansion tank bladder rupture that twisted and snapped my cpvc pipe and within minutes I had the water off and dried up, but not able to use water. Within hours he had a guy there and it was repaired within the hour and Osbaldo was communicative with the tech and myself the entire time. Quick response, with honest and knowledgeable team members, it couldn’t have gone any better. This will NOT be the last time I use this team and I highly recommend them. Can’t select both, but it was great and reasonable pricing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicki Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgPCVgUSy_CRV7k2GY9va3tj1DMCyL9LnmgX_49fxt1HrkIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Osbaldo by a very happy customer - lucky me!  He was very responsive to my needs, extremely prompt, friendly, and professional service.  He is now on my speed dial!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vessie Djambazova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS2LLJjhSVcZDtZUCXOqVpHBOQbz0E_lP1Mh3SGQ8lBeceQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really happy with work done by JD Plumbing\u0026 Fire Protection.\nFast and high quality work with lower end estimates.\nI highly recommend this company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beau Jenkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHm_qZT0tn-jcTcYEEp3v6leb2tKvMdjV5w0fhNXYq7YtypQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place has the worst service I've ever experienced and over charged me by almost double the estimate. Stay clear!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D. Eric Stephen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUktrMsK-m21H0xUf3-gx3VS9F7hubUA-lIZk3oucSgaFm5ABQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"wasnt yesterday. was this day 9.1.20 talked about work \u0026 the lack thereof","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
