ty was in our house he was always respectful. He completed the job quickly and other than a new furnace and his card left no trace of his visit. If we require any future plumbing or water work we will be requesting Monty for the work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZNpRaoXzcEKkLvbSHX7ibP4vL4GT_61_tLd3mhUICBkdXxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Monty replaced my main water valve and hot water heater, along with repairing leaks. He's professional, patient, and clearly explained his actions. He dealt with challenging, unexpected pipe configurations at my home and difficult clearance in my closet for the hot water heater. Thanks to him for positive experiences with these projects! I'm so relieved to have a main water valve that easily works now.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mads K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS-FRxVhNvFOL9o3hLnI3Ft7ydqAZM46RktHVTAObZ3Z79pSw-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Folks, do yourself a favor and go with Craftsman for your plumbing needs. Cameron arrived on time, was extremely courteous and fixed a whole host of plumbing issues quickly and without (like their ads say) mansplaining! Communication with the team was also very easy and they were able to accommodate me quickly. Highly recommend. Deserving of 6 stars tbh.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Busch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx6F8EZg4Ju7MrYi84X9PYXbu9MEG9T0c8HXeqrLEE5Q41_4Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cameron was outstanding—his explanations were clear and thorough, and his attention to detail was second to none. Another great experience with this company. You can tell they operate with a high level of integrity. Craftsman will always be my first call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Neitzel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI224Im_HRhCjxISc-o6JHl