/ACg8ocKfuOjteyPAYjTr2dwjp9HfjD-egv1E6Dx-TKQCIk5KDITm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience while working with ProMax Water Heaters \u0026 Plumbing was fantastic. I had them re-pipe our commercial building. The process from the very start was above my expectations. Todd was quick to respond and had clear communication throughout the process. Evan and his crew did a great job. Their support and understanding the need to be flexible and work side by side with our tenants was greatly appreciated in keeping distractions to a minimum for our tenants. I highly recommend them and they will definitely be our go-to plumbers for our business and home needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ed Blakely","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqQC8iAUw39ywqBRuDWb_nRL8q0KmJqnDxJdMtmGNomkxu66WN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Evan and Owen upgraded our old leaking water heater to a larger size to better support our household.  The quote from Todd at ProMax was accurate to the final cost, comparable to other options, and I was happy to be able to support a local small business!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2OsUIpOPATDNmYwQsM8towZa9zDc_0BwdVb15ZxdaCQjC0fKSEki3NAn8TsZ8EUodKpTUa9bCTR_EiMuchvBCvKKNuCmRzRf5_5EhUvkdgmkjKxoxBXvLDAKzmElEb3-ryf1cx6NsAuxCJ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pdDyvcYv4nWq-UqXsALKot5rqxKexvTGfPxGgi-ymGiDiqrx85eX87KKCgB-CSAoUNBF0O938TAHRIH1aSIVjs18mvtXqO_PU5wobKEB-mEzvm3l4rkQrDlbriGu9nCd9zGm5NDaG_w8f=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-24"},{"Name":"Tanya Grant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2xITBSWpNtnfauhdd7YVgUv2huozIUlqxXuSat4n7rmwtz5I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These ProMax guys came out to run propane line for a generator install. They gave a significantly better price than the local plumbers I’ve worked with previously on projects. The staff were authentic, friendly, and so knowledgeable that they g