ogleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKkee3gZ48cTEPqN9l2dlA5fZC_wCf0yVJ7OPTO4JAIvnoWggKwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my outdoor faucet hose bibb replaced and installed in a new location. Very impressed with protocol plumbing professional friendly service. Thank you Eric and Zachery for your awesome help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdZvfzpeBwO15GibF1jkje7AQy0FHd-6s0AwJIi1PRtgm-WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"WOW!  We were referred to Protocol Plumbing by a friend of ours and what a great referral it turned out to be!!   I called on a Friday and was greeted by a very friendly and knowledgeable gentleman who after listening to my problems, offered to send someone out that day!  I wasn't prepared for an appointment that quickly, so we settled on the following Monday at 8:30 AM.  Zach called me at 8:10 AM Monday morning to let me know he was on his way.  8:30 AM on the nose and Zach is at my front door.  Another extremely friendly knowledgeable guy.  I explained my issues to him and provided my unsolicited \"DIYer\" thoughts on what the causes might be.  He listened to me very patiently and then promptly started his own investigation. About 20 minutes later, he found the problem (not even close to my guess), recommended a solution and made the repairs.  Problems solved!  He came in with the bill and I was pleasantly surprised at what I considered to be an extremely fair price.  More than fair if I'm being completely honest.   I will never use another plumber again... NEVER!!!  Thanks again Zach and everyone at Protocol Plumbing!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerry Stuesser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_kwOcQWnbPFvoOBbdSgCHE9luX70CVvfU5AXJAe4XhqPi8Ho=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Protocol did a great job fixing my main waterline leak under my driveway. Had the right know-how, tools and parts. Kyle and his assistant worked continuously until the repair was made. I appreciated that they willing to do the messy uncomfortable work in the hole and on their stomachs and did so cheerfully. Fair prices. Would definitely call Protocol again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zAiJltPSd53bdM12p84TsH3QJt1r3CnCXI13AOKUQncU5VIAcdxzx87Lsm_J4ilLp6DLfvu2b-9wPVS-4hVvByQw9M6JO5w6U4cAo-noegA9pD2Zkc6KJQARCQeikBrceYuVL=k-no"],"When":"2021-2-9"},{"Name":"Alisha Clogston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8DzdCaQq0DXcHRb1ZbC1OIxQGCwgrq-wj_P4EkhPEMxkf1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible experience with this company. Met with sales rep Kathy in their showroom and was very excited to pick out my fixtures. The most important things to me was having a touch start kitchen faucet, and I have two faucets in my kitchen (3 total with laundry room). Kathy priced everything out and sent it to me. I went to pay and the ACH function on their system wasn’t working. Due to this delay, I started researching prices on the internet. Come to find out Protocol was marking up my fixtures between 40%-70%, and there were other items (material) that were marked up over 100%. This didn’t sit right with me, so I decided to purchase the EXACT same fixtures myself and have them do the installation. When I ordered the fixtures, I copied and pasted the model numbers provided by Kathy. I didn’t want to risk me typing it in wrong. Skip toward the end of trim, and my kitchen faucets weren’t working with the touch. I spoke to the plumber on-site so he could get it working, and he told me that they are standard faucets, not touch. I reached out to the owner Erich and Kathy to inform them of this error, hoping they would make it right. Their response is they’ll get the touch faucets for me at full cost-plus extra time and material for the installation. I also got the extra gift of the foreman Mike yelling at me telling me that it’s my fault. I should have paid for their markup, and to sum it up, I should have been double checking all their work. So much for trusting a professional. My advice, if you don’t want to pay for their extreme markup, go somewhere else for installation. No customer service to customers who don’t purchase fixtures from them.\n\nThey still need to install my bath tub that I’ve already paid for. We’ll see how that goes. I’ll post pictures when completed.\n\nI've worked with many contractors on my project and haven't had any problems, except Protocol.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edith Lind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW213XSfT4FXOSyxoir8SdkiWr49MEw1610Oa348GaOVEE0yue7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When we discovered a slow, hidden leak, I remembered how impressed we'd been with Protocol Plumbing for an under-sink repair years ago. Fortunately they are still in business - and still excellent! James and Nate came out the day after I called. They were skilled, friendly, and careful of our home. They spent over 3 hours fixing the leak, testing the repair, and discussing our next steps. (AND putting in a new garbage disposal, as ours started making a racket 2 weeks earlier.)  Stressed by the leak discovery, I expected more stress from the bill. I was instead very relieved at the very reasonable cost!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Christensen1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOSDvEAi65lHYrgU5z2AhJ6zuexgy_UO4UqIVXtPfBQaOzYYhtsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Called them today. They had someone in the area. He showed up in about 30 minutes. Was professional, friendly, and efficient.\n\nHe fixed the issue I called about, and fixed something my wife was worried about, and also fixed two issues that have been driving me nuts for a few years.\n\nI found the price per hour to be acceptable, and the technician, Zack, to be professional and top-notch. I will definitely use them again when and if needed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynn Treseler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWna0zso3ilqjVMnMv0CsTFo6n0LoHWsVe5gdhfkuxkbN8eD1_FOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used this company for many years. They are prompt, do excellent work, and are reasonably priced. Today Zach fixed my leaking kitchen faucet and did other plumbing tasks -all in one hour. He was efficient and took the time to answer all of my questions.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
