,"When":""},{"Name":"Elgroup.design","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_A_lE8q5JR7D1iHEuQ0BSFYG4_Vs9v4lK1yCHBySRU1zOJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Kirkland Rooter! Shamim and his team helped me fix a leak quickly and professionally. They were friendly, honest, and their price was very good compared to others. They also left everything clean. I really appreciate their work and would definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dana Hedlund","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfRQd9HDt-TKf9RumsrFjDVRXZpymezxh13y-fiG6Dh82a1Zmt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently used Kirkland Rooter to fix a toilet and sink issue.  We chose them because they were a local business and they have great reviews.  We were NOT disappointed!  They were responsive and timely.  Our plumber, Milad, was professional, knowledgeable, and kind.  Their customer service was top rate and they were very concerned with making sure we were satisfied with the results.  We are very glad we used them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adriana Serrano Guemez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpwDsD5ga4Lt5NdXkf_gq1Jaq05vLh02cDKn5Laj9K2So-eQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently experienced a serious plumbing emergency, and I cannot recommend Kirkland Rooter highly enough. From the moment I called, the response was phenomenal—he was at our door in literally minutes, which is exactly what you need in a crisis.\nThe job itself was complex, but Shamim diagnosed and fixed the issue with speed and professionalism. He clearly knows his stuff and didn't waste any time. If you need reliable, fast, and highly skilled plumbing service, especially for an emergency, this is the one to call. Five stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liam Aliporyan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmzeMtBFMDndacGYzGQv1OfYvCpeuXLDv9ZezbyHwQuGbsmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with Kirkland Rooter. Shahim and his great team even came late at night when I really needed help and took care of my job with professionalism and care. They were fast, efficient, and very knowledgeable. It’s rare to find such a reliable and hardworking team. If you have any plumbing problems, make sure to call them , they truly will go above and beyond for you. I’m extremely satisfied and will definitely call them again for any future plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Effie Soroor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhh6TSKFnLI0vKe_nflXnbXpYUU_S19HwcUrwCGfBA-MOpDkK0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our plumber was absolutely fantastic! He arrived quickly, diagnosed our badly clogged kitchen sink right away, and explained everything in clear detail so we understood exactly what was going on. He was extremely professional, respectful, and truly went above and beyond.\n\nAfter comparing many businesses, his pricing was by far the most reasonable — and the quality of his work was exceptional. He fixed the issue efficiently and left our home spotless, which we really appreciated.\n\nWe will definitely be using him again for any future plumbing needs. Outstanding service from start to finish!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Snap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOKJerGaWVKtTTeyHhXcf7R01eOtudy4BRfY2SYyyj3PqH6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shamin was prompt, courteous, and fixed exactly what we needed. He gave us a quote before arriving and didn't change it after finishing. And it was on Saturday night. We needed additional service couple of days later, and Milad came over and also did a great job.\n\n100% recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R. Ryan Sadeghian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZhLNVvE3xRN1TMixkocEWFlIAXg_zr4i6eHHfFt7tpFFHhX