es people but don’t deliver. But it’s really the people that are friendly, humble, direct, do the work themselves, and are available to answer questions without making you feel dumb for asking. Eddie at PuroClean is that guy!!!! Unfortunately, I had two water situations at the same time (shower leak due to bad plumbing job and a refrigerator leak due to my bad water filter install..). I called and Eddie came and inspected right away, and was super thorough. He told me what likely happened, what to expect with their process, got me an estimate quickly, and came and did the work himself. He was efficient, thorough, and he was always available when I called for additional questions and advice afterwards. I can tell he’s not the type to upsell unnecessarily but tells it like it is. And also not trying to pull one over on me because I’m not a dude, which I have sensed from others. I really appreciate that.\n\nHe’s the definition of above and beyond and made me a customer for life (hopefully not too many more issues!).  Thank you so much!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ueoAtSvp8cRjBrA2P8yeAusYDfRPsesmpt8dsvZC89iZDHEf0-zu9LD4nNknIEsqif9C1BqfoR3r_addvrE1NelMWKEQNNecn-zv8-dltD2oEKz5nWlycSNENEJBVz5TtL8ldEQd8JUyE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0d0f4S63jrJSLk-tjmFE-9PtMeq47LlQmEEkm4nHaPrQY7yV2Z6zTwdqFD6fjtzkplBuZqbT7592wCMRSg4BT99fAFK9lyLX89JlH_LAeDWd-idbL1dS1Q1I5Tmj8ynkNb1xr_zhoCpNqY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0U3WmXhiHanW25ztEu8KXsefMc5nPQfQC1wJI_3TTaxcDn5fSut3AxwiQv_wf0rk25n_XmhdvCwgYxmL3CnhfET4zC-061CXedu7v7lb9pvtBy70bfNY96OGtIEyHXxoGMrO5-AQ6UT7KT=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-3"},{"Name":"Sue Griffith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWKo0XuEpnOMcUYIXY6eFGhvQUblOizwhsPYhZrzedrZLK_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Never received documentation on recommendations. No take down of drywall and no removal of carpet and padding. Only dried out areas. New contractors estimate was 6,000 above Pureclean estimate. Having difficulty with Insurance now. Due to incorrect assessments. No furniture moved to do replacement with carpet. Ask for couches to be moved to other area. This did not happen. Disappointed.  Should have used Servpro!!! Which I had previous experience with in 2013. Unable to assess until after contractor did evaluation and saw mold under carpet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Tanabe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxtOSS8YqowiPHvC-qrIXm4eGUHHn8rCh-xv-5wBPHOivE0yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The entire crew that came to support my remediation was nothing short of AMAZING—from Wendy who did the initial call, contracts, and follow up, to Eddie who did incredible inspection work and explained everything every step of the way (always available by phone, too), to Stephanie and David who also went the extra mile to ensure the job was done right and done fast. I highly—like Mt. Everest highly—recommend them. I hope I never have water damage again, but if I do, I know who to trust and who to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Naomi vanTrump","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuYWfQ--99EXLEQBnr7brql4NzPIYHmAqv0BzaE4ITvWvmSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly impressed with their website. Every question I had was already answered on their website. It was thorough, informational and more. I would 100% remember them and call if/when I find myself needing any of the services they provide. No question I had was left unanswered just from their website alone. Impressive. Makes me believe they know their business and how to help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaylee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpI12Vy5vYlLdWHBAK9CeAHwNkyZmO6Bx8nG3Rq8tDCb6Fa8aNhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Truly outstanding company, that goes above and beyond for their customers. Pros in water, fire, and mold damage. Transparent, compassionate, flawless work.\nHighly recommend 👍🏻—they saved our home and our sanity!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Meryl McQueen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc1LsjLJunZoQJt6Oug8AM-Mt63rJHsSfUkAhcKoHfFA-WQ9Sykg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding team! Heri and Tristan came out and did a thorough assessment of the damage. They were both knowledgeable and efficient, explaining the process and outlining how the work would be done. The estimate was fair and comprehensive. Wendy in the office as helpful and friendly. A great team focused on getting the job done right with terrific customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damon Binder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPcuE8dKe2HdFEkq5ds_lDB_kd027BdbUzaLoSuotO2Zbhhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We Had PuroClean handle the Water clean up from our home. I was impressed how quick they were to get on site and completed the remediation.\nWe are Remodelers by trade and to be able to partner with other companies to keep jobs on time is essential.\nIn this case it allowed us to keep helping our clients why The PuroClean team got in and got done what they needed to.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cIqxAevac9Kwn2g8cTWOwT8fbze3iVtO86sXRZaDrloZLCWOalUSCo9gByyxsaSb4NGLJV1X2W1HVvGKJois_yFw7Y_3a1G2zmepnCFV3HBXNc4vWeT2WLM9yl69mvb4FMkHWtQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17BT_mvS8UIWO7TJ-kq2a_xxgKF0cx42vN3_zblSuHa8hzYTRVexSLkEqXtvRbcOwoS5dL37VUK84xVN3JubAxpFgRwU_DzWKko3WNY9KYSTsVbXab4MYFni76G5QZSZuiwAZ7=k-no"],"When":"2021-11-23"},{"Name":"Ria Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_s6DfNGMxhXmyTNhM2guOA3iH1j62h4CHvkiXTW3xe3Pmcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a water leak issue in the kitchen a couple weeks ago, and was informed water mitigation action is needed right away. Fong and his team came and did a complete check for kitchen, first floor, dry wall and crawl space. They provided a quick plan to dry wherever got impacted, and dried everything in less than two weeks.\nThe team is kind professional and helpful. It’s a pleasure to do business with them!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tV_uKWF_zl4EV0bavSFtOgEq-ZTdUZDnBQS-DkJa8cJsFJm3n1WgUnjHqHVMJ6mieNMjIzBJSmo6lWaGNlm3pCa_r3qyGzfvzJXhdpU8_H4LzSssajgctp3OeENuyk4ZF90zi=k-no"],"When":"2021-8-31"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
