 major leak due to sub-par plumbing work done by another company. Jim Dandy’s team came in and assessed, diagnosed and resolved the issue quickly and competently. Very professional, kind and communicative. Would HIGHLY RECOMMEND!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rhetta Fisk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDFgCV0bvlWSCleYRS38-nYq54BU40GxF2a3uYL_wnxtZJXRk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thorough checking and found the problem(s) with leaking toilet and small part for dishwasher in kitchen. Replacement for three pumps et al were available. Could have done it today but I needed to coordinate one of the repairs with MIL tenant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anuj Surana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkusmnftj6dKHgiW3EA9RU5tClgKktLCYozKndODRsCfsQp6yt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in promptly and available on Sunday when we had a water leak in our home. Plumber was extremely knowledgeable and courteous and was able to quickly figure out problem and refer us to a water damage restoration company. He himself made the calls and asked them to come take a look. Overall a wonderful experience and definitely will hire them again for any plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Lippert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDfjntEyDTCtqJx0YHB5cqG6YMq2JK3LYJlwZ2NL0SQdlFeT4r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a mainline blockage that needed repairs and Jim Dandy was a life saver. Shane came out on Saturday and was knowledgeable and shared every step of the process with us. When it turned out to be more than originally quoted for reasons of our older home, they shared options and solutions. Manuel came out the next day and after making the necessary repairs we shared thatbwe had shopped there pricing and that they were competitive with other local companies. They were appreciative, professional, and respectful. Great company and great employees, Manuel and Shane were great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K Walden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXClbXJyPd_-5f5RwBU0tu4XI9kEyKFkMgt9TZp_7G5aITfd7GJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needing a plumber is such a dreadful feeling but the service we received was a big relief! Alexander arrived promptly and explained his course of action after I showed him the gross results of our sewer backup. His work was thorough, he was honest and transparent with costs and he got it all done quickly. I really appreciated that he cleaned the entire area and is just a super nice guy! The whole process ended up being a positive experience. Totally recommend JDS\u0026P and Alexander.\n\n***** Another 5 stars! Adding to my review - after the above service I asked for a water heater check and was able to get my old one replaced with a much more efficient modern water heater same day. I was very happy with Manny’s advice, detailed explanations, and his work. He gave me a great price for a quality product and exceptional work. Glad to have used Jim Dandy again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nancy oblanas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQ5qU_CkHUBgC6Nsk7dtRGEemrG557yRJyA8P8dEEFduWhlw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jairo is an OUTSTANDING man. He is one of the few people who took the time and explained my issue. He deserves a raise 😀😀 Nancy Oblanas","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvw8l7qP4cu1qJNJEfOXCAzSPRiLizSd9XdIZuz0Bhdzon10wi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Top notch crew was sent to my house to tackle some plumbing issues including main water line replacement, drain clean out and inspection and rebuild of washer ptrap. This crew was seriously on their A game and I never doubted anything they said. The plan was clearly laid out and communication was constant thru the entire process. The guys are clearly a team that works well together. Yoesef was the team apprentice, I can confidently say he will do big things in life based on his work ethic, honesty and charismatic personality. Jim Dandy is lucky to have him aboard. Alexander went above and beyond to fix my washer drain. His approach was as if it was his own drain. I was so thankful to be in good hands. Chucks attention to detail and clear explanation of what the project entailed also made me feel like I was well taken care of. Ferris was the lead on the waterline replacement. There was a clear understanding of what was taking place the entire time. Ferris made sure I was totally satisfied and happy before they left. These young men are a shining example of how a crew should work. They treated my house as if it was their own and I couldn't be more happy with the clean work that was done. Thank Jim Dandy team!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carole Schroeder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQyjvf2MDfKiXy6OQi49LDTbOy-5I4gUHKTxhNIekjj9Nmpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"prompt, kind, always solve my plumbing problem quickly, clean up, easy to schedule and price is fair.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
