-UjUJ-PZfMlSFifAdZ7kL7x07jjL2zFYw60Y0yTn816XYTLmz93Cwog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From Taylor in the office, Heather and Shane during the pre bid inspection, and then Tate and Brian for the removal of my old galvanized piping and it's upgrade, A-List plumbing was enjoyable to work with. They arranged for the dry wall to be patched and painted after the plumbing project was completed and included that work in the bid so I didn't have to interview contractors separately for that portion of the project. The only thing that could have gone more smoothly was if I would have had more prior notice of the date and time for the dry wall work. The drywallers even placed the cover on the newly installed Ox box in my garage as that was overlooked at the finish of piping installation project. I will definitely recommend your company to others!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joshua Kelley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1m1NGn6jGLuiT8X7-vF9mp0B0Lzn10Co-cagNYVZcMmOxZdAi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bryan at A-List Plumbing did an excellent job replacing our toilet flange and installing the new toilet here in Everett, WA. He showed up on time, explained everything clearly, and worked efficiently. The new flange was installed perfect, the toilet sits solid with no leaks, and he left the area spotless when he was done. It’s great to see someone who takes real pride in their work. I’d definitely recommend Bryan and A-List Plumbing to anyone in the Everett area needing reliable, quality plumbing service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg Belvill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlLcd3nGe9XVMzFAWGmGNx5VcbWyIFCZj1Zz9wk1UnTbTxrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bryan from A-List Plumbing is very professional, courteous, and a nice guy! He did a fantastic job taking care of a plumbing issue underneath my kitchen sink. Thanks a again Bryan for your help and A-List for sending him…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deanna Mang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbm7ddpFYLTXq63W9vr2tNWBpo9dIVGm-7WwA2dlcm3O9tBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was a delivery day for our new refrigerator. Today was the day that we learned that Lowe’s does not deal with copper piping so I in the past at a salon I worked at used services before and now have tried them out for residential. I got very lucky. Taylor was really nice on the phone and we were willing to wait it out until Monday however, our technician Kate finished up a job and headed right over. He was able to get our water main shut off to the house because we were not sure if there was a valve to turn off the water on the refrigerator And handled so much more in one visit with us. It was well worth the job scope and fair on the pricing, I cannot recommend this family owned company and I hope that they can meet your business and residential needs in the near future","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Hammond","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtuFmKG78_5kP1I8n6Cyf0NZcM3bPUmAEe4sxVbXxtUJTXZEUS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone that I talked to at A-list plumbing, was great to work with. Our technician Tate was super respectful and resolved our issue promptly and went above and beyond for us. I would highly recommend Tate and A-list plumbing and will absolutely use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy Unan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvlmWk1ZtflCk8AvUgBZ6Sl2L_eoMIYH5eM2vtGNiAR2kN3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brian was knowledgeable and skilled.  He spent hours troubleshooting our  slow moving drains in a house that unexpectedly had one cleanout filled with cement!  He spent the time needed, provided careful analysis, provided info and education at every juncture, and provided excellent service.  Thankyou to Brian and A-list.  Integrity and honorable service.  We cannot thank you enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthelle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpFOGMX-ctemYnBc6ClRxkEc98R4HNRmPqOaMJ0wV4gdqDNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jason did a fine job resolving a leaking u set-sink pipe in the kitchen. There was a hole in the galvanized pipe that he was able to remove and replace with an ABS fixture. I am glad I did not try to snake the thing myself and instead relied on the professionals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Drummond-Hay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4prFlSSH7FdX6wCCchXIS2fygx_wHhlF1lEP-fWGMY2O274iM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jason is reliable and friendly and will return again next week to fix a few faucets. I trust the work A-List does","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
