,"enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mark Northrup","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCtPLxy1y8l4DaGTs-s7VVAYlURo_Y6Wg_ISUq00JpBJxReQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Johnny with Tech City was great.  He arrived at our home promptly as scheduled and finished our job within 30 minutes.  Throughout his work, he was professional, friendly, courteous, and skilled at the task at hand.  From our initial call to Tech City, our project was completed within 36 hours.  Very reasonable price for the service we received.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nilanka Kuruppu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkP9L-IjjYvUtEyYFv21bXrBNXuHVkn2Ks5Tj2OKc7MaOsJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I  live in Mill Creek WA and recently had a water heater installation done by Tech City Plumbing Kirkland, and the service was excellent from start to finish. Justin was the technician who completed the installation, and he did an outstanding job—professional, knowledgeable, and very thorough. Everything was installed perfectly, and he took the time to explain what he was doing and how everything works.\n\nA special thanks to Elvis, who first introduced me to Tech City Plumbing and guided me through the process. His communication and customer service were top-notch and made everything smooth and stress-free.\n\nI highly recommend Tech City Plumbing, especially Justin and Elvis, for anyone needing quality plumbing service. Great company, great people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Cole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEaTNxUeN55jzATfSG0TWqnLSKDaZtVsIMp5jv1GTZmoZF7pH8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Elvis and the plumber Justin were great. Easy and friendly process for me from estimate to completion and testing of finished work. Incredibly knowledgeable, proactive, timely, and diligent. I believe I paid for quality and received it, would hire again and recommend to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randy Reeves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnJnzkD4zWpMwj3iuR2zkDosgLJNkfHHBiSi5OOyDhY7d-wdX7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Johnny with Tech City Plumbing is an amazing guy and plumber. Just a shout out to him and the quality of his work and character. I have worked with many plumbing contractors over 41 years of my real estate practice and Tech City Plumbing is the best. Best quality work, value, and service. Honest. Efficient. Great people. I can't say enough good things about them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gail Round","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTLukFtLWbtKsNfGJ0MS29uxskhmCVl4cseHiyqlpCq2y1wf0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jesse did a great job fixing my disposal!  The replacement was done quickly.  All my questions were answered professionally.  I will be calling Tech City again in the future if additional work is required.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Buyco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxlOsGQIv_jjKryejQ6NfxYWxJXUeGd4j7Ow8QQUmfWuytsjar=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience getting our garbage disposal fixed. The technician arrived on time, diagnosed the problem right away, and had it working again in no time. They were polite, knowledgeable, and left the area clean when they finished. And they didn’t charge us! Definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISy6BwoWiSlgB5bVHtreuHDWRpPGhfjGzxO6bYgiKoeXI27A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Johnny from Tech City Plumbing came out to replace my garbage disposal which was leaking, on  October 24th, 2025, and he did a great job. He was kind, knowledgeable and quick. He also had a great sense of humor which helps when you're having a plumbing issue. It works great now with no leaks. I would definitely hire him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Crawford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX91xz7c__dM1sEFgB1N8eUvR50a4tBtNAz0Ly3AhSWsHR-KjlU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had a leaky toilet. Tech City was initially helpful. The price to remove and inspect the toilet was $450 (which I paid). The initial appointment was \"free,\" but to \"inspect\" it was $450. I already figured this would be the case so I paid no problem. The leak caused damage to the flooring which I removed so that the flange could be replaced/repaired.\n\nWe had a short window in which this needed to be done. I called Tech City back saying the flooring had been removed and we were ready for the flange repair. The tech scheduled the appointment and asked for a picture of the existing flange. I sent the photo and confirmed the appointment. The tech responded saying they were canceling the appointment and would schedule it when we were ready to re-set the toilet.\n\nFor reference this would have been another $600+ fee, meaning the only way they would replace the flange is if I was going to pay another $500 toilet re-set fee + the flange repair fee. Why didn't they just repair the flange when they were there initially? They could have easily accessed  the flange without the flooring being removed. Yet in still, they could have said up front \"hey we will charge a minimum service fee no matter what.\"\n\nFortunately, I found another plumber to take care of the issue no problem with up-front pricing. My two cents, if you use Tech City, be crystal clear with pricing. Lastly, please ensure follow up calls. I was told two times that I would be called back to confirm the first and second appointment, but never was.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3n5CAB_somUUPjK5nYxy4qXfTyAGz1GkBKfkF7lkKrqvPRPasWxDfHW9zuz0uNLV3AGOpkj9d6duNf_x5ylO1_OfBv-6KSJ_XHlT7fs_f2kq5uGnwtSSGEGfn0KLmcNW8FLHJb=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Fxlsbkc220SoEKu7Vx2_ZP7a40GBK-CXbfM8oMwcI5awk8LAypyJW2HtLLzFcoVA6U721-wwTjFpKaEUWFifcpS57HctVmr-TF--6LFmVDfi_iwL7mHNQkVUpC4GZH6yYoZ7D=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-2"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
