],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"110666142834879717050","name":"AnytimeCE (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110666142834879717050"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"23024 Brier Rd","city":"Brier","postal_code":"98036","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Peter Bennett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmICff1J4X_h9byz7n1i4c-oBGwZ-UPBARimPS8SgCdAGQmVoi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not Impressed. Bought all my courses online at the same time as it was a bundle rate.\nAt time of purchase it was stated,  \"no time limit on courses and saved progress.\"\nThis was untrue, they now are stealing from people in the trades actually making a living. Now you go on the website and it says you must complete courses within 60 days.\nThat is no way to treat a customer. I will be reaching out to BBB about this situation. Don't Buy all you're courses at once! It will just be a friendly donation to anytime CE and the questionable sales tactics they have recently implemented.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVKXX5UrFT7njWiqCOyHoL2NJTTZNmTd8tJrLeGFJYW4cSD0E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was able to complete 24 hours of CEU's in about 4 1/2 hours on a Sunday.  Bundled pricing for the 6 classes saved me a bit of money.\n\nWorth the money to not have to sit in a classroom.\n\nBy Tuesday morning the hours had been reported to the state and I was able to renew.\n\nOverall a good experience.  I will be taking these classes again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brent Zenkner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnsGH3U7H0stQjkTqHUNDGKqUb58gy5veMRlLKc9iM4AJLqgc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I like their continuing education courses online. But unfortunately just like everything else these days you can't call somebody and talk with them if you have a problem. I forgot my password and for some reason they will not send a new link to the right email. And when I try and call of course they tell me I need to go online and email. So how does this solve my problem?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMY9fZ3avxZk2WiWa1krc7yu2kXM2N2CG6Wi0MahML-Z1JHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used AnytimeCE for many years. Every time it has been smooth and I get my credits immediately. I have been in this state 15 years with my card needing to be updated. I did use another company one time and that was a mistake. It seemed like trick questions , I was very frustrated and I kicked myself for not using AnytimeCE. I love being able to get my CE's online at my own furious pace.  Thanks again AnytimeCE !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee McAllister","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-BJAsa50RZSDeK9RYls7cxJtG4ve6CecPKCAnjkpdMAd1hg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"So many problems. It took almost a month to get fixed. Some of the questions didn't match the print out compared to the test. One course got submitted incorrectly and between anytime ce and ce broker and the state nobody would help get the problem fixed. It kept falling on me I was pissed. Would not recommend for electrical","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lloyd Cole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaOk1c4eakjgNofDBdzD1zpx3_wzmcEssqtGD8s85P0z1qx1U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am an HVAC contractor, every year I have to take 4 hours of Continuing Ed courses to keep my licence.  I've used Anytime CE since 2007.\n\nHaving to obtain annual CE hours is never something I like to do, I'm always busy with other things I would rather be doing.\n\nThis year I discovered through AnytimeCE  that I can take 8 hours of CE's and now I can skip every other year. This is great!\n\nThis year I took the course on understanding HVAC electrical diagrams. I can't say that I have mastered the subject in just 8 hours but I do understand wiring schematics much better than prior to talking the course.\n\nWiring diagrams no longer intimidate me.\n\nAnytimeCE courses are easy to use, you go at your own pace. It is set up so that you take a section and while it is still fresh in your mind you take a short test. The 8 CE course I took had 15 segments with a test after each one.\nIf you don't pass you can retake it immediately.\n\nI like the way it is organized.\n\nThe fact that you don't have to study the material and then take one huge test at the end makes it user friendly.\n\nI would highly recommend AnytimeCE to anyone who that needs CE Credits","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Kuriatnyk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWH296bjfT6hdRjM8bAoYqgkB_Q44DuOaNC-7Qlx3zouyWqGKo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Anytime CE proved to be a refreshing improvement over other CE methods I had tried.  Both the design and content were structured such that over all, it combined an excellent teaching format with relevant content.  I highly recommend Anytime CE to anyone and look forward to using it again myself.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Moeller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQVrP6BUmOJLWcpqfRxgzJdgvEIihwHGq8qF4LzSDC31Zavg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AnytimeCEU is the only way to go for any and all plumbers that need to get there credits done. I would not use another online CEU course but theirs for my future credits. The prices are affordable and even better when you bundle them together. I will definitely recommend their service to all my brothers of the pipe trades. Thanks guys for offering such a great tool. This one tool ill be keeping in my tote bag and loaning out to all who ask.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
{"input_id":"32485934-b2f7-461c-952c-c66eee6a2c33","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Allen+Plumbing/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x549aa9e5e912416f:0x92b40193e8a06e1c!8m2!3d47.9630874!4d-122.0168511!16s%2Fg%2F1thl0krb!19sChIJb0ES6eWpmlQRHG6g6JMBtJI?authuser=0\u0026hl=en\u0026rclk=1","cid":"10571075960120045084","title":"Allen Plumbing","categories":["Plumber","Service establishment"],"category":"Plumber","address":"","open_hours":{},"popular_times":{},"web_site":"https://plumbersnohomish.com/","phone":"(425) 502-0106","plus_code":"","review_count":48,"review_rating":4.9,"reviews_per_rating":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":47},"latitude":47.9630874,"longtitude":-122.0168511,"status":"","description":"","reviews_link":"","thumbnail":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFstImjv9GVTfJATvq4XTWBs4Hd4O_rQHOyW44fIJkN_SIEwsVopUReIaKpivpan_ebJ8WxiwklT8-85_fEs5aiGdVrC_EjyTIeJWqYNNVnph1ObRwawqGItiBS5cLxVYxhG70ecA=w408-h306-k-no","timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","price_range":"","data_id":"0x549aa9e5e912416f:0x92b40193e8a06e1c","place_id":"ChIJb0ES6eWpmlQRHG6g6JMBtJI","images":[{"title":"All","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFstImjv9GVTfJATvq4XTWBs4Hd4O_rQHOyW44fIJkN_SIEwsVopUReIaKpivpan_ebJ8WxiwklT8-85_fEs5aiGdVrC_EjyTIeJWqYNNVnph1ObRwawqGItiBS5cLxVYxhG70ecA=w397-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102339080152214499117","name":"Allen Plumbing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102339080152214499117"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Seattle Gal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrxOyedD5X2qfzkc0Q8HZUx89_okHhr4ZIpyZ4B-svy2K2pFA_jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had just had my hip replaced and was home from the hospital when the toilets started to back up. I knew it wasn't the septic and originally called a different plumbing company who wanted to charge $5000. Yeah really. My homeowners insurance recommended Allen plumbing. Shawn fit me in and because my friends were able to dig and expose the pipe from the house to the septic which was the issue he only charged $600 and advised how to reinstall one of the toilets. He was honest, polite and respectful. I would highly recommend Allen Plumbing to anyone. They answer their phones promptly and care about the customer. Integrity and transparency, great to see in a small business! 👏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gene Chatham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1yqCGa1F6PSeUxBWD6sIuAE6T4dFCetCX_XRyTPvqMaDfIE68=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've hired Allen Plumbing four times now, and always been happy with the quality of work done.  My house has had a couple problems due to original work not being done correctly.  I appreciate that Shawn takes the time to explain why the old work was wrong, and then fixes it properly.  Prompt service. Reasonable prices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stacie Douglas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH4pwwRns31RfQmGbx2Vmlku3s3EecrvXbwYIxXmtINYvGU-aB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We called Allen Plumbing to help us assess a water main leak in September of 2023. Sean was able to come out the day after I called him. When he was running late with his morning job he called to let me know that he would be late and was very apologetic. He gave me a second time of arrival and he did show up at that time.\nWhen he realized that we had already dug the trench and found one of the leaks in the water main he was confident that we would be able to fix the leak(s) on our own. So he provided us with valuable information about the lifespan and history of our current pipes. He allowed us to take pictures of the fittings that we would need to fix the repair and told us where to go to get all the supplies. He said to give him a call if we had any questions and wished us the best in our repair journey! We appreciate all of Sean’s knowledge and assistance he was willing to give us Free of charge! Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kris M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrhTvT09KuW1Y2p-JxR0Fqo4uBZnfsmggKyLaIZ_u_eGEkVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shawn came through again! We have worked with Allen plumbing through 2 houses and many years. He and his crew are always quick to come out to our house and not only do the work but keep us educated on how our plumbing systems work. He has done great work for us everytime. Thanks Shawn!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Douglas Hamilton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoYTk099DOk2zHOgWufo5wkU_YK458NTIJIRDdHEwH4bYz2DvZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Allen Plumbing when my garbage disposal jammed up badly—there was a metal bottle opener stuck in the teeth. Instead of just saying it wasn’t worth a service call, he took the time to walk me through the steps to fix it myself over the phone. Thanks to his guidance, I was able to get it out! I really appreciate businesses like this. He could have easily said no, but instead, he took a few minutes out of his busy day to help me out. Thank you, Allen Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Fields","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC9KmArOLNbqnbvfBovdIA2dwwZI33O_7U3tvhC7oWFzFLFsGW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shawn was very patient and prompt as we navigated working with multiple service providers for a plumbing/mold issue that arose at our house. He was flexible in his timing to meet our needs, and was very thorough in his work. He'll definitely be the one we call for future needs! Very nice and professional!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob Ort","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKx72jPbMa4FG2UzWflnyNddxrnBaJ4DtTSBGfRPwGX7aMJkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was having some trouble with my drain pipe for the kitchen sink, it is an older home so it has a copper drain pipe. It kept leaking underneath and i tried to fix it a couple times by myself but to no avail. Shawn came over same day and fixed it within 30 mins or so and it’s been working great ever since. Shawn is very knowledgeable and very personable, you can ask him anything about plumbing and he’ll have an answer for ya. Pricing is very reasonable considering he’s been doing this for 40 years so you’re going to get the best quality as well. Highly recommended! Blessings!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Allen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUk2Fc389SX14iEfNBTWPbg7OzCKyQFJIiACVDo_XiYLKfsJI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Allen Plumbing has been our \"go to\" plumber for the last 8 years.  Mr. Allen always responds promptly and offers his services at a fair price.  He is a pleasure to do business with and we highly recommend for all of our plumbing needs.  Allen Plumbing has redone our septic system and most recently replaced all of the pipes for our bathroom and installed our new hot water heater.  He is knowledgeable and professional.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
