398-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=htU3vxtw4-IjkrN0tWm_zA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=56.58624\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101895021414230398125","name":"Sewer Friendly (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101895021414230398125"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"23930 Hwy 99","city":"Edmonds","postal_code":"98026","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as women-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Ryan Hagen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwbG7NCCmuwk2BL5GvKdGpHtz_itYEo5VPqx3M8qq1VBaHmyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thomas and Jeff from Sewer Friendly were fantastic. We discovered a blocked side sewer right before we were leaving for vacation, and they came out within 45 minutes of our call. They were professional, knowledgeable, and quickly resolved the issue while explaining everything clearly. Their fast response and great service were a huge relief. Highly recommend! Thanks again!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiran Chitluri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmQ5B3n6ACPAnKr6_K7g4TDZ8fTiksuHYbqeziOcl6nPzHk00eTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great team at Sewer Friendly.  we chose them after looking at several local sewer teams.  the main reason we chose them was because it is a family run business with great customer care.  Caleb in the front office was really responsive.  The team that came to do the work was amazing.  I am thankful to Roto, Gabriel, Luis, Chucho, and Guss for doing the job right and taking care of a difficult project between my neighbor and I.  The team always went the extra mile to communicate, make sure the quality was high and that the work got done.  I also appreciated their customer first attitude and camaraderie.  I am thankful for Sewer Friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Seethoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLqFzwz9mbPkZlfd9WNvEIFsmXV15NWH4mP5vGfTim4JxY9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an excellent experience with Sewer Friendly. Our home sits at the bottom of a slope, and heavy rain would send runoff straight into our yard. Combined with a collapsed drain field, this caused severe ground saturation and frequent flooding in our driveway—and even our basement—whenever it rained hard.\nSewer Friendly took the time to walk us through every option, listened thoughtfully to our concerns and ideas, and helped us choose the best long-term solution. Once the plan was set, the work was completed quickly, professionally, and with great care. The crew was clean, friendly, and easy to work with.\nIt’s been two years since the repair, and we’ve now gone through two winter seasons without a single issue. We couldn’t be happier with the results and highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jane Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWoUBWEKLMTVQltgrlT1_TVTTpgB6gJDbwXaUMLbq0Gaddw8ws=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company lives up to their name! Very friendly team! I had been working with Caleb on an estimate for a liner. He was very helpful sharing information and very communicative throughout. It so happened that we had a backup during the process. He was quick to send his team over within the hour of me calling for help! Thomas and Jeff came and saved the day with a quick jetting. We will be getting our liner done this spring with Sewer Friendly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Mecham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpX2ItyXHGICCPA0yf6KVowro8_Ll4iVMs6a7fUnFZp2EO0GFY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We couldn't be happier with the quality of work of Sewer Friendly. They were very thorough in their diligence and repairs of offsets in both our private sewer drain line and a common sewer drain line that we share with three neighbors. We worked with several good folks at Sewer Friendly including Caleb, Sheree, Jeff, Thomas, Gabriel, Nacho, Gus and Rodo. We would use Sewer Friendly again in a heartbeat. Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Crites","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpLqkdDrXpg_Aal2dxnm41pXdchmeku2MHCp20FhvQjd7C8_0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sewer Friendly!\nWow. Okay, so we had an issue, early AM on 12/24. Downstairs toilet backed up from blockage in sewer line. We were headed out of town so couldn't have come at a worse time. Sister-in-law who is a real estate agent got them to come within a couple of hours to scope the line (while we were at the airport) and they got us estimates right away. Besides holidays and already being booked we were able to schedule them to come out first thing in the morning the day after we got back (01/02). They were able to flush the line clear and everything back to normal in just under an hour.\n\nThe response, the professionalism and work was excellent. Would definitely call them again for any issues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Quackenbush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWamLm7X2aVeSbyUNE2tlkbZD3coQXd6oPu1QwCPEzCOSqKkYWNiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We couldn’t be happier with the quality of work of Sewer Friendly. Thomas took the time to explain the technical side of relining our old, cracked sewer so I could feel more knowledgeable and informed. Jeff, Gabriel and Rodo did a high quality job from start to finish. They communicated very well throughout the whole process and also offered competitive prices. We couldn’t be happier with Sewer Friendly and the work they did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Carsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlcp88ynkcTGGEcW_tazvdWSqCdiJfKWy9GjgRw3ILa2d0Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sewer clean out, and replaced sump pump.  SewerFriendly was lowest cost and the folks who did the estimate and installation were the highest skill. And on time, on budget, and friendly!  Thank you Jeff \u0026 Izzy. Look no further (and have your sewer cleaned out regularly!).","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
