rked.\n\nReceived the estimate for replacement on Feb 18.  Originally scheduled for March 11, but they had a cancellation and could fit us in on Feb 26.  Steve was efficient and thorough and had the old water heater swapped out with the new water heater within a few hours.  So very happy to have hot water again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1JZ7KQc1qZ7lm9ZM-5Ncl5awfSjeQqQsoKNwc1cB8STue46jeewq2JwxrGWNwdReEbC3FnFf-E-ALuGZDUdPGcnFc9lTPAk6hMm4D8Bj5k4X9BHRNUmUXRdEzlut6Sv6LdKqDOwVOZB0Vp=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-2"},{"Name":"Debby H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZJrTQaoG8SJLcL7WIPiFTZE6sPURcCn3-rmhaGgFkHiTOwKNT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was able to get a convenient appointment.\nMy disposable wasn't draining properly.\nThe service person was prompt, professional, kept the area clean and worked efficiently and effectively to the point of lowering the overall original quote due to his skill set. Also offered some helpful information regarding keeping drains cleared. THANK YOU to Swift. Always a pleasure to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicki Denoyelles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4B03MVbmyWIOVXVZqHOVltNohYlPsPCZzWUNPpHVl-jl0WQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were amazing! Showed me where and why my toilet seal was failing. Very transparent with charges and explained everything. Couldn’t be more please as to their professionalism and quality of work. Very respectful to myself, and my property. I’m an older widow, and have sadly gotten used to having to question and be very cautious of who I hire to do repairs. This company is trust worthy, as well as reliable! Post my experience with them, I will never go any place else for my plumbing and heating needs! Amazing job guys!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandra Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWJVy-_jX1tDpPZpNlu-qNsxfotvOqbqQwB17WahJ-VLQ6Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Troy from Swift Plumbing and Heating came to our home to repair/replace a faucet that was hard to access and was leaking. We had been told it was not fixable. He diagnosed , replaced and repaired it in 20 minutes! Troy was very personable, professional and skilled! Thank you Troy!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22iehDm1ZI_ALkQ7CP7JvsulyJggF5BnbYBMGEqY3u1ejffWe_Hl6HnICLGl7TKrnYZCHOb_OuRF56StqCMGKC2bKe33UZaMTu6fRS4zrKEjPd8QJtn-xxh19diAv3Bo17TuzjpwDRmSm5=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-19"},{"Name":"Danielle Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVsKNfWiZ4XJSdosVvStq27Sm6NLGRuVg1czPsdmzy3KgdRuWs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Swift Plumbing is fantastic. Lisa and the technicians were amazing to work with from start to finish. They were incredibly responsive, kind, and patient, and made what could have been a stressful situation feel very manageable.\n\nThe team was flexible and understanding, communicated clearly, and worked efficiently even when the job required coming back another day and navigating a few site challenges. Their professionalism really stood out, and the quality of the work was excellent.\n\nOn top of that, their pricing was very competitive and fair. Overall, the customer service, speed, and workmanship were top-notch. I would absolutely recommend Swift Plumbing and wouldn’t hesitate to use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katy T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJtbMfLdSztqw2fk55vq4l_Iu3_Wacg7g0qv5QvnfsfENttg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've used Swift Plumbing three times since moving into a condo a few years ago--first to install a water heater, then remove/install two toilets, and then to remove/install a garbage disposal. Each time I had excellent service. The technicians were kind and efficient, and the work impeccable. They're definitely my go-to!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAhJNRPGiZyVnXZgksJ-7Gt5zKA0Q7r_06lyemBJGatpFUHCu4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Swift Plumbing is our trusted plumber on the Island because the technicians are experts, they arrive on time and prepared to help with whatever leak, clog or issue you may have. Their prices are fair, no pressure to do upgrades, and honestly super friendly and indeed, very swift. Also the folks at the office are also super helpful, great communication and all around excellent customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR8zCwbZnCqzTvN5C8NvIta3gLcJp8NsUwLmEDKXs66MTu4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very good experience.  Two visits.  The first correctly diagnosed two issues. One having to do with our septic system, the second with a toilet left by the previous owner which needed to be replaced.  Completely happy with the professional judgement and the transparent pricing.  We then hired Swift to do the installation of the new toilet.  Exceptionally professional and thorough.   We are going to rely on them for all future work.   Very impressed.  I recommend them without reservation.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
