 our sewer problem, coordinating with the city was critical for expediting the repair. Chris was on it and updated us throughout the entire coordination process. He also checked in with us regularly to make sure we felt that things were moving along smoothly. The two gentleman who came out to do the repair knew exactly what they needed to do and understood the nuances of our particular situation. Within a few hours, we were back online.\n\nThe folks at PSR are really good at what they do, are creative thinkers when a situation requires it, and are really nice human beings. They aren't interested in giving a super high bids simply because they can. I HIGHLY recommend using these guys.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OUuVqL98zr9P7b_lUV_rLRj0q-C4FHDvxNtWoUSltoa3WcL6VfmPWBh_b0UON-3szPIlSNvi1hTKvT7HH6F75CmVkQT-rSJgftMgOx2v_e4IP8inrjj-i4_m_TkYkpFEqdu4pm5r2T3k=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0f0h-KK7wnPq_N-cYUloz7EBLQsDS7iIS-biDJiHJ9EZEWWPsTDQQ0T9li9PJrGMASKEsXZC6enogbDy5DpI797Zqlom64XCmjkOsPPU41-lGpcQE04GTLhUUCwc304y9rbV3_nU63k3IF=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-23"},{"Name":"Doug Auerbach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIozRLPIBiAThzoHQIQ5ARQkBKpeXVv9liiCjg_s2TZcTj2X6dUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were quick to come over and scope out our deteriorated sewer line, provided a written estimate via email in the mid-price-range of the market, scheduled the work, and then came when they said they would; removed our sidewalk stones, dug a big hole, \"shot a liner\" to the sewer main, and restored the surface to almost as good as new. Calm communication and a good experience overall. Other sewer repair companies ghosted us after a verbal estimate or charged an expensive fee just for the scoping before the estimate.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1EYTQKzGNB1DbHG2l9_CfiBgcjyLwjUEINEKijf-MPaDb6B8d8QFfm7wDFuCb7hpMxfkF3_Y4B54ZEuPa2n0vFuWXd37lLQIimNiQ1aMa2SdgAiOzkdxcpyaJV2qdNoCqfMNmrqzTLIvS3=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-6"},{"Name":"Nicole Mastin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwC_FMcMCdrxaVkzq4MWFxRXn-DSjmeAfUYcYDoRWf2UR41MPsww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jaime, Chris and the entire team from ProSewer were fantastic. This was our first scope and discovery project and the team was helpful, transparent and professional every step of the way. After the scope they added an external clean out (as none existed for our property), did a hydro flush and then liner for part of the line. We are on a steep slope, but that did not discourage the team. They managed the excavation, filling of the hole and all repairs beautifully. They followed up a couple months after the work to ensure the excavation site remain stable, which was greatly appreciated and gave us additional peace of mind. We highly recommend the team and their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Mccausland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiUjpe8pElA5d643ZY46lIUrnCzxJx94pNHyEQ2vO8Jsqxrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a pleasure working with Pro Sewer Repair for the lining of my sewer through all phases of work, from the initial estimate and scoping of the work, excavation, lining, and final cleanup.\nAll of their staff were very client oriented, professional, and knowledgeable concerning their work. They kept me informed through the entire process.\nI received other competitive quotes for this work. Pro Sewer Repair was the most competitive.\nThey gave me a schedule for completing the work and they met it, working late the final day and bringing in additional workers to meet their commitments.\nMy sewer line was quite complex to line as there were 4 wye bends from the property line to the city main. Other companies told me they could not shoot the liner past these bends and therefore would have to excavate through the sidewalk and street which would have been a very costly way to make this repair. Pro Sewer Repair did not agree. They felt confident they could shoot the liner through these 4 wye bends which they succeeded in doing saving me thousands of dollars.\nI highly recommend Pro Sewer Repair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christi McCarren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIqIQC831LIxqMkuo4nPQGn-lxwDsMCwD8ZcSbdo7k4qXI8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Pro Sewer Repair for their professionalism, skill and work ethic.  I needed a main sewer line repaired for 125 year old home.  Pro Sewer was able to find a way to avoid digging up my whole back yard and replacing pavers that were involved.  I couldn't have been happier with the result.  I solicited several bids.  While Pro Sewer had the most competitive bid, they also had the most complete work list and detail.  I would definitely use them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chau Pho Tung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrCcGU87yMuHbbh1itIrufKdm5oFQJ0VtfsGeo5V8_qPgTeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a truly excellent experience with Pro Sewer Repair for a spot repair and installation of a CIPP liner for our aging side sewer. The entire team was a pleasure to work with from start to finish, especially Chris B. who was always available to answer our questions and expertly guided us through the entire process.  Scheduling was prompt, communication was excellent, and pricing was very competitive.  They even gave us an existing customer discount on the lining project, plus matched a competing bid to keep our business.  Every member of the work crew was very friendly and both projects were completed on time and in a professional manner.\nThis is a company that really cares about their customers. Chris even made it a point to follow-up with us to make sure that we were happy with service provided.\nWe've already recommended Pro Sewer Repair to a neighbor and would not hesitate to use them again for sewer projects!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Krista Caskey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICQa_i9HyUXYL0ec13RydAXTcmWkvAN4H0q3foJkgvOhhnDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Integrity, kindness, and professionalism from beginning to end - I would recommend Pro Sewer Repair in a heartbeat!\n\nPro Sewer Repair was recommended to us through friends and from the time we started having major issues to the time we felt comfortable moving forward with the fix, it ended up being a year. Rob was gracious enough to come back out and scope the line again, and honor the price of the original bid. At that point, we knew immediately, he was our guy. We felt comfortable with his confidence and knowledge.\n\nThe team showed up right on time all three days, and we’re gracious enough to let us pop out every-so-often to see what was going on and when we did, they explained what was happening and what was to come. Communication was key to us feeling comfortable with a project that seemed daunting, but standard to them.\n\nTo everyone we connected with on the team Rob, Jamie, Peter, Adam, Chris, Michael and Drake you are truly professionals in your field and we are immensely grateful. We can now rest easy!\n\nProject- complete sewer lining on 100+ year old pipe. Plus installing clean-out in front yard.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YVOXaizauKDOQA5AjskDvS8yw_z6RCA00ar_bbGwMfYoN5hsHd8Xtax-0K9JZyffi-NWH0KXTs9O21tGYvPv-MRZ2sQaYkZ5tYqCig_ssoHnPYYtXf72CYI570cQ3VN_7lkCIRMr1mpZj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0mCJWz-WtaVdx3gVwoTA1BIBa-AcCyki8GStrtuaI9pbzRRsU_vILPafsLku2nll2vH3-y6leq_0HzoGBGiH_j3CoBNRSMZsP26BjirjhmCsFFWhYeJ_roAgpw4VzQcYSDcfWhs9omr4cJ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IqR-uWP9m2oEvqOuGx7oCah5-4Y_iASceBOvC6eylI66SMzm6d0T9BTz-cBzVS7kdkJZsiZ5Q31ZkRALe0tAoYiUfLw01RT6VudCs8jgeS43B3b3zC3VKXop23QWgULCzbyGKC7SvSRPE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1IdsKnZOxtCfE0SyOxMJkHx3uOGEIOoFS3dbj89210GQWP6abqXIJvqmC2GN67GyPdJO_RixWYlHV_xCUP-tHypMSNFLB7vtGHRc1iyqR3fTIbnSPAWhg43eWpgmfkLdCK2vJObP6mxa0D=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-6"},{"Name":"Darsi Meyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIXrlNyHDLEyMJAdCLa-0C7ElfGPTeLnqcTEnHnWM8xoqYhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience with Pro Sewer repair for a recent seqer repair. Their Customer Service is truly five star from the first call to the final inspection. They were professional, responsive, and incredibly helpful. What I appreciate most was how they handled the diagnosis.  Instead of pushing a single expensive fix they’ve provided me with multiple options to address the issue. They took the time to suggest the best long-term solution and explain everything in a way that was very easy to understand.  Once they were finished, they let me personally inspect the repair through a video scope of the sewer line so I can see the results for myself. It gave me total piece of mind knowing the job was done right.  I highly recommend Pro Sewer repair to anyone looking for honest, high-quality sewer work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
