olin took the call and shortly after, Shawn called me back. He was at my house same day within 4 hours and unplugged my kitchen drain. The price was very affordable compared to the other quotes I received. Shawn took the time to explain everything as he worked. I will be recommending this business to anyone that needs a plumber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJFURIwdu4NEPSELYiG0mAtW9WOvqKkFWofVWjYGQRnSqOzzs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give more stars if I could. Arrived in a timely manner, personable, knowledgeable, and very fair priced without pushing upsells. Gave us options and recommendations of additional services, but never felt forced one way or the other. Added bonus is that we now know the condition of our plumbing system of this older but new-to-us house.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carlos Medina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLajFPwA13-UXFzdNG4WumQEPHdHmO1bYJJJKsNQC2Xcsyxog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best service ever! Called the day after Christmas due to a clogged kitchen sink and Colin the owner sent Shawn to my house. Nicest guys you could ever meet! And super efficient. Shawn took the time to explain everything , was friendly and kind. He aced the job and it was extremely affordable! Would recommend to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Renee I","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQXU0Y1CDSsJdsOypBGVodUgYWey_Y8hgCOFl96fqxXAM8ltpL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Here's the story: I have a shitty sewer (literally and metaphorically). The sewer line for our house is poorly designed and has lots of bends.  So we have had Angel \u0026 Dirt Cheap Sewer come out to our house a couple times.\n\nFortunately for us, Angel really lives up to his name. He has saved us lots of money and headaches by being a professional and having reasonable rates. He's very kind and considerate with how he works on our house (I have had some other contractors come out and they are sooo messy compared to Angel!) and gave us all the information we needed to make the best decisions moving forward. He resolved our sewer issue quickly and worked with us on a plan for how to avoid the problem in the future.\n\nAfter this most recent visit, it's very clear to me that Angel is the right man for the job! I highly recommend him for any sewer projects you need completed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Ashcroft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImCXSrvi0CU9wp8cJ-Ppjcp5pP_7QsXupho87LLJhVhoO2bA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"am extremely happy with Second Opinion Sewer. They pumped my septic tank and explained how my system works and what might cause the alarm to go off — they answered all my questions and were super eager to help. The amount they charged was very reasonable. Steven and Mark were both great. I am very happy with their service. I will definitely be using them again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYQRbSShZTxFFQATJcBUxY5DdlybQgNVYYWZbMWzwMEU9G2btS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had half a gallon a minute leaking from my water line from the meter to my main shutoff valve.  Carmin ran through the different solutions we could use to remedy the situation.  Not only did Dirt Cheap give a great bid, but they didn't charge to come and give a quote.  Most of the other companies wanted to charge to come out AND wouldn't be able to until next day at the earliest. Dirt cheap came the next morning, replaced my entire line with 1nch pex and did such a professional job.  Dan and Leo are such pros and actually took pride in their work.  The way they worked on it was as if it was their place they were working on.\n\nI'd recommend Dirt cheap for the up front pricing, down to earth vibes (n