new right away based on the symptoms what was going on and gave us three options based on our houses pipe material. ~$400 for the job to clear a clog deeper within our pipes in the shower and it solved the issue!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQypuSsqegg-4EOpMV0vUwUjuTyeRcflZg4tEwh1fNbm4ukvX3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We called 2 Sons to get a second opinion on a pricy quote we received from another company. Dave was professional, very knowledgeable, thorough, and took the time to explain everything and to answer my many questions. He gave us a fair quote for the work that needed to be done as well as a quote for future work items that we didn’t need immediately, which we appreciated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phaedra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIDG2JGoswCDfLs07j4QJGr22gbUpN6JaLMdPTYWLpSCmHnLSwwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dave was incredibly professional and efficient! He clearly explained the issues and didn’t try to talk me into any unnecessary services. Everything is working smoothly.  He also talked to me about how to take better care of my kitchen’s set up, stressing the types of things my garbage disposal actually can/can’t handle. He was also very kind to my cats who insisted on closely monitoring him. I will definitely be calling 2 Sons Plumbing (and Dave!) back for any future issues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Snapper Ploen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxVp4B27YtnU3G-IbsovFLLaFG7r7QAMMzxFVuE8FMCwS7O3T7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dave was awesome and super helpful. He showed up on time, completed fixing my bathroom sink in less than 1 hour and was super friendly. Price point was decent too. It was an absolute pleasure to work with this company. Would definitely recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":