025-11-12"},{"Name":"Ning Hou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvYTdxm7rdfZvT4W0LLPbejKp-L8KFjpY3k-Yx6G4DKK7MYx-y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Queen Plumbing LLC. Steve replaced the shower heads and handles in both bathrooms and fixed a leaking handle quickly and professionally. He was very responsive and able to come out within the same week. We’d definitely use them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cole Hartman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImTWFIpUtTNzPmknCEgd87NffxS7kD-ZIFPlxyNUpVzy-5jzA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Queen Plumbing install a new tankless water heater in our Seattle townhouse and add hot water to an outdoor faucet for dog baths.\n\nThey were the most efficient and transparent of all the companies we got quotes from, and they scheduled the job quickly. The install was professional and friendly, and the work showed real pride and attention to detail.\n\nI don’t usually write reviews, but Queen Plumbing is exactly what you hope for in a plumber. We’ll be using them from now on.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ti8QIKXgx16Zro53fN7lxGldDAzTltLWethbGNWdjV7if3F6-qPYqwsrIQppo6M9sjFn_uFBvWq7nkkqd_Xlkq23BQPnPq63_X9aIEHeRNwYRfFnKvlVXV0Ilr2i7zQ3yNlgL9ViVdf2P=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3WThbXs0KdZiMeVR-bI1L0IZwb_XT96m3zLrb27rOep1Uc28yB6FMREGG96fX_FJn_gr-6MEhdOAizxCuCNvHLLoCZkCkK_amLybT6lXr7BPGN-Md9V5UEobWLMPYGA0ksaAw1qXe3Hcc=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39j1OsULXuaeJshddNXMWLN9-4E-UNj_3qLw625zIAUBMMr2juBUq98f-YmHXs5sqyu7YXknzSwZw_agCCoGOchqwLPUTlPig_F-vtXeBftFgnqS4ehVDzzeAD7dnJOjCmvYtL4xl6PeEt=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-19"},{"Name":"Kiran Chitluri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmQ5B3n6ACPAnKr6_K7g4TDZ8fTiksuHYbqeziOcl6nPzHk00eTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are looking for an excellent plumber for your home projects, I highly recommend Steven and his crew.\n\nGreat service from Queen Plumbing.  We had multiple issues with sewer gas in the house.  Steven and John worked on my basement toilet with persistence and with a positive attitude.  Steven is the owner, operator.  He is really knowledgable.  Steven also has great listening skills and experienced at treating the customer right.  I was pleased with the options he also shared to do a couple of maintenance projects which I already had on my list while they were at the house.  That was super helpful as well.  Steven was also happy to discuss issues on the phone and was extremely responsive over text as well.  I will keep him at the top of my list for future plumbing projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Kommer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIZ4w-LjJU9XtJlHfeYiicwYC1Vr5a9H0KGii6rHuXHGIN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Queen Plumbing recently replaced a leaking plumbing stack in my new house and I couldn’t have asked for better service. From the initial estimate through the work and close out, Steven was a true professional. His work was competitively priced and he was able to start immediately following the first inspection, despite it being a holiday. I will be using Queen Plumbing for all my future needs and recommending them to friends and family without any reservations. 5 Stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gayathri Sriram","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-Vj50zCVmvqWKthgZiRxKpI_QsyBjDn4zdrf8xXgr32hvYfqh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Steven was absolutely incredible to work with. He fixed every issue I’d been struggling with for weeks in like five minutes, which honestly felt like magic. He was extremely flexible with scheduling and timing, and went above and beyond by trying different parts to make sure everything worked perfectly. If you want something done right and without stress, Steven is 100% the guy—I couldn’t be happier with the service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
