tem—they showed up exactly when scheduled, completed the installation quickly, and accommodated our technical requests without hesitation. From beginning to end, the team listened carefully to our needs, provided clear explanations, and made the process easy. Highly recommend Greenwood for their professionalism, punctuality, and dedication to customer satisfaction.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0BoHit9ewzmgLPFqbfUTrD43mVAdozfNATXmyALJGSNr7yqqI9_KjSzOnuLi4witirZFrEQvl66NMTVcSpLivp3vtRhtOwYr439cl908-dc43wKpqZFOSSxLaJJ3c3yMp2QgxEyPOQ2TA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FEC1XYMEdqVTLgvDUzguDCS_t1q2shxTWYDUgWddDT9f6HlCso8GJmJPmySKqSPjDyUQb9AxIf5otl5mR2sEdfNVIdjbS935Yukva2MseDrzspgZfQM66UCidj2nWv91OFKBxN1u6mjg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0akaTsZZZQLvvj1FDEtE9XSyjJ1fxLOxHkY7z3d10LEtcJHKwr00EX2PX1L-_2dVTi1WqVYJ9D4UhqWKmCwtUK70rOOAte0zYD2ImubHtICs6Kpm8T7y-RV0cpqW7AoznvMwNXpwNZDcgq=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-17"},{"Name":"A W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb71rkGDXlSW4mBtxsjzmE_v3IpWotLPyYoLuUtdmKHn-OxRjk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an air conditioner installed for our home and Greenwood made the process by far, the most stress free  and smooth experience. From initial contact for a quote appointment, then going through the details for decision making, and finally installation, every person we worked with was so knowledgeable and professional. Kris assisted with quotes and patiently answered our many questions. Her direct and honest approach was refreshing, and very easy to talk to. Josh, Marco and two other electricians did the install in one day. Josh and his team came on time and were thorough every step of the way. You could just tell they've worked together many times and had excellent problem solving skills to address the house layout. The end product looks so clean and we can't wait to enjoy it this coming summer. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Geoffrey Bean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAFO8m-NZBn9RIvTEQLNeW2uueWkl1k8Lm2UIejg4b7XRLE1Hm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hot water heater burst and Greenwood got someone out on a Sunday to help stop the leak. In the process of getting us back on track a few names are worth mentioning. Tanner helped get our place dry and was very communicative during the process. Mike was the plumbing genius who dug deep and was able to get us a tankless. His professional demeanor and craftsmanship was incredible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phil Flickinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpJfEHc4J4U4TDF4D5jI9nzbktpTAtURxm6aii_dFrsUgKwmhO-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve had amazing experiences using Greenwood’s electrical services. A year ago, we moved into a house that had old electrical wiring that was struggling to keep up with the demands of modern appliances. When Seattle had that awful cold spell in February ‘24, our heat pump kept tripping the circuit and we knew we needed to upgrade our electrical immediately.\n\nOur first interactions were with Jen—a point person who immediately visited to check out the situation, answer our questions, and guide us through the process. She confirmed our suspicions that the house needed both a new panel and upgraded meter. Her colleague Aaron then came to iron out the details. Aaron was phenomenal; he’s incredibly knowledgeable and does a good job of explaining things in easy-to-understand terms. We were in a tricky situation as the power line running from the street to the meter traveled through a tree in our front yard, so Aaron figured out a plan A, B, and C to work around this. (It’s also worth noting that Greenwood has a good relationship with Seattle City Light and they made it easy to get through the potential hurdles of getting things permitted and scheduling service with SCL.) Finally, Chris came to do the actual electrical work and he was extremely professional and his work was impeccable. All of the wiring was organized and secured, and everything on the panel was clearly labeled.\n\nWe used Greenwood again when we needed to set up a dedicated connection for a new dishwasher after our old one broke. Chris came back, and again he did impeccable work, having to work around some constraints to ensure to dishwasher would fit right when the appliance store came to install it.\n\nLast but not least, all of my interactions with Greenwood’s billing team were great. The organization as a whole sweats the details, which any homeowner can appreciate!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2-5e4MZnwg-WPuD_eW9udHj4btf_DA_RPD9Qnwi5c9aJkIijCLLu84rzW4uG5rlDK5aWnPSS0ju2DSDhPraJcRMAqnPqrrs-jEuO9Wz3Wf6KnuNOeKVuzPXRwuorRLHMp8wOQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3SDhYxJgUISbSTGM2mXinF5vLej0GeZi8k-zuceIU9ZvW7dZNmXIxsBP_JskO5MeMk4xv2jYpedmuJ1XQPHZLW1yfH4c6fBsrjtJ3b6rv9PZbXV1Aa_lEcWUQh2EZXzQjWDK-wWw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2rbIbn80MAd1N-ramCuuMB1kHiVEBNtseDBOczv4hd2yy5K8awmdMufLeNVcdbjJzfDQDqn5bRPE1LMJjqLX-49gPMEeMjArYSuYnxfataTTdzRqDPvDVUOa15rFlPOaMcdsRi=k-no"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Bee Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4bZk7nEllABip7uFyNtAi6ku0cB6zajgRqB81JOzoEeTG1Xk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Luke came out to our house on Queen Anne today to help with our thermostat. He was professional, and  had great knowledge of the scope of the problem. Friendly. Great experience! Thank you Luke!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Straub","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFWSGug54Jv4963vKkfL_2u-XtEcIsmKgTSFoAhz0rilCrdGqz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Greenwood provided stellar customer service from the moment Quincy answered my call to the fantastic experience David Mendoza provided to troubleshoot a heat pump issue for me. My issue was resolved same-day for a reasonable cost and with great communication and follow through. As a real estate broker and service provider myself, I’m very impressed and will be recommending Greenwood to clients and anyone else that may have HVAC repair or maintenance needs. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kailin Z Cobos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQobgDSIGwECX4U7lGOWDF1jjM6drDcrXciuXWZmktDtNgiN4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Curtis McCall of Greenwood Heating \u0026 Home Services provided excellent customer service during our annual maintenance appointment last week for our heat pump. I have great confidence in his experience \u0026 expertise and detailed workmanship. I am grateful for the time, patience, care, \u0026 thoroughness with which Curtis works. He is happy to answer all questions and strives to provide you with the information you need to make the best decisions. I always feel like I am in excellent hands with the staff of Greenwood Heating \u0026 Home Services! Thank you so much, Curtis, for the exceptional work and customer service you provided! Thank you, Greenwood Heating \u0026 Home Services, for continuing to be so reliable in your offerings.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tyler Rhead","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5zf6fkY1YxfdAX05afRhb4aIrFCqYTwv1QfcHucoXnzBIyx4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great Greenwood experience! From service tech Al, to sales rep Kyler, to installer Felix and his assistant all went great. Professional, honest, communicative, fast service, and all-around great guys. Would definitely recommend! Nice to have warm tootsies again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Gnh4WlYR406Ml2Jv9kr0leABFdy670i2ZWfvaL4i2Dwpq_d7NJP1drC_LQzedvhoQkN9v6RHvYVeiBiAFazKhBxPc95rY3qrjcsQfLfGF8ldGdyHkkBLFKaimQ7rl-feADGLb=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-30"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
