-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Fresh N Clean repair our septic alarm system - they worked tirelessly through wind storms and heavy rain to get the job done. I would use them again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37pLaNhp12-EdjnDIU6kTd2_3UmQGQ8eDJStUbOPPrwOdD2rKbBS4JbOk6xyxA7DVDs6TdSIpRVi_LGVTB4RjhRqfWD9fuCjaaaiOZbC6ucjLBRdSJLHQxBwMcQDJlCkTgiHLfbVd4fgNQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-16"},{"Name":"Alexander Far","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1azQJuwCNzxrDwbtitKtD3vUwkW0LHrQEhVTwnvjXVLvVCwp2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They responded quickly, arrived on time, and efficiently identified the problem. The crew dug up the area, repaired the issue, and restored everything neatly. They also provided maintenance recommendations and explained the possible causes that led to the pipe failure. I am very satisfied with both the service and the speed of the work, and I can recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Amman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1GUjVP4MZb_QQI4rMKhDmevKghKSEPclHtuifV_-dOqW2EKn3Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had them come out and pump my septic tank today and they did a great job! Very professional and efficient. I highly recommend them for any septic tank pumping and/or maintenance you may need. I am a septic designer so I have extensive experience in the industry and appreciate working with fellow professionals that subscribe to the same level of customer service as I do.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vj7R7pC2OP7vEf3H2OiE8kFeKXLwa3a2RjvXnw6D4hRjHSH5vJbv5zXM8z4rEWcac82bohhdUnUAh9RcX0lVcK86k96JO0-DwT84C_hLTK2-95RvD8X61clIpYImmQF3tiQl-hQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xeNG4K2Fm5IoefYU8VuWrSdUSNERSMLotvpapoy-ul0bj5HA9jbbbtQRE0MqIF6OxBsm4BxpBkFz48WLAmL5Qu_cU4ckZ4jlddFTEXiMvciTgJtYmFK0cqze8szK2Mq8iVPLm=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Sean Lagers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGIjau8ix-OwSI6wQf87z4fzQDjjFpi3ITKZ3UaM2LssF0HeS1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As an infill home builder, we often find “surprises” when excavating new projects.  Keeping things on schedule can be tough when coming across unexpected abandoned septic tanks and timing is everything when you need to get things pumped out fast and decommissioned. I called at the end of the day and Fresh N Clean was able to get us taken care of the next morning.  Great service and great communication!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Byron Hansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGVrYozn_jXj79sXJO-jRZeZ7pgLV0II9gEIljCAqfcgLU_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called for regular service (septic pump-out) and they were able to book next day. They gave me a two hour window, messaged me a couple of updates, and had the job done within the scheduled timeframe. Courteous, conscientious, clean, professional… the whole deal. Their pricing is market, and better if you use a coupon or promotion. I’d sure use them again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2t2uhlXuhSXN8lRhQ0tNMemwbHDPGFDEMY87SWv1KWV1Q-3xrW0YIC75S4v9RyV_37WADOOyqJUKfeygv3ZJ9UpFYrv_qwdCG9pNiAFQTXOlovnJvJWmPsIru9uFt-_s43pG18=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yrl_VDibXKY6UnSCEoiN9lgQVs_UfCyxtwFMzZjqk1S2GiSMlGcqZBjnVBEhx3qyK3jcDK9KYcXarK8FWpILKIA7Natyte_yh8yKBhjrL-2a13v7-EBFUJdmpV9De0_vpE7cxjg=k-no"],"When":"2023-8-4"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
