r100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve used CM Heating for several different projects over the years, including installing my air conditioning, an EV charger, electrical work, and most recently a furnace installation. Every experience with them has been excellent.\n\nTheir team is consistently professional, knowledgeable, and easy to work with, and their pricing has always felt fair and transparent. What really sets them apart, though, is how much they stand behind their work.\n\nAt one point I had an equipment failure that turned out to be a manufacturing defect, not something caused by their installation. Even so, CM Heating stepped in quickly, handled the situation without hassle, and ultimately replaced the unit with an even better product. That level of accountability and customer support is rare.\n\nIt’s clear they genuinely care about doing the job right and making sure their customers are taken care of long after the installation is complete. I wouldn’t hesitate to recommend CM Heating to anyone looking for reliable HVAC or electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MI HYUN SONG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRa-zYkHuKW8UKD2ChNGf09YAXazGf90GZ55OntscOwRUPrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Younis Abdel-Kader accurately identified the issue and handled the repair quickly and efficiently.  His professionalism and technical skills were truly impressive.  His kind demeanor and dedication to providing excellent service, even in the cold weather, reinforced our decision to choose CM Heating.  I ​​especially want to emphasize that employees like Younis are invaluable assets that enhance CM Heating's reputation. Younis, thank you so much. Thanks to you, we were able to escape the cold. I wish you all the best and support you in your future endeavors. I highly recommend Younis and CM Heating to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R Rockhill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJi7rHFnlfiw6H4sL6iUmuBqIcVGlITN_318slmpbtqi48A4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had my gas fireplace fixed, and was extremely happy with my service. Charles was polite/knowledgeable, and had great customer service skills.\nHighly recommended CM and (Charles)!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mihyun Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcKUjrFuhlnZZh-BNf7XTGd_vVct3TVRCemmcjZnyFd_bUkPJjbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you, Younis Abdel- Kader!\nThe technician, Younis, who visited to fix the malfunctioning heater, was professional and highly skilled. He provided detailed explanations and was very kind, making every effort to resolve the problem. He was a helpful employee who genuinely cared about helping us, who were suffering from the cold. We are grateful to Younis for promising to obtain the furnace pressure switch part and repair it as quickly as possible. We hope the problem will be resolved soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNNBCUJjzudsyFtA6sIUV8pbQ1T4hHx-DqvGRJ9d7vDM1Fdlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did a fine job, only time will tell. They came and replaced my 20yr furnace that was busted. Not sure if it could have been repaired but didn’t want to pay just to get a diagnosis for something that probably would need replacement or maybe the tech would try to sell the new furnace anyways… can’t trust people now in days but they did what was asked efficiently, only time will tell how well the works was completed and how the warranty will uphold.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Iman Kalyan Mandal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkHPhlav9jZ1ExCb6v8RbhBck1rdHfVU2d07VglKkmsyax3K0vjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I called these guys for repair as my heat pump wasn't working. They came, inspected the unit but gave vague description of how the compressor was 'shorted' and it was too old of a system to repair. I realized that they had no interest in repairing and were only interested in replacing the whole system with a new unit ($$$).\n\nI called another company and they performed the repair in 15 minutes. Turns out that there was no problem with the compressor at all! In fact, the repair was so easy that it led me to believe that the tech from CM Heating was intentionally misleading me into buying a new system.\n\nDon't think I will call CM heating again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ted Ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTvnMG77_i2OeaEioQ23JRfkKv6lLKBXNCx9QB8ordFqRAUTpZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob and his team installed a new heat pump, (I did not have one, or AC), and replaced my 20 year old gas furnace with a new one in my crawlspace. They were excellent in all areas of completing this job.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jYgyy2f0xnHoz92MiunUawKyKvfVA7GE4XXDT1c_XEEN6O0xBvix0UM82WuSk_5FX04ectm32C8E0VQ4cLp9b9UATaG9H7TcBdzSVXo4UZBW51piECYKzGTEuINyHfFllwBg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0wMxbWY0LXsn-DNAhPGXb-xfMq4-wgLeJU4H-CQj8MU0yB6KKpeshsO5YFp6TI6jy0RNln2mMLqgiDwoq609RIZRsA91sJzMyAxpw4Sr2FbXOzQe6fcDzXeM1zTOdVGx7urORC=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3vQm2-HweJHYlqGhpTt_Jo91Lhf-uXeoq9SvXLPPXQpmMtmwewsdN48cU-jszub1EXrHkOac-4LSyeIiK7bx4MmlXag1S0UXKwUyh3amUAyaMJE_uqarKxY9G4cAAGofZ8QOep=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2py-BFbATMMh7RQdcyf6hL97hZKf2uY3FvELkOiw7qQA-_FdJTDjCzRUdSZ3meW8fwgaH2ePDryfa6uwNvxThyIJmsMHqCcSf3de7HCkHb3hokCUGoK4ztpv1WmGgilQwQMWxhDw=k-no"],"When":"2022-9-14"},{"Name":"Lanay Gard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeD-cPnyJzzU3T3bKD79rmVjOj01GIBBEPwVvsYMljJmFT-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wade young and Mark did a great job. I had no hot water and they figured it was the ignitor switch that 