as right, I would acknowledge that, and if he was wrong, I would change my review and notify the company. He stormed out of my house essentially yelling at me for wasting his time.\n\nI just had that second opinion from Eco Electric, Plumbing, and Heating. My tech, Zach, looked under the sink, found the outlet, and pushed the reset button. Voila. Garbage disposal working again. $50 consult fee and an even better tip for him.\n\nI do not recommend Hotwire Furnace, and I definitely do not recommend Alex K.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Q218d1Oeby5yjfVZUTuFNku8EdLHTo6aFKtV-8jsY_AqOdX7MMz9razSHESjlNk0cRP4oMA5PG2X5PejVtgetJFbEKKsDE5va_QlgyFroSETt378dqPiszC5VC9oH16SHGu8uNeyRwdU=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-3"},{"Name":"Jeff Padilla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjfSUsHZNhgWFd3JK0mv5cYsHh3VSlsCOWIXFYQo8XXylAbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vlad was great! He was on time and very friendly! He took care of everything and got our oven running again. I would definitely recommend their services to anyone I know!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0h5ZwdlLrLUffE27uzDBFoDeWjCyr4F-i34YRDjhl0JXNZlw-ubt5VS13VXvjRjjvam3iFbbfRLNBPYLWPX_V-AMUoEJOO3pSe3Ze5gXXXA7gcqWoM1H6xpRuB3Rku2zQYlnek1XhV2-Vc=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-13"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
