h3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9GsOfaCU_oWipsW1-QLm7Kj2dQoZsCAZfPJCPJ50FY-d__w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel so lucky to have found Crown Plumbing. We needed to re-direct the  whole drain line of our house to opposite direction in order to connect to sewer. I was overwhelmed with the scale of work but when Crown Pluming came for an eatimate I could tell I could totally trust them. They started the job as planned and were informative, professional and straight forward and friendly. I felt like they were “taking care of us” rather than “ just doing the job”.\nA house project like this could be a headache if you got flaky and unreliable company but Crown Plumbing was just a total opposite of that. I’m very thankful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Welvaert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMPZzmYVjc3k92kJS_syTMHTeFP4WV6t2Md2glj9J5X8s3BX57=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need an honest plumber to do work in your home or business, I recommend Nate and his crew at Crown Plumbing.  It can be extremely difficult to find a business that operates with core values like;  integrity, honesty, and excellence.  Nate operates one of those businesses. He doesn't just go to work to make money, he goes goes to work to help people and their plumbing needs. Nate is genuine and professional,  and I recommend him and his entire team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rick O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFsqyl_85fFxlCalPRWeND8-otRFKK-mcqurd-tzfV8t4BWd05=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The crew from Crown did all the plumbing in a bathroom remodel we did at our house.  They were extremely patient and flexible  and worked around our schedule.  They were friendly, helpful, very professional and reasonably priced.  I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristina Lampert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvWA405VKR8KSb2BYsLKPqffOQt11yuhhtVEmgL3UYm8W5iA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I feel I was completely ripped off on pricing.  Their office is about a half mile from my home and they charged me an $8.14 fuel tax.  They also had two people there and it was a one person job and they billed me for both.  Then, they would not guarantee their work!   Plus they charged me $59 to come fix a leak I told them about as an \"assessment\" fee!  Even though they stayed and fixed the leak, they still charged that on top of parts, labor for two, fuel tax, sales tax and then the $59 fee!  Wow, way to rip off a customer who could have given you a great recommendation and tons of repeat business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"judy a nason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2IzqhDNJJOPL5FAmZkCBKs8kIx0djuMcRBsUIwOb2xBRPm77A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nathan and his employees have done work for us on several occasions, and we have been more than satisfied every time!  Nathan is responsive, honest, fair and experienced. He also has artistic capability, which is demonstrated in the way he designs his work to be functional, safe and making the best use of space. Most important, he has integrity in running his business.  We will use no one else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVVICtINH31Rnwgy1yqEn-JigFT71UdskRut_jNa5J7TSaEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently moved to Snohomish and have needed a plumber several times with issues from sewer line back up to pipes leaking in the walls.  Every time the team has come out they have been courteous and they know there business.  They are up front about cost and issues.  They take time to answer questions.  I will call them for my next plumbing issue.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
