t_0vRlkFTErw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a major leak and our regular plumbing couldn't make it until later in the day. We called RW and they were able to fit us in much sooner. They did such a good job and were there for me so I will be calling them next time I have any plumbing problems.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edmond Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdxJWhnPkFzBbVT-23J3aUSk3mm7ULsDjPq5_NUeFahHqlMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used them a few times in the last few months for different things. The service is reliable and they arrive when scheduled. The worker are professional and courteous at all times and were never shy about answering questions. I like the work they do and would have no problem hiring them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gueorgui Dimitrov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5Y4cQ0MsDSZOdQXJdVWEtU78xAUjcNTIeZ29gZrhyBJ2CKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
