0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"","name":"Garrett \u0026 Sons Water Heaters (Owner)","link":""},"complete_address":{"borough":"Fremont","street":"202 N 36th St #7550","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98103","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mario Graham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIND0daIhwhqZlOTAuRZz5JSKYNTn--_iafGzqYcNIwcUg6Sg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"i had a fantastic experience with Garrett \u0026 Sons Water Heaters. i needed a new hot water heater installed, and a young plumber named Austin came out to check things out and gave me a free estimate. we scheduled the replacement for the following week, but when my old water heater suddenly started leaking badly, i called to see if they could help sooner. they were able to come out just a few hours later. austin took care of removing the old tank and installing the new one, and he did an excellent job. he was friendly, professional, and really knew what he was doing. the price was fair, and the service was even better than i expected. i'm glad to have a reliable plumbing company i can count on now.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"avery keller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-RI4ZHwTEvRr5_6N5RN9spSKhfjZ8z4j3oQSPtJyhLPd5aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a plumbing emergency at our home in Seattle, and we are so grateful for the quick response. Austin arrived right away and took care of the issue efficiently. Not only did he fix the problem, but he also made sure our place was spotless when he finished. The team was incredibly friendly and explained everything to me and my kids in simple terms, which we really appreciated. Everyone was knowledgeable, polite, and went above and beyond to make sure we understood what was going on. I highly recommend this plumbing company for anyone in Seattle looking for reliable and friendly service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jose mckenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR8IEQf11GPQaz204RunfLJD1Nf28OiZjWatrlHn8tHiRChQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our septic system stopped working, so we needed a plumber to install a new one. After getting several estimates, we chose this company because they gave us the best price. Cesar and his team were great from start to finish. On the first day, they pumped out the old system and removed the old tanks. Once they started digging, the new tank was delivered right on time, and we could use it within a few hours. The next day, they built the mound and ran the pipes from the tank to the mound. By the third day, everything was finished. I was really impressed by how quickly and smoothly the crew worked together. They were so dedicated that they didn’t even take a lunch break—they just wanted to get the job done for us. My wife and I are very happy with the service and highly recommend them if you need plumbing or septic help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann Mathews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIY-ydHc5KKkDxZZz44wYVz8BXqTEdBlI05ZYA_ldz8-bGcGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cesar came out to my brother-in-law's condo in Seattle to replace a toilet. While working, he noticed the bathroom sink needed a new P-trap, and also found a slow leak in one of the pipes caused by rust. We didn't know about these extra issues, but thanks to Cesar, everything was found and fixed quickly and at a great price. We've used this plumbing company before and they always provide excellent service. We plan to call them for any future plumbing needs. The team is always thorough and makes sure everything is working perfectly. We feel lucky to have found such a reliable plumber and highly recommend them to anyone in Seattle.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"maverick arnold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5yvPgneIhTpsBkgFHc_vpadvIZ29P8qDdMcbIjsoVEB2LaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My mom's double kitchen sink was draining really slow, so I called a plumber for help. Cesar and Austin came out and put in a lot of effort to get the drain cleared up. They ran into a tricky issue with one of the pipes downstairs, so they got in touch with the team for extra help. Cesar returned with another plumber and they worked together to fix everything. Everyone who helped was friendly, professional, and really knew what they were doing. The price for the service was fair too. I appreciate all the hard work they did to get our sink working right again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robin13 W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0jZaxrCvSBeS7AaVzOhIsr2EflxKNnuVhfbqCAbnDLqR1Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"i've been calling this plumbing team in seattle for a while now, and i'm always happy to use their services again and again! a while back, they came out and fixed my kitchen sink and garbage disposal for a really fair price, even though i'm a bit outside the main part of seattle. austin and his coworker were super professional, knew what they were doing, and took the time to explain everything to me. this week, when a water pipe broke at my house, i knew exactly who to call. they even showed up earlier than i expected, finished all the repairs quickly, and the price was very reasonable. everything was done in under two hours. i appreciate how reliable and fast these plumbers are. i'll definitely call them again next time i need help with my plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stacy Mullen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIG8OqrT0XmK6vXOJByIoK0Byy9buZbYq9Tk77HaVxGabiK_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Austin and Cesar were fantastic to work with. They were flexible and managed to fit my cafe's plumbing work in between other projects so the job got done quickly. The piping installation was smooth, and everything looks great. They also helped me install a faucet I picked out myself to match a sink I purchased elsewhere, which I really appreciated. On top of that, they found a more affordable water heater for me online and took care of getting it, which saved me money. As a small business owner, I was very happy with their reliable, high-quality, and reasonably priced plumbing services. I would definitely recommend them to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marissa E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2ytHXmVjYv9uOgEHns-aCBs1eMvq0-bN13wppazGNhIElCUY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are so grateful for the help we received! We had a plumbing emergency after hours when water started dripping from our drop ceiling in the finished basement. After trying a few other plumbing companies in Seattle with no luck, we finally got connected with Cesar. He realized he was close by and came over right away. Cesar quickly figured out what was wrong and fixed the issue in less than an hour. He was really friendly and professional throughout the whole process. We’ve found a great plumber, and this will definitely be our first call whenever we need plumbing services!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
