:[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"k gal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-xQ6NJht4JaDRN2-MenDN0vLKvnmr4GvlSktYOBN9bUGqxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s a great feeling when a company goes above and beyond to make you feel that you are their number one priority.\n\nThis winter Kings Heating, Air \u0026 Electric  replaced my 40-year-old electric furnace with a two piece, indoor, outdoor, Mitsubishi ducted heat pump.\n\nThis was a big job and significant investment for me.\n\nThe entire team, from start to finish, interacted with great support and a personalized approach.\n\nThey were patient and took the time to address my many questions without rushing through with quick answers.  They gave knowledgeable and thorough explanations providing me with understanding that allowed a level of confidence and eased my stress.\nGreat Company, Great Customer Service.  I would choose them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Traveller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVDuLboQEof_UnHBnTJW7xg8oO1F1AXRWr0ia1PLswQM7zBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a new HVAC system installed at my home back in August 2025, and I’m finally getting around to leaving this review. The system has been running great since the installation, and I happy with the entire experience.\n\nFrom the start, Mike in sales was great to work with—no pushy sales tactics, just honest information and a real willingness to earn my business. I gathered quotes from several companies, and they not only beat the others on price but also offered a higher-rated HVAC system.\n\nThe installation crew—Mason, Josh, Cody, and Treg—did an outstanding job. They kept me informed throughout the process, worked efficiently, and even fixed an existing electrical issue from my old HVAC at no additional cost. They ran a new wire line to the panel and made sure everything was safe and up to code.\n\nThere was a missing Kumo Cloud during the initial install order, but the team handled it professionally. They followed up, came back out, and completed the configuration without much hassle.\n\nOverall, excellent service, fair pricing, quality equipment, and a team that truly cares about doing things right. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roger Krause","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRf3liXhDJOqq80bcVp4A1CTXCZH_QtZiLIJysCs-LYETgiA7K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a condensation pump go out on our gas furnace. We contacted Kings Heating and Cooling service on Sunday ( left a voice mail) and they returned our call first thing Monday morning. They dispatched a service technician (Ryan) that morning who replaced the pump. Ryan was very professional and personable. He did a great job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Marie White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbYJ7RgojbFlRXCHjQa0d8BKgVmBbqBPQ_tiXn18U2PLfLUte6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We originally reached out to King's for a second quote, this was done for a home warranty claim to replace a defective furnace. Chris was our estimator and he was great to work with. We went ahead and accepted the bid from King's. The folks who came out to do the work did a very, very good job. The customer service from start to finish, from every person, was top notch. Thanks for making our home cozy and safe again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicki Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfZQzCeFEBo1ljLQfNXItEVUpQlY0gHTrJhVYblfj0nxl9Boyi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kings Heating Air \u0026 Electric did a totally AWESOME job on replacing an old furnace.  We shopped several contractors.  Kings came out and did a completely thorough job evaluating the need and coming up with the best solution.  Plus, the price was highly competitive to all others who provided bids.  We feel they gave us excellent service and the heating system is so far above what we previously had - we are very happy.  I thoroughly recommend Kings.  Many thanks to Padric and Josh L. who did the installation.  Great job!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dani Gamman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZijIV7z-8BEPXaPKEcP0gYbw5aSvw818TJQ4wxPiLGTzVUyi1QQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"100/10 stars for this company! Every single person I talked to was so nice, so helpful. Mike was especially lovely. I'm a GC and had some HVAC work pop up on a project with an already super tight timeline... They fit me in super quick and completed a difficult job for a fair price that other companies quoted $10-20k to do, or told me it couldn't be done. Great communication too. So so happy with them and will 100% be using them for all HVAC from here on out!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Johanson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRNPZjl6Opx1OMzHSFFsH8lFK48g0TRgwvloGNBZljwwKs7RsR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently bought a house and wanted our furnace/HVAC system checked over. We got a recommendation for this company and decided to give them a call. We called the week of Thanksgiving and they had an last minute opening they could fit us into which was suprising and convenient. Our tech Geoffrey was very communicative about when he would arrive so we didn't have to wait around all evening wondering. He was fast, friendly and knowledgeable. He did a thorough inspection, helped educate us on how to properly maintain our system and even called the next day to follow up on one issue he found and wanted to give us more information. I highly recommend them to anyone looking for a reputable company to work with and ask for Geoffrey if you get a chance - he was great. I always prefer small businesses over large corporations and this is one of those gems.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rayna Hwynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRa2cN4m8hRuJaK-YEjHkBYG8JJgwtkMZ0z-tYPWJZaVP78TUvwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just had Kings Heating, Air and Electric come to our house for a service appointment on our furnace. I was extremely impressed from start to finish. Scheduling the appointment was easy. When it was time for the technician to arrive, I got a text message with his picture and a little bio about him. This was nice so I knew exactly who was arriving at our house. He was thorough and showed us pictures of the furnace inside. He educated us on our furnace and filters. He made sure that he cleaned up after his work. We were given recommendations which were honest and thorough. I highly recommend using this company for any service or installation needs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kynHMehs208WTvztEYBT8XqySre32LmEwFzfnP_zc_p5Hj1yO4A8yDOh9vkgUDOHoWMJyyIkqs8ptaNqc5ayjI41gRpHQwy_ngfRf2SaxrWBHgL0x7T4o8wZuZkcgdy1dO2TGFPRrBm8=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-25"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
